4513 		top.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
4514 		grp.appendChild(top);
4515 	}
4516 	var path = "M %X%,%Y% l %W%,0 l 0,%F% l -%W%,0 l 0,-%F%";

5552 {

5580 	}

6416 /**
6417  * Draw a circular arch frame inside a specified rectangle.
6418  * 
6419  * Frame corners are mitered.
6420  *  
6421  * @param id		String id
6422  * @param x			decimal x coordinate
6423  * @param y			decimal y coordinate
6424  * @param w			decimal width
6425  * @param h			decimal height
6426  * @param h2		decimal height legs
6427  * @param inset		decimal frame thickness
6428  * @param color		String web color code
6429  * @param segParm	char L (left), R (right), F (full)
6430  * @return
6431  */
6432 function initArchCircular(id, x, y, w, h, h2, inset, color, segParm)
6433 {
6434 // segType: F=full, L=left half, R=right half
6435 try
6436 {
6437 trace("initArchCircular'"+id+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ h+","+ h2 + ","+ inset+",'"+ color+"','"+segParm+"')");
6438 
6439 var segType = segParm === null ? "F":segParm;
6440 
6441 	var pLT,pRT,pLB,pRB,pC;
6442 	if(h2 == 0)
6443 	{	
6444 		switch(segType)
6445 		{
6446 			case 'F':
6447 				computeCircleCenter(x,y+h,x+w/2,y,x+w,y+h); // sets global R
6448 				pLT = new Point(x,y+h);
6449 				pRT = new Point(x+w,y+h);
6450 				pLB = new Point(x,y+h);
6451 				pRB = new Point(x+w,y+h);
6452 				break;
6453 
6454 			case 'L':
6455 				computeCircleCenter(x,y+h,x+w,y,x+(2*w),y+h); // sets global R
6456 				pLT = new Point(x,y+h);
6457 				pRT = new Point(x+w,y);
6458 				pLB = new Point(x,y+h);
6459 				pRB = new Point(x+w,y+h);
6460 				break;
6461 							
6462 			case 'R':
6463 				computeCircleCenter(x-w,y+h,x,y,x+w,y+h); // sets global R
6464 				pLT = new Point(x,y);
6465 				pRT = new Point(x+w,y+h);
6466 				pLB = new Point(x,y+h);
6467 				pRB = new Point(x+w,y+h);
6468 				break;
6469 						
6470 			default:
6471 				break;				
6472 		}
6473 	}
6474 	else
6475 	{
6476 		switch(segType)
6477 		{
6478 			case 'F':
6479 				computeCircleCenter(x,y+h,x+w/2,y,x+w,y+h); // sets global R
6480 				pLT = new Point(x,y+h);
6481 				pRT = new Point(x+w,y+h);
6482 				pLB = new Point(x,y+h+h2);
6483 				pRB = new Point(x+w,y+h+h2);
6484 				break;
6485 
6486 			case 'L':
6487 				computeCircleCenter(x,y+h,x+w,y,x+(2*w),y+h); // sets global R
6488 				pLT = new Point(x,y+h);
6489 				pRT = new Point(x+w,y);
6490 				pLB = new Point(x,y+h+h2);
6491 				pRB = new Point(x+w,y+h+h2);
6492 				break;			
6493 							
6494 			case 'R':
6495 				computeCircleCenter(x-w,y+h,x,y,x+w,y+h); // sets global R
6496 				pLT = new Point(x,y);
6497 				pRT = new Point(x+w,y+h);
6498 				pLB = new Point(x,y+h+h2);
6499 				pRB = new Point(x+w,y+h+h2);
6500 				break;
6501 				
6502 			default:
6503 				break;						
6504 		}
6505 	}
6506 	pC = new Point(Xo,Yo);
6507 	initArchCircularSeg(id, pLT, pRT, pLB, pRB, pC, R, inset, color);
6508 	
6509 }	
6510 catch(e)
6511 {
6512 	alertUser("Exception:  initArchCircular('"+id+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ h+","+ inset+",'"+ color+"','"+segParm+"')");
6513 	alertUser(e);
6514 	trace(e);
6515 }
6516 }
6517 
6518 /**
6519  * Draw a circular arch frame inside a specified rectangle.
6520  * 
6521  * The base of the frame (sill) is squared.
6522  *  
6523  * @param id		String id
6524  * @param x			decimal x coordinate
6525  * @param y			decimal y coordinate
6526  * @param w			decimal width
6527  * @param h			decimal height
6528  * @param h2		decimal height legs
6529  * @param inset		decimal frame thickness
6530  * @param sill		decimal sill thickness
6531  * @param color		String web color code
6532  * @param segParm	char L (left), R (right), F (full)
6533  * @return
6534  */
6535 function initArchCircularWithSill(id, x, y, w, h, hLeg, inset, sill, color, segParm)
6536 {
6537 // segType: F=full, L=left half, R=right half
6538 try
6539 {
6540 trace("initArchCircularWithSill"+id+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ h+","+ hLeg + ","+ inset+ ","+ sill+",'"+ color+"','"+segParm+"')");
6541 
6542 var segType = segParm === null ? "F":segParm;
6543 
6544 	var h2 = hLeg;
6545 	if(sill > hLeg && hLeg > 0)
6546 	{
6547 		h2 = 0;
6548 		h += hLeg;  
6549 	}
6550 		
6551 	var pLT,pRT,pLB,pRB,pC;
6552 	if(h2 == 0)
6553 	{	
6554 		switch(segType)
6555 		{
6556 			case 'F':
6557 				computeCircleCenter(x,y+h-sill,x+w/2,y,x+w,y+h-sill); // sets global R
6558 				pLT = new Point(x,y+h-sill);
6559 				pRT = new Point(x+w,y+h-sill);
6560 				pLB = new Point(x,y+h-sill);
6561 				pRB = new Point(x+w,y+h-sill);
6562 				break;
6563 
6564 			case 'L':
6565 				computeCircleCenter(x,y+h-sill,x+w,y,x+(2*w),y+h-sill); // sets global R
6566 				pLT = new Point(x,y+h-sill);
6567 				pRT = new Point(x+w,y);
6568 				pLB = new Point(x,y+h-sill);
6569 				pRB = new Point(x+w,y+h-sill);
6570 				break;
6571 							
6572 			case 'R':
6573 				computeCircleCenter(x-w,y+h-sill,x,y,x+w,y+h-sill); // sets global R
6574 				pLT = new Point(x,y);
6575 				pRT = new Point(x+w,y+h-sill);
6576 				pLB = new Point(x,y+h-sill);
6577 				pRB = new Point(x+w,y+h-sill);
6578 				break;
6579 						
6580 			default:
6581 				break;				
6582 		}
6583 	}
6584 	else
6585 	{
6586 		switch(segType)
6587 		{
6588 			case 'F':
6589 				computeCircleCenter(x,y+h,x+w/2,y,x+w,y+h); // sets global R
6590 				pLT = new Point(x,y+h);
6591 				pRT = new Point(x+w,y+h);
6592 				pLB = new Point(x,y+h+h2-sill);
6593 				pRB = new Point(x+w,y+h+h2-sill);
6594 				break;
6595 
6596 			case 'L':
6597 				computeCircleCenter(x,y+h,x+w,y,x+(2*w),y+h); // sets global R
6598 				pLT = new Point(x,y+h);
6599 				pRT = new Point(x+w,y);
6600 				pLB = new Point(x,y+h+h2-sill);
6601 				pRB = new Point(x+w,y+h+h2-sill);
6602 				break;			
6603 							
6604 			case 'R':
6605 				computeCircleCenter(x-w,y+h,x,y,x+w,y+h); // sets global R
6606 				pLT = new Point(x,y);
6607 				pRT = new Point(x+w,y+h);
6608 				pLB = new Point(x,y+h+h2-sill);
6609 				pRB = new Point(x+w,y+h+h2-sill);
6610 				break;
6611 				
6612 			default:
6613 				break;						
6614 		}
6615 	}
6616 	pC = new Point(Xo,Yo);
6617 	initArchCircularSegWithSill(id, pLT, pRT, pLB, pRB, pC, R, inset, sill, color);
6618 	
6619 }	
6620 catch(e)
6621 {
6622 	alertUser("Exception:  initArchCircularWithSill"+id+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ h+","+ h2 + ","+ inset+ ","+ sill+",'"+ color+"','"+segParm+"')");
6623 	alertUser(e);
6624 	trace(e);
6625 }
6626 }
6627 
6628 /**
6629  * Compute a horizontal adjustment factor used to center a radial shape 
6630  * inside the containing frame.
6631  * 
6632  * @param w		decimal width of the frame
6633  * @param h		decimal height of the frame
6634  * @param inset	decimal inset from base of frame to the glass 
6635  * @return	decimal 
6636  */
6637 
6638 function computeHorzOffset(w,h,inset)
6639 {
6640 		computeCircleCenter(0,h,(w/2),0,w,h);
6641 		
6642 		var adj =  (w/2) - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(R,2) - Math.pow(Yo-h+inset,2));
6643 		
6644 		return Math.abs(adj);
6645 }

6663 function initGlassArchCircular(id, idFrame, x, y, w, h, h2, inset, segParm)

6666

6668

6671

6681 			case 'F':

6684 				pRT = new Point(x+w,y+h);
6685 				pLB = new Point(x,y+h);

6691 				pLT = new Point(x,y+h);
6692 				pRT = new Point(x+w,y);
6693 				pLB = new Point(x,y+h);
6694 				pRB = new Point(x+w,y+h);
6695 				break;
6696 							
6697 			case 'R':
6698 				computeCircleCenter(x-w,y+h,x,y,x+w,y+h); // sets global R
6699 				pLT = new Point(x,y);
6700 				pRT = new Point(x+w,y+h);
6701 				pLB = new Point(x,y+h);
6702 				pRB = new Point(x+w,y+h);
6703 				break;
6704 						
6705 			default:
6706 				break;				
6707 		}
6708 	}
6709 	else

6716 				pRT = new Point(x+w,y+h);

6718 				pRB = new Point(x+w,y+h+h2);

6723 				pLT = new Point(x,y+h);

6726 				pRB = new Point(x+w,y+h+h2);
6727 				break;			
6728

6731 				pLT = new Point(x,y);
6732 				pRT = new Point(x+w,y+h);

6770 /**
6771  * Draw a horizontal segment of a radial glass.
6772  * 
6773  * @param id		String id
6774  * @param idFrame	String id of containing frame
6775  * @param pLT		Point left top
6776  * @param pRT		Point right top
6777  * @param pLB		Point left bottom
6778  * @param pRB		Point right bottom
6779  * @param pC		Point center of the arc
6780  * @param r			decimal radius of the arc
6781  * @param inset		inset inside the frame
6782  * @return
6783  */
6784 
6785 function initGlassArchCircularSeg(id,idFrame, pLT, pRT, pLB, pRB, pC, r, inset)
6786 {
6787 
6788 try
6789 {
6790 trace("initGlassArchCircularSeg'"+id+"',("+pLT.x+","+ pLT.y+"),("+pRT.x+","+ pRT.y+"),("+pLB.x+","+ pLB.y+"),("+pRB.x+","+ pRB.y+"),("+pC.x+","+ pC.y+"),"+ r+","+ inset+")");
6791 
6792 	var x = pLT.x;
6793 	var y = Math.min(pLT.y,pRT.y);
6794 	var w = pRT.x-pLT.x;
6795 	var h = pRB.y-y;
6796 	var segType = "F"; // segType: F=full, L=left, R=right
6797 	if(pLT.y < pRT.y)
6798 	{
6799 		segType = "R";
6800 	}
6801 	else
6802 	if(pLT.y > pRT.y)
6803 	{
6804 		segType = "L";
6805 	}
6806 	
6807 
6808 
6809 
6810 
6811 	var iLT,iRT,iLB,iRB;
6812 	
6813 	var hLegs = pLB.y - Math.max(pLT.y,pRT.y);
6814 
6815 
6816 	var	rInner = r - inset;
6817 		
6818 	if(hLegs === 0)
6819 	{
6820 		switch(segType)
6821 		{
6822 			case "F":
6823 				iLT = new Point( pC.x - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.y-(pLT.y-inset),2)),
6824 								pLT.y - inset);
6825 				iRT = new Point(pC.x + Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.y-(pLT.y-inset),2)),
6826 								pRT.y - inset);	
6827 				
6828 				d = "M "+iLT.x+","+iLT.y+" A "+rInner+","+rInner+" 0 0,1 "+iRT.x+","+iRT.y+ " L "+iLT.x+","+iLT.y;
6829 				iLB = iLT;
6830 				iRB = iRT;
6831 				break;
6832 			case "L":
6833 				iLT = new Point( pC.x - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.y-(pLT.y-inset),2)),
6834 								pLT.y - inset);
6835 				iRT = new Point( pRT.x - inset,
6836 								pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.x - pRT.x + inset,2)));
6837 				iRB = new Point(pRB.x-inset,pRB.y-inset);
6838 				d = "M "+iLT.x+","+iLT.y+" A "+rInner+","+rInner+" 0 0,1 "+iRT.x+","+iRT.y+
6839 				 " L "+iRB.x+","+iRB.y+
6840 				 " L "+iLT.x+","+iLT.y;
6841 				iLB = iLT;
6842 				break;
6843 			case "R":
6844 				iLT = new Point( pLT.x + inset,
6845 								pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pLT.x + inset - pC.x,2)));
6846 				
6847 				iRT = new Point( pC.x + Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.y-(pRT.y-inset),2)),
6848 								pRT.y - inset);
6849 								
6850 				iLB = new Point(pLB.x+inset,pLB.y-inset);
6851 				d = "M "+iLT.x+","+iLT.y+" A "+rInner+","+rInner+" 0 0,1 "+iRT.x+","+iRT.y+
6852 				 " L "+iLB.x+","+iLB.y+
6853 				 " L "+iLT.x+","+iLT.y;
6854 				iRB = iRT;
6855 
6856 				break;
6857 			default:
6858 				break;	
6859 		}
6860 	}
6861 	else
6862 	{
6863 		switch(segType)
6864 		{
6865 			case "F":
6866 				iLT = new Point( pLT.x+inset,
6867 								 pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.x-pLT.x-inset,2)));
6868 				iRT = new Point( pRT.x - inset,
6869 								 pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pRT.x-inset-pC.x,2)));
6870 				iLB = new Point( pLB.x+inset,pLB.y-inset);
6871 				iRB = new Point( pRB.x-inset,pLB.y-inset);
6872 				break;
6873 				
6874 			case "L":
6875 				iLT = new Point( pLT.x+inset,
6876 								 pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.x-pLT.x-inset,2)));
6877 				iRT = new Point( pRT.x - inset,
6878 								pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.x - pRT.x + inset,2)));
6879 				trace("iRT.x="+pRT.x-inset);
6880 				iRB = new Point(pRB.x-inset,pRB.y-inset);
6881 				iLB = new Point(pLB.x+inset,pRB.y-inset);
6882 				break;
6883 			case "R":
6884 				iLT = new Point( pLT.x + inset,
6885 								pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pLT.x + inset - pC.x,2)));
6886 				
6887 				iRT = new Point( pRT.x - inset,
6888 								pC.y - + Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pRT.x-inset-pC.x,2)));
6889 				iRB = new Point(pRB.x-inset,pRB.y-inset);
6890 				iLB = new Point(pLB.x+inset,pLB.y-inset);
6891 				break;
6892 			default:
6893 				break;	
6894 				
6895 		}
6896 		d = "M "+iLT.x+","+iLT.y+" A "+rInner+","+rInner+" 0 0,1 "+iRT.x+","+iRT.y+
6897 					 " L "+iRB.x+","+iRB.y+
6898 					 " L "+iLB.x+","+iLB.y+
6899 					 " L "+iLT.x+","+iLT.y;
6900 			
6901 	}
6902 
6903   	var glass = drawing.getElementById(id);
6904 
6905 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id);
6906 	var idPrefix = g("f_idprefix");
6907 	if(grp === null)
6908 	{
6909 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
6910 		grp.setAttribute("id",id);
6911 
6912 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
6913 	}
6914  	
6915 	var gls = drawing.getElementById(id+"_pane");
6916 	if(gls === null)
6917 	{
6918 		
6919 		gls = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
6920 		gls.setAttribute("id",id+"_pane");
6921 		gls.setAttribute("class","glass");
6922 		gls.setAttribute("onmouseover","expose(evt,'"+idPrefix+idFrame+"',true)");
6923 		gls.setAttribute("onmouseout","expose(evt,'"+idPrefix+idFrame+"',false)");
6924 		//These attributes don't apply to a <path>, but they feed the grid functions
6925 		gls.setAttribute("x",x);
6926 		gls.setAttribute("y",(segType == "F" ? pC.y - r : y));
6927 		gls.setAttribute("width",w);
6928 		gls.setAttribute("height",
6929 			(segType == "F" ? iLB.y - (pC.y - r)
6930 							: iLB.y - Math.min(iLT.y,iRT.y)));
6931 		
6932 		
6933 		grp.appendChild(gls);
6934 	}
6935 
6936 	var t,tText;
6937 	if(g("f_glass") == "TEMPERED")
6938 	{
6939 	trace("creating T");
6940 		t = drawing.getElementById(id+"_pane_t");
6941 		if(t === null)
6942 		{
6943 			t = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"text");
6944 			t.setAttribute("id",id+"_pane_t");
6945 			t.setAttribute("class","glass");
6946    			tText = drawing.createTextNode("T");
6947     		t.appendChild(tText);
6948 			grp.appendChild(t);			
6949 		}
6950 		t.setAttribute("x",x+w-(g("f_um")=="mm"?inchesToMM(2):2));
6951 		t.setAttribute("y",y+h-(g("f_um")=="mm"?inchesToMM(2):2));
6952 	}
6953 
6954 
6955 		try
6956 		{
6957 			trace("d="+d);
6958 			gls.setAttribute("d",d);
6959 		}
6960 		catch(e){alert(id + "_arch d="+d);}
6961 		createDescription(id , "Arch WIDTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w) +"  HEIGHT: " + inchesToInchesDim(h) + "  HEIGHT LEGS: " + inchesToInchesDim(hLegs) +  "  RADIUS: "+inchesToInchesDim(r)+".");
6962 
6963 
6964 
6965 }	
6966 catch(e)
6967 {
6968 	alertUser("Exception:  initGlassArchCircularSeg'"+id+"',("+pLT.x+","+ pLT.y+"),("+pRT.x+","+ pRT.y+"),("+pLB.x+","+ pLB.y+"),("+pRB.x+","+ pRB.y+"',("+pC.x+","+ pC.y+"),"+ r+","+ inset+")");
6969 	alertUser(e);
6970 	trace(e);
6971 }
6972 }

6990 
6991 /**
6992  * Draw a horizontal segment of a radial glass.
6993  * 
6994  * @param id		String id
6995  * @param idFrame	String id of containing frame
6996  * @param pLT		Point left top
6997  * @param pRT		Point right top
6998  * @param pLB		Point left bottom
6999  * @param pRB		Point right bottom
7000  * @param pC		Point center of the arc
7001  * @param r			decimal radius of the arc
7002  * @param inset		inset inside the frame
7003  * @return
7004  */
7005 
7006 function initArchCircularSeg(id, pLT, pRT, pLB, pRB, pC, r, inset, color)
7007 {
7008 // segType: F=full, L=left half, R=right half
7009 try
7010 {
7011 trace("initArchCircularSeg'"+id+"',("+pLT.x+","+ pLT.y+"),("+pRT.x+","+ pRT.y+"),("+pLB.x+","+ pLB.y+"),("+pRB.x+","+ pRB.y+"',("+pC.x+","+ pC.y+"),"+ r+","+ inset+",'"+ color+"')");
7012 
7013 	var x = pLT.x;
7014 	var y = Math.min(pLT.y,pRT.y);
7015 	var w = pRT.x-pLT.x;
7016 	
7017 	var yBase = Math.max(pLT.y,pRT.y);
7018 	var segType = "F";
7019 	if(pLT.y < pRT.y)
7020 	{
7021 		segType = "R";
7022 	}
7023 	else
7024 	if(pLT.y > pRT.y)
7025 	{
7026 		segType = "L";
7027 	}
7028 	
7029 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id);
7030 	if(grp === null)
7031 	{
7032 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
7033 		grp.setAttribute("id",id);
7034 		
7035 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
7036 	}
7037 	var hLegs = pLB.y - Math.max(pLT.y,pRT.y);
7038 	
7039 	var iLT,iRT,iLB,iRB;
7040 	
7041 
7042 
7043 	var d = null;
7044 	var dSill = null;
7045 	var dLeft = null;
7046 	var dRight = null;
7047 	var angleSill = null;
7048 	var	rInner = r - inset;
7049 	trace("rInner="+rInner);	
7050 	if(hLegs === 0)
7051 	{
7052 		switch(segType)
7053 		{
7054 			case "F":
7055 				iLT = new Point( pC.x - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.y-pLT.y+inset,2)),
7056 								pLT.y - inset);
7057 				iRT = new Point(pC.x + Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.y-pRT.y+inset,2)),
7058 								pLT.y - inset);	
7059 				
7060 			
7061 				d =  "M " + pLT.x + "," + pLT.y + " A " + r+","+r+" 0 0,1 " +pRT.x+","+pRT.y +
7062 					" L " + iRT.x+","+iRT.y +
7063 					" A "+rInner+","+rInner+" 180 0,0 "+ iLT.x+","+iLT.y +
7064 					" L " + pLT.x +","+ pLT.y;
7065 				trace(">>>> d = " + d);
7066 				dSill = "M " +pLT.x+","+pLT.y +
7067 						" L " + pRT.x+","+pRT.y +
7068 						" L " + iRT.x+","+iRT.y +
7069 						" L " + iLT.x+","+iLT.y +
7070 						" L " +pLT.x+"," +pLT.y;	
7071 				angleSill = Math.atan2(pLT.y-iLT.y,iLT.x-pLT.x);
7072 
7073 				trace(">>>> dSill = " + dSill);		
7074 				break;
7075 			case "L":
7076 				iLT = new Point( pC.x - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.y-(pLT.y-inset),2)),
7077 								pLT.y - inset);
7078 				iRT = new Point( pRT.x - inset,
7079 								pC.y == pRT.y ? pC.y :
7080 								pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(inset,2)));
7081 				iRB = new Point(pRB.x-inset,pRB.y-inset);
7082 				d =  "M " + pLT.x + "," + pLT.y + " A " + r+","+r+" 0 0,1 " +pRT.x+","+pRT.y +
7083 					" L " + iRT.x+","+iRT.y +
7084 					" A "+rInner+","+rInner+" 180 0,0 "+ iLT.x+","+iLT.y +
7085 					" L " + pLT.x +","+ pLT.y;
7086 				dRight = "M "+ pRT.x+","+pRT.y+
7087 						" L "+pRB.x+","+pRB.y+
7088 						" L "+iRB.x+","+iRB.y+
7089 						" L "+iRT.x+","+iRT.y+
7090 						" L	"+pRT.x+","+pRT.y;
7091 				dSill = "M " +pLT.x+","+pLT.y +
7092 						" L " + pRB.x+","+pRB.y +
7093 						" L " + iRB.x+","+iRB.y +
7094 						" L " + iLT.x+","+iLT.y +
7095 						" L " +pLT.x+"," +pLT.y;	
7096 				angleSill = Math.atan2(pLT.y-iLT.y,iLT.x-pLT.x);
7097 						
7098 				break;
7099 			case "R":
7100 				iLT = new Point( pLT.x + inset,
7101 								pC.y == pLT.y ? pC.y :
7102 								pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(inset,2)));
7103 				
7104 				iRT = new Point(pC.x + Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.y-(pRT.y-inset),2)),
7105 								pRT.y - inset);	
7106 				
7107 								
7108 				iLB = new Point(pLB.x+inset,pLB.y-inset);
7109 				d =  "M " + pLT.x + "," + pLT.y + " A " + r+","+r+" 0 0,1 " +pRT.x+","+pRT.y +
7110 					" L " + iRT.x+","+iRT.y +
7111 					" A "+rInner+","+rInner+" 180 0,0 "+ iLT.x+","+iLT.y +
7112 					" L " + pLT.x +","+ pLT.y;
7113 				dLeft = "M "+ pLT.x+","+pLT.y+
7114 						" L "+pLB.x+","+pLB.y+
7115 						" L "+iLB.x+","+iLB.y+
7116 						" L "+iLT.x+","+iLT.y+
7117 						" L	"+pLT.x+","+pLT.y;
7118 				dSill = "M " +pLB.x+","+pLB.y +
7119 						" L " + pRT.x+","+pRT.y +
7120 						" L " + iRT.x+","+iRT.y +
7121 						" L " + iLB.x+","+iLB.y +
7122 						" L " +pLB.x+"," +pLB.y;	
7123 				
7124 				angleSill = Math.atan2(pRT.y-iRT.y,pRT.x-iRT.x);
7125 						
7126 				break;
7127 			default:
7128 				break;	
7129 		}
7130 	}
7131 	
7132 	else
7133 	if(hLegs > 0 && hLegs <= inset )
7134 	{
7135 		switch(segType)
7136 		{
7137 			case "F":
7138 				iLT = new Point( pC.x - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.y-(pLT.y-inset),2)),
7139 								pLT.y - inset);
7140 				iRT = new Point(pC.x + Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.y-(pRT.y-inset),2)),
7141 								pLT.y - inset);	
7142 				
7143 			
7144 				d =  "M " + pLT.x + "," + (pLT.y + (inset-hLegs)) +
7145 					" L " + pLT.x + "," + pLT.y + 
7146 					" A " + r+","+r+" 0 0,1 " +pRT.x+","+pRT.y +
7147 					" L " + pRT.x + "," + (pRT.y + (inset-hLegs)) +
7148 					" L " + iRT.x+","+(iRT.y + (inset-hLegs)) +
7149 					" L " + iRT.x+","+iRT.y + 
7150 					" A "+rInner+","+rInner+" 180 0,0 "+ iLT.x+","+iLT.y +
7151 					" L " + iLT.x+","+(iLT.y + (inset-hLegs))+
7152 					" L " + pLT.x +","+ (pLT.y + (inset-hLegs));
7153 				dSill = "M " +pLT.x+","+(pLT.y + (inset-hLegs))+
7154 						" L " + pRT.x+","+(pRT.y + (inset-hLegs))+
7155 						" L " + iRT.x+","+ (iRT.y + (inset-hLegs)) +
7156 						" L " + iLT.x+","+(iLT.y + (inset-hLegs))+
7157 						" L " +pLT.x+"," +(pLT.y + (inset-hLegs));	
7158 				
7159 				angleSill = Math.atan2((pLT.y + (inset-hLegs))-(iLT.y + (inset-hLegs)),pLT.x-iLT.x);
7160 						
7161 				break;
7162 			case "L":
7163 				iLT = new Point( pC.x - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.y-(pLT.y-inset),2)),
7164 								pLT.y - inset);
7165 				iRT = new Point( pRT.x - inset,
7166 								pC.y == pRT.y ? pC.y :
7167 								pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(inset,2)));
7168 				iRB = new Point(pRB.x-inset,pRB.y-inset);
7169 				d =  "M " + pLT.x + "," + pLT.y + " A " + r+","+r+" 0 0,1 " +pRT.x+","+pRT.y +
7170 					" L " + iRT.x+","+iRT.y +
7171 					" A "+rInner+","+rInner+" 180 0,0 "+ iLT.x+","+iLT.y +
7172 					" L " + pLT.x +","+ pLT.y;
7173 				dRight = "M "+ pRT.x+","+pRT.y+
7174 						" L "+pRB.x+","+pRB.y+
7175 						" L "+iRB.x+","+iRB.y+
7176 						" L "+iRT.x+","+iRT.y+
7177 						" L	"+pRT.x+","+pRT.y;
7178 				dSill = "M " +pLT.x+","+pLT.y +
7179 						" L " + pRB.x+","+pRB.y +
7180 						" L " + iRB.x+","+iRB.y +
7181 						" L " + iLT.x+","+iLT.y +
7182 						" L " +pLT.x+"," +pLT.y;	
7183 				angleSill = Math.atan2((pLT.y + (inset-hLegs))-(iLT.y + (inset-hLegs)),pLT.x-iLT.x);
7184 						
7185 				break;
7186 			case "R":
7187 				iLT = new Point( pLT.x + inset,
7188 								pC.y == pLT.y ? pC.y :
7189 								pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(inset,2)));
7190 				
7191 				iRT = new Point( pC.x + Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.y-(pRT.y-inset),2)),
7192 								pRT.y - inset);
7193 								
7194 				iLB = new Point(pLB.x+inset,pLB.y-inset);
7195 				d =  "M " + pLT.x + "," + pLT.y + " A " + r+","+r+" 0 0,1 " +pRT.x+","+pRT.y +
7196 					" L " + iRT.x+","+iRT.y +
7197 					" A "+rInner+","+rInner+" 180 0,0 "+ iLT.x+","+iLT.y +
7198 					" L " + pLT.x +","+ pLT.y;
7199 				dLeft = "M "+ pLT.x+","+pLT.y+
7200 						" L "+pLB.x+","+pLB.y+
7201 						" L "+iLB.x+","+iLB.y+
7202 						" L "+iLT.x+","+iLT.y+
7203 						" L	"+pLT.x+","+pLT.y;
7204 				dSill = "M " +pLB.x+","+pLB.y +
7205 						" L " + pRT.x+","+pRT.y +
7206 						" L " + iRT.x+","+iRT.y +
7207 						" L " + iLB.x+","+iLB.y +
7208 						" L " +pLB.x+"," +pLB.y;	
7209 				
7210 				angleSill = Math.atan2((pRT.y + (inset-hLegs))-(iRT.y + (inset-hLegs)),pRT.x-iRT.x);
7211 				
7212 				break;
7213 			default:
7214 				break;	
7215 		}
7216 	}
7217 	else
7218 	{
7219 		angleSill = .125 * Math.PI;
7220 		switch(segType)
7221 		{
7222 			case "F":
7223 				iLT = new Point( pLT.x+inset,
7224 									pC.y == pLT.y ? pC.y :
7225 								 	pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.x-(pLT.x+inset),2)));
7226 				iRT = new Point( pRT.x - inset,
7227 								pC.y == pRT.y ? pC.y :
7228 								pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pRT.x-inset-pC.x,2)));
7229 				iLB = new Point( pLB.x+inset,pLB.y-inset);
7230 				iRB = new Point( pRB.x-inset,pLB.y-inset);
7231 				break;
7232 				
7233 			case "L":
7234 				trace("pC.y="+pC.y);
7235 				trace("pC.x="+pC.x);
7236 				trace("pLT.x="+pLT.x);
7237 				trace("pLT.y="+pLT.y);
7238 				iLT = new Point( pLT.x+inset,
7239 									pC.y == pLT.y ? pC.y :
7240 								 	pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.x-pLT.x-inset,2)));
7241 				iRT = new Point( pRT.x - inset,
7242 								pC.y == pRT.y ? pC.y :
7243 								pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.x-(pRT.x-inset),2)));
7244 				iRB = new Point(pRB.x-inset,pRB.y-inset);
7245 				iLB = new Point(pLB.x+inset,pRB.y-inset);
7246 				break;
7247 			case "R":
7248 				trace("pC.y="+pC.y);
7249 				trace("pC.x="+pC.x);
7250 				trace("pLT.x="+pLT.x);
7251 				trace("pLT.y="+pLT.y);
7252 			
7253 				iLT = new Point( pLT.x + inset,
7254 								pC.y == pLT.y ? pC.y :
7255 								pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.x-pLT.x-inset,2)));
7256 				
7257 				iRT = new Point( pRT.x - inset,
7258 								pC.y == pRT.y ? pC.y :
7259 								pC.y - + Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pRT.x-pC.x-inset,2)));
7260 				iRB = new Point(pRB.x-inset,pRB.y-inset);
7261 				iLB = new Point(pLB.x+inset,pLB.y-inset);
7262 				break;
7263 			default:
7264 				break;	
7265 				
7266 		}
7267 				d =  "M " + pLT.x + "," + pLT.y + " A " + r+","+r+" 0 0,1 " +pRT.x+","+pRT.y +
7268 					" L " + iRT.x+","+iRT.y +
7269 					" A "+rInner+","+rInner+" 180 0,0 "+ iLT.x+","+iLT.y +
7270 					" L " + pLT.x +","+ pLT.y;
7271 				
7272 				dLeft = "M "+ pLT.x+","+pLT.y+
7273 						" L "+pLB.x+","+pLB.y+
7274 						" L "+iLB.x+","+iLB.y+
7275 						" L "+iLT.x+","+iLT.y+
7276 						" L	"+pLT.x+","+pLT.y;
7277 				dRight = "M "+pRT.x+","+pRT.y+
7278 						" L "+pRB.x+","+pRB.y+
7279 						" L "+iRB.x+","+iRB.y+
7280 						" L "+iRT.x+","+iRT.y+
7281 						" L	"+pRT.x+","+pRT.y;
7282 				dSill = "M " +pLB.x+","+pLB.y +
7283 						" L " + pRB.x+","+pRB.y +
7284 						" L " + iRB.x+","+iRB.y +
7285 						" L " + iLB.x+","+iLB.y +
7286 						" L " +pLB.x+"," +pLB.y;	
7287 			
7288 	}
7289 	angleSill = Math.round(100*((angleSill) / Math.PI)*180)/100;
7290 	
7291 	var archCircumference = Math.abs(Math.atan2(pC.x-pLT.x, pC.y-pLT.y) - Math.atan2(pC.x-pRT.x, pC.y-pRT.y))*R;		
7292 	
7293   
7294 		var arch = drawing.getElementById(id + "_arch");
7295 		if(arch === null && d != null)
7296 		{
7297 			arch = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
7298 			arch.setAttribute("id",id+"_arch");
7299 			arch.setAttribute("class","frame");
7300 			grp.appendChild(arch);
7301 		}
7302 		
7303 		
7304 		try
7305 		{
7306 			trace("d="+d);
7307 			arch.setAttribute("d",d);
7308 			arch.setAttribute("style","fill: "+color);
7309 		}
7310 		catch(e){alert(id + "_arch d="+d);}
7311 		createDescription(id + "_arch", "ARCH WIDTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w) + "    LENGTH: " +inchesToInchesDim(archCircumference)+"  OUTER RADIUS: "+inchesToInchesDim(r)+".");
7312 
7313 
7314 		var bottomRail;
7315 		if(dSill !== null)
7316 		{
7317 			bottomRail = drawing.getElementById(id + "_bottom_rail");
7318 			if(bottomRail === null)
7319 			{
7320 				bottomRail = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
7321 				bottomRail.setAttribute("id",id+"_bottom_rail");
7322 				bottomRail.setAttribute("class","frame");
7323 				grp.appendChild(bottomRail);
7324 			}
7325 			try
7326 			{
7327 				trace("d="+dSill);
7328 				bottomRail.setAttribute("d",dSill);
7329 				bottomRail.setAttribute("style","fill: "+color);
7330 			}
7331 			catch(e){alert(id + "_bottom_rail d="+dSill);}
7332 			trace("pLB.x="+pLB.x);
7333 			trace("pRB.x="+pRB.x);
7334 			createDescription(id + "_bottom_rail", "SILL WIDTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(pRB.x-pLB.x) + "  THICKNESS: "+inchesToInchesDim(inset)+"  MITRE: " + angleSill + " .");
7335 			
7336 		}	
7337 		
7338 		var leftRail;
7339 		if(dLeft !== null)
7340 		{
7341 			leftRail = drawing.getElementById(id + "_left_rail");
7342 			if(leftRail === null)
7343 			{
7344 				leftRail = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
7345 				leftRail.setAttribute("id",id+"_left_rail");
7346 				leftRail.setAttribute("class","frame");
7347 				grp.appendChild(leftRail);
7348 			}
7349 			try
7350 			{
7351 				trace("d="+dLeft);
7352 				leftRail.setAttribute("d",dLeft);
7353 				leftRail.setAttribute("style","fill: "+color);
7354 			}
7355 			catch(e){alert(id + "_left_rail d="+dSill);}
7356 			createDescription(id + "_left_rail", "LEFT RAIL LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(pLB.y-pLT.y) + "  THICKNESS: "+inchesToInchesDim(inset)+".");
7357 			
7358 		}	
7359 
7360 		var rightRail;
7361 		if(dRight !== null)
7362 		{
7363 			rightRail = drawing.getElementById(id + "_right_rail");
7364 			if(rightRail === null && dRight != null)
7365 			{
7366 				rightRail = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
7367 				rightRail.setAttribute("id",id+"_right_rail");
7368 				rightRail.setAttribute("class","frame");
7369 				grp.appendChild(rightRail);
7370 			}
7371

7376 				rightRail.setAttribute("style","fill: "+color);
7377 			}
7378 			catch(e){alert(id + "_right_rail d="+dSill);}
7379 			createDescription(id + "_right_rail", "RIGHT RAIL LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(pRB.y-pRT.y) + "  THICKNESS: "+inchesToInchesDim(inset)+".");
7380 		}
7381 	
7382 
7383 }	
7384 catch(e)
7385 {
7386 	alertUser("Exception:  initArchCircularSeg'"+id+"',("+pLT.x+","+ pLT.y+"),("+pRT.x+","+ pRT.y+"),("+pLB.x+","+ pLB.y+"),("+pRB.x+","+ pRB.y+"',("+pC.x+","+ pC.y+"),"+ r+","+ inset+",'"+ color+"')");
7387 	alertUser(e);
7388 	trace(e);
7389 }
7390 }

7395 /**
7396  * Draw a horizontal segment of a radial frame with a square base (i.e. sill)
7397  * 
7398  * 
7399  * @param id		String id
7400   * @param pLT		Point left top
7401  * @param pRT		Point right top
7402  * @param pLB		Point left bottom
7403  * @param pRB		Point right bottom
7404  * @param pC		Point center of the arc
7405  * @param r			decimal radius of the arc
7406  * @param inset		frame thickness
7407  * @param sill 		sill thinkness
7408  * @param color		frame flll color
7409  * @return
7410  */
7411 
7412 function initArchCircularSegWithSill(id, pLT, pRT, pLB, pRB, pC, r, inset, sill, color)
7413 {
7414 // segType: F=full, L=left half, R=right half
7415 try
7416 {
7417 trace("initArchCircularSegWithSill'"+id+"',("+pLT.x+","+ pLT.y+"),("+pRT.x+","+ pRT.y+"),("+pLB.x+","+ pLB.y+"),("+pRB.x+","+ pRB.y+"',("+pC.x+","+ pC.y+"),"+ r+","+ inset+","+ sill+",'"+ color+"')");
7418 
7419 	var x = pLT.x;
7420 	var y = Math.min(pLT.y,pRT.y);
7421 	var w = pRT.x-pLT.x;
7422 	
7423 	var yBase = Math.max(pLT.y,pRT.y);
7424 	var segType = "F";
7425 	if(pLT.y < pRT.y)
7426 	{
7427 		segType = "R";
7428 	}
7429 	else
7430 	if(pLT.y > pRT.y)
7431 	{
7432 		segType = "L";
7433 	}
7434 	
7435 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id);
7436 	if(grp === null)
7437 	{
7438 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
7439 		grp.setAttribute("id",id);
7440 		
7441 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
7442 	}
7443 	var hLegs = pLB.y - Math.max(pLT.y,pRT.y);
7444 	
7445 	var iLT,iRT,iLB,iRB;
7446 	
7447 
7448 
7449 	var d = null;
7450 	var dSill = null;
7451 	var dLeft = null;
7452 	var dRight = null;
7453 	
7454 	var	rInner = r - inset;
7455 		
7456 	if(hLegs === 0)
7457 	{
7458 		switch(segType)
7459 		{
7460 			case "F":
7461 				iLT = new Point( pC.x - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.y-pLT.y,2)),
7462 								pLT.y);
7463 				iRT = new Point(pC.x + Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pRT.y-pC.y,2)),
7464 								pLT.y);	
7465 				
7466 			
7467 				d =  "M " + pLT.x + "," + pLT.y + " A " + r+","+r+" 0 0,1 " +pRT.x+","+pRT.y +
7468 					" L " + iRT.x+","+iRT.y +
7469 					" A "+rInner+","+rInner+" 180 0,0 "+ iLT.x+","+iLT.y +
7470 					" L " + pLT.x +","+ pLT.y;
7471 				dSill = "M " +pLT.x+","+(pLT.y+sill) +
7472 						" L " + pRT.x+","+(pRT.y+sill) +
7473 						" L " + pRT.x+","+pRT.y +
7474 						" L " + pLT.x+","+pLT.y +
7475 						" L " +pLT.x+"," +(pLT.y+sill);	
7476 						
7477 				break;
7478 			case "L":
7479 				iLT = new Point( pC.x - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.y-pLT.y,2)),
7480 								pLT.y);
7481 				iRT = new Point( pRT.x - inset,
7482 								pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(inset,2)));
7483 				iRB = new Point(pRB.x-inset,pRB.y);
7484 				d =  "M " + pLT.x + "," + pLT.y + " A " + r+","+r+" 0 0,1 " +pRT.x+","+pRT.y +
7485 					" L " + iRT.x+","+iRT.y +
7486 					" A "+rInner+","+rInner+" 180 0,0 "+ iLT.x+","+iLT.y +
7487 					" L " + pLT.x +","+ pLT.y;
7488 				dRight = "M "+ pRT.x+","+pRT.y+
7489 						" L "+pRB.x+","+pRB.y+
7490 						" L "+iRB.x+","+iRB.y+
7491 						" L "+iRT.x+","+iRT.y+
7492 						" L	"+pRT.x+","+pRT.y;
7493 				dSill = "M " +pLT.x+","+(pLT.y+sill) +
7494 						" L " + pRB.x+","+(pRB.y+sill) +
7495 						" L " + pRB.x+","+pRB.y +
7496 						" L " + pLT.x+","+pLT.y +
7497 						" L " +pLT.x+"," +(pLT.y+sill);	
7498 						
7499 				break;
7500 			case "R":
7501 				iLT = new Point( pLT.x + inset,
7502 								pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(inset,2)));
7503 				
7504 				iRT = new Point( pC.x + Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.y-pRT.y,2)),
7505 								pRT.y);
7506 								
7507 				iLB = new Point(pLB.x+inset,pLB.y);
7508 				d =  "M " + pLT.x + "," + pLT.y + " A " + r+","+r+" 0 0,1 " +pRT.x+","+pRT.y +
7509 					" L " + iRT.x+","+iRT.y +
7510 					" A "+rInner+","+rInner+" 180 0,0 "+ iLT.x+","+iLT.y +
7511 					" L " + pLT.x +","+ pLT.y;
7512 				dLeft = "M "+ pLT.x+","+pLT.y+
7513 						" L "+pLB.x+","+pLB.y+
7514 						" L "+iLB.x+","+iLB.y+
7515 						" L "+iLT.x+","+iLT.y+
7516 						" L	"+pLT.x+","+pLT.y;
7517 				dSill = "M " +pLB.x+","+(pLB.y+sill) +
7518 						" L " + pRT.x+","+(pRT.y+sill) +
7519 						" L " + pRT.x+","+pRT.y +
7520 						" L " + pLB.x+","+pLB.y +
7521 						" L " +pLB.x+"," +(pLB.y+sill);	
7522 				break;
7523 			default:
7524 				break;	
7525 		}
7526 	}
7527 	else
7528 	{
7529 		switch(segType)
7530 		{
7531 			case "F":
7532 				iLT = new Point( pLT.x+inset,
7533 									pC.y == pLT.y ? pC.y :
7534 								 	pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.x-(pLT.x+inset),2)));
7535 				iRT = new Point( pRT.x - inset,
7536 								pC.y == pRT.y ? pC.y :
7537 								pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pRT.x-inset-pC.x,2)));
7538 				iLB = new Point( pLB.x+inset,pLB.y);
7539 				iRB = new Point( pRB.x-inset,pLB.y);
7540 				break;
7541 				
7542 			case "L":
7543 				iLT = new Point( pLT.x+inset,
7544 								 pC.y == pLT.y ? pC.y :
7545 								 pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pC.x-pLT.x-inset,2)));
7546 				iRT = new Point( pRT.x - inset,
7547 								pC.y == pRT.y ? pC.y :
7548 								pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(inset,2)));
7549 				iRB = new Point(pRB.x-inset,pRB.y);
7550 				iLB = new Point(pLB.x+inset,pRB.y);
7551 				break;
7552 			case "R":
7553 				iLT = new Point( pLT.x + inset,
7554 								pC.y == pLT.y ? pC.y :
7555 								pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(inset,2)));
7556 				
7557 				iRT = new Point( pRT.x - inset,
7558 								pC.y == pRT.y ? pC.y :
7559 								pC.y - Math.sqrt(Math.pow(rInner,2)-Math.pow(pRT.x-inset-pC.x,2)));
7560 				iRB = new Point(pRB.x-inset,pRB.y);
7561 				iLB = new Point(pLB.x+inset,pLB.y);
7562 				break;
7563 			default:
7564 				break;	
7565 				
7566 		}
7567 				d =  "M " + pLT.x + "," + pLT.y + " A " + r+","+r+" 0 0,1 " +pRT.x+","+pRT.y +
7568 					" L " + iRT.x+","+iRT.y +
7569 					" A "+rInner+","+rInner+" 180 0,0 "+ iLT.x+","+iLT.y +
7570 					" L " + pLT.x +","+ pLT.y;
7571 				
7572 				dLeft = "M "+ pLT.x+","+pLT.y+
7573 						" L "+pLB.x+","+pLB.y+
7574 						" L "+iLB.x+","+iLB.y+
7575 						" L "+iLT.x+","+iLT.y+
7576 						" L	"+pLT.x+","+pLT.y;
7577 				dRight = "M "+pRT.x+","+pRT.y+
7578 						" L "+pRB.x+","+pRB.y+
7579 						" L "+iRB.x+","+iRB.y+
7580 						" L "+iRT.x+","+iRT.y+
7581 						" L	"+pRT.x+","+pRT.y;
7582 				dSill = "M " +pLB.x+","+(pLB.y+sill) +
7583 						" L " + pRB.x+","+(pRB.y+sill) +
7584 						" L " + pRB.x+","+pRB.y +
7585 						" L " + pLB.x+","+pLB.y +
7586 						" L " +pLB.x+"," +(pLB.y+sill);	
7587 			
7588 	}
7589 	var archCircumference = Math.abs(Math.atan2(pC.x-pLT.x, pC.y-pLT.y) - Math.atan2(pC.x-pRT.x, pC.y-pRT.y))*R;		
7590 	
7591   
7592 		var arch = drawing.getElementById(id + "_arch");
7593 		if(arch === null && d != null)
7594 		{
7595 			arch = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
7596 			arch.setAttribute("id",id+"_arch");
7597 			arch.setAttribute("class","frame");
7598 			grp.appendChild(arch);
7599 		}
7600 		
7601 		
7602 		try
7603 		{
7604 			trace("d="+d);
7605 			arch.setAttribute("d",d);
7606 			arch.setAttribute("style","fill: "+color);
7607 		}
7608 		catch(e){alert(id + "_arch d="+d);}
7609 		createDescription(id + "_arch", "ARCH WIDTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w) + "    LENGTH: " +inchesToInchesDim(archCircumference)+"  OUTER RADIUS: "+inchesToInchesDim(r)+".");
7610 
7611 
7612 		var bottomRail;
7613 		if(dSill !== null)
7614 		{
7615 			bottomRail = drawing.getElementById(id + "_sill");
7616 			if(bottomRail === null)
7617 			{
7618 				bottomRail = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
7619 				bottomRail.setAttribute("id",id+"_sill");
7620 				bottomRail.setAttribute("class","frame");
7621 				grp.appendChild(bottomRail);
7622 			}
7623 			try
7624 			{
7625 				trace("d="+dSill);
7626 				bottomRail.setAttribute("d",dSill);
7627 				bottomRail.setAttribute("style","fill: "+color);
7628 			}
7629 			catch(e){alert(id + "_sill d="+dSill);}
7630 			createDescription(id + "_sill", "SILL LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(pRB.x-pLB.x) + "  THICKNESS: "+inchesToInchesDim(sill)+ ".");
7631 			
7632 		}	
7633 		
7634 		var leftRail;
7635 		if(dLeft !== null)
7636 		{
7637 			leftRail = drawing.getElementById(id + "_left_rail");
7638 			if(leftRail === null)
7639 			{
7640 				leftRail = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
7641 				leftRail.setAttribute("id",id+"_left_rail");
7642 				leftRail.setAttribute("class","frame");
7643 				grp.appendChild(leftRail);
7644 			}
7645 			try
7646 			{
7647 				trace("d="+dLeft);
7648 				leftRail.setAttribute("d",dLeft);
7649 				leftRail.setAttribute("style","fill: "+color);
7650 			}
7651 			catch(e){alert(id + "_left_rail d="+dSill);}
7652 			createDescription(id + "_left_rail", "LEFT RAIL LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(pLB.y-pLT.y) + "  THICKNESS: "+inchesToInchesDim(inset)+".");
7653 			
7654 		}	
7655 
7656 		var rightRail;
7657 		if(dRight !== null)
7658 		{
7659 			rightRail = drawing.getElementById(id + "_right_rail");
7660 			if(rightRail === null && dRight != null)
7661 			{
7662 				rightRail = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
7663 				rightRail.setAttribute("id",id+"_right_rail");
7664 				rightRail.setAttribute("class","frame");
7665 				grp.appendChild(rightRail);
7666 			}
7667 
7668 			try
7669 			{
7670 				trace("d="+dRight);
7671 				rightRail.setAttribute("d",dRight);
7672 				rightRail.setAttribute("style","fill: "+color);
7673 			}
7674 			catch(e){alert(id + "_right_rail d="+dSill);}
7675 			createDescription(id + "_right_rail", "RIGHT RAIL LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(pRB.y-pRT.y) + "  THICKNESS: "+inchesToInchesDim(inset)+".");
7676 		}
7677 	
7678 
7679 }	
7680 catch(e)
7681 {
7682 	alertUser("Exception: initArchCircularSegWithSill'"+id+"',("+pLT.x+","+ pLT.y+"),("+pRT.x+","+ pRT.y+"),("+pLB.x+","+ pLB.y+"),("+pRB.x+","+ pRB.y+"',("+pC.x+","+ pC.y+"),"+ r+","+ inset+","+ sill+",'"+ color+"')");
7683 	alertUser(e);
7684 	trace(e);
7685 }
7686 }

7691 
7692 /**
7693  * Draw an arch grille pattern
7694  * 
7695  * @param id			String id of grille group
7696  * @param glass_x		decimal x coordinate of rectangle encompassing the glass 
7697  * @param glass_y		decimal y coordinate of rectangle encompassing the glass
7698  * @param glass_w		decimal width of rectangle encompassing the glass
7699  * @param glass_h		decimal height of rectangle encompassing the glass
7700  * @param leg_h			decimal leg height
7701  * @param inset			decimal inset from the containing frame
7702  * @param grid_pattern	String grid pattern
7703  * @param thk			decimal thickness of grille element 
7704  * @param color			String web color of grille
7705  * @param segParm		char F=full, L=left qtr-round, R=right qtr-round
7706  * @return
7707  */
7708 
7709 function initArchGrille(id, glass_x,glass_y,glass_w,glass_h, leg_h, inset, grid_pattern, thk, color,segParm)
7710 {
7711 // segType: F=full, L=left half, R=right half
7712 
7713 	trace("initArchGrille('"+id+"',"+ glass_x+","+glass_y+","+glass_w+","+glass_h+","+leg_h+","+","+inset+","+ grid_pattern+"',"+ thk+",'"+ color+"','"+ segParm+"')");
7714 try{
7715 	var segType = segParm === null ? 'F':segParm;
7716 	var arches = 0;
7717 	var spokes = 0;
7718 	var iSpokes = 0;
7719 	var hBars = 0;
7720 	var ix = 0;
7721 	switch(grid_pattern.charAt(0))
7722 	{
7723 		case 'A':
7724 				arches = grid_pattern.charAt(1) - 0;
7725 				ix = grid_pattern.indexOf('T');
7726 				if(ix!=-1)
7727 				{
7728 					iSpokes = grid_pattern.charAt(ix+1) - 0;
7729 				}
7730 				ix = grid_pattern.indexOf('S');
7731 				if(ix!=-1)
7732 				{
7733 					spokes = grid_pattern.charAt(ix+1) - 0;
7734 				}
7735 				ix = grid_pattern.indexOf('H');
7736 				if(ix!=-1)
7737 				{
7738 					hBars = grid_pattern.charAt(ix+1) - 0;
7739 				}
7740 				
7741 
7742 				
7743 				
7744 				break;
7745 		case 'S':
7746 				spokes = grid_pattern.charAt(1) - 0;
7747 				ix = grid_pattern.indexOf('A');
7748 				if(ix!=-1)
7749 				{
7750 					arches = grid_pattern.charAt(ix+1) - 0;
7751 				}
7752 				ix = grid_pattern.indexOf('T');
7753 				if(ix!=-1)
7754 				{
7755 					iSpokes = grid_pattern.charAt(ix+1) - 0;
7756 				}
7757 
7758 				if(arches === 0)
7759 				{
7760 					iSpokes = spokes;
7761 					spokes = 0;
7762 				}
7763 				ix = grid_pattern.indexOf('H');
7764 				if(ix!=-1)
7765 				{
7766 					hBars = grid_pattern.charAt(ix+1) - 0;
7767 				}
7768 				break;
7769 
7770 		case 'G':
7771 				spokes = grid_pattern.charAt(1) - 0;
7772 				ix = grid_pattern.indexOf('H');
7773 				if(ix!=-1)
7774 				{
7775 					hBars = grid_pattern.charAt(ix+1) - 0;
7776 				}
7777 				
7778 				drawGothicGrille(id, glass_x,glass_y,glass_w,glass_h, leg_h, hBars, inset, spokes, thk, color, segType, false);
7779 				return;
7780 		
7781 		case 'H':  // segmented hub
7782 				hBars = grid_pattern.charAt(1) - 0;
7783 				ix = grid_pattern.indexOf('S');
7784 				if(ix!=-1)
7785 				{
7786 					spokes = grid_pattern.charAt(ix+1) - 0;
7787 				}
7788 				drawSegHubGrille(id, glass_x,glass_y,glass_w,glass_h, leg_h, inset, spokes, hBars, thk, color, false);
7789 				return;
7790 		 
7791 		 
7792 		default:
7793 				break;
7794 	}
7795 	
7796 	var scalloped = grid_pattern.indexOf('C') != -1;
7797 
7798 	drawArchGrille(id, glass_x,glass_y,glass_w,glass_h, leg_h, hBars, inset, arches, spokes, iSpokes, scalloped, thk, color, segType, false);
7799 
7800 }	
7801 catch(e)
7802 {
7803 	alertUser("Exception: initArchGrille('"+id+"',"+ glass_x+","+glass_y+","+glass_w+","+glass_h+","+leg_h+",'"+inset+",'"+ grid_pattern+"',"+ thk+",'"+ color+"','"+ segParm+"')");
7804 	alertUser(e);
7805 	trace(e);
7806 }
7807 }
7808 
7809 
7810 /**
7811  * Draw arch grille
7812  * 
7813  * @param id 			String id
7814  * @param glass_xP		decimal x coordinate of the glass rectangle
7815  * @param glass_yP		decimal y coordinate of the glass rectangle
7816  * @param glass_wP		decimal width of the glass rectangle
7817  * @param glass_hP		decimal height of the glass rectangle
7818  * @param leg_hP		decimal leg height of the glass
7819  * @param hbars			integer horizontal bars
7820  * @param inset			decimal inset from from the containing frame
7821  * @param arches		integer arches
7822  * @param spokes		integer spokes radiating from inner arch
7823  * @param iSpokes		integer spokes radiating from center
7824  * @param scalloped		boolean true/false scolloped
7825  * @param thk			decimal thickness of grille element
7826  * @param color			String web color of elements
7827  * @param segType		char	F=full,L=left qtr-round, R=right qtr-round
7828  * @param redraw		boolean redrawing
7829  * @return	void
7830  */
7831 function drawArchGrille(id, glass_xP,glass_yP,glass_wP,glass_hP, leg_hP, hbars, inset, arches, spokes, iSpokes, scalloped, thk, color,segType,redraw)
7832 {
7833 try{
7834 	trace("drawArchGrille('"+id+"'"+glass_xP+","+glass_yP+","+glass_wP+","+glass_hP+","+leg_hP+","+inset+","+ arches+","+ spokes+","+ iSpokes+","+ scalloped +","+ thk +",'"+ color+"','"+segType+"')");
7835 	var horzAdj = computeHorzOffset(segType=='F'?glass_wP:glass_wP*2,glass_hP,inset);
7836 	var glass_x = segType == 'R' ? glass_xP + inset : glass_xP + inset + horzAdj;
7837 	var glass_y = glass_yP + inset;
7838 	
7839 	var glass_w = segType == 'F' ? glass_wP - (2*(inset+horzAdj)) : glass_wP - horzAdj - (2*inset);
7840 	
7841 	var glass_h = leg_hP === 0 ? glass_hP -(2*inset) : glass_hP - inset;
7842 	var leg_h = leg_hP === 0 ? 0 : leg_hP - inset;
7843 	
7844 	var yTopBar;
7845 	var halfRound = (segType == "F" && glass_h >= (glass_w/2))
7846 					|| (segType != "F" && glass_h >= glass_w);
7847 	if(leg_h === 0 || halfRound || hbars === 0)
7848 	{
7849 		yTopBar = glass_y + glass_h;
7850 	}
7851 	else
7852 	{
7853 		yTopBar = glass_y + glass_h + (leg_h/(hbars+1));
7854 	}
7855 
7856 
7857 	if(spokes == iSpokes || iSpokes > 1)
7858 	{
7859 		spokes = 0;
7860 	}
7861 	
7862 	var splitHub = 0;
7863 	if(spokes > 0 && iSpokes == 1)
7864 	{
7865 		spokes = Math.floor(spokes/2) * 2;
7866 		spokes++;
7867 		
7868 		splitHub = Math.ceil(spokes/2);
7869 		trace("splitHub="+splitHub);
7870 	}
7871 	
7872 	var idPrefix = g("f_idprefix");
7873 
7874 	if(!redraw)
7875 	{
7876 		createClipPattern(id);
7877 	}
7878 	
7879 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id+"_grid");
7880 	if(grp === null)
7881 	{
7882 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
7883 		grp.setAttribute("id",id+"_grid");
7884 		grp.getStyle().setProperty("clip-path","url(#"+idPrefix+"clip_"+id+")","");
7885 		
7886 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
7887 	}
7888 	var gls = drawing.getElementById(id);
7889 	var shape = gls == null ? null : gls.getAttribute("shape");
7890 	if(shape == null || shape == "")
7891 	{
7892 		shape = "CIRCLEARC";
7893 	}
7894 
7895 trace("shape="+shape);
7896 
7897 	var radiusX = segType == 'F'?glass_w/2:glass_w;
7898 	var radiusY = glass_h;
7899 	var cx = segType == 'R'? glass_x : glass_x+ radiusX;
7900 	var cy = glass_y+glass_h;
7901 	
7902 	var lites,radius,radians,radianStart,radiansA1,radianStartA1;
7903 	var x,y,r;
7904 	var radialPointsOuter=null;
7905 	
7906 	switch(segType)
7907 	{
7908 		case 'F':
7909 			computeCircleCenter(glass_x,cy,cx,glass_y,glass_x+(radiusX*2),cy);
7910 			if(shape=="3CTRARC")
7911 			{
7912 				radialPointsOuter=getRadialPointsFor3CenterArc(glass_x,glass_y,glass_w,glass_h,Math.max(spokes,iSpokes),segType);
7913 			}
7914 			else
7915 			{
7916 				if(hbars>0)
7917 				{
7918 					r = Math.sqrt(Math.pow(glass_w/2,2)+Math.pow(yTopBar-glass_y,2));
7919 					radialPointsOuter=getAnglePoints(	Math.PI/2,
7920 														-Math.PI/2,
7921 														new Point(Xo,yTopBar),r,Math.max(spokes,iSpokes),
7922 														false, false);
7923 				}
7924 				else
7925 				{
7926 					radialPointsOuter=getRadialPoints(	new Point(glass_x,cy),
7927 														new Point(glass_x+glass_w,cy),												
7928 														new Point(Xo,Yo),R,Math.max(spokes,iSpokes),
7929 														false, false);
7930 				
7931 				}
7932 			}
7933 			break;
7934 		case 'L':
7935 			computeCircleCenter(glass_x,cy,cx,glass_y,glass_x+(radiusX*2),cy);
7936 			if(shape=="3CTRARC")
7937 			{
7938 				radialPointsOuter=getRadialPointsFor3CenterArc(glass_x,glass_y,glass_w/2,glass_h,Math.max(spokes,iSpokes),segType);
7939 			}
7940 			else
7941 			{
7942 				if(hbars>0)
7943 				{
7944 					r = Math.sqrt(Math.pow(glass_w,2)+Math.pow(yTopBar-glass_y,2));
7945 					radialPointsOuter=getAnglePoints(	Math.PI/2,0,
7946 													new Point(Xo,yTopBar),r,Math.max(spokes,iSpokes),
7947 													false, false);
7948 				}
7949 				else
7950 				{
7951 					radialPointsOuter=getRadialPoints(	new Point(glass_x,cy),
7952 													new Point(cx,glass_y),
7953 													new Point(Xo,yTopBar),R,Math.max(spokes,iSpokes),
7954 													false, false);
7955 				}
7956 				
7957 			}
7958 			break;
7959 		case 'R':
7960 			computeCircleCenter(glass_x-radiusX,cy,glass_x,glass_y,glass_x+radiusX,cy);
7961 			if(shape=="3CTRARC")
7962 			{
7963 				radialPointsOuter=getRadialPointsFor3CenterArc(glass_x,glass_y,glass_w/2,glass_h,Math.max(spokes,iSpokes),segType);
7964 			}
7965 			else
7966 			{
7967 				if(hbars>0)
7968 				{
7969 					r = Math.sqrt(Math.pow(glass_w,2)+Math.pow(yTopBar-glass_y,2));
7970 					radialPointsOuter=getAnglePoints(	0,-Math.PI/2,
7971 														new Point(Xo,yTopBar),r,Math.max(spokes,iSpokes),
7972 														false, false);
7973 				}
7974 				else
7975 				{
7976 					radialPointsOuter=getRadialPoints(	new Point(glass_x,glass_y),
7977 														new Point(glass_x+glass_w,cy),
7978 														new Point(Xo,Yo),R,Math.max(spokes,iSpokes),
7979 														false, false);
7980 				}
7981 				
7982 			}
7983 
7984 			break;
7985 	}
7986 
7987 	var frameArch_center = new Point(Xo,Yo);
7988 	var frameArch_radius = R;
7989 		
7990 
7991 
7992 	if(applet && !redraw)
7993 	{
7994 		var redrawScript = 	"drawArchGrille('"+id+"',"+glass_xP+","+glass_yP+","+glass_wP+","+glass_hP+","+leg_hP+","+hbars+","+inset+","+ arches+","+ spokes+","+ iSpokes+","+ scalloped +","+ thk +",'"+ color+"','"+segType+"',true)";
7995 		
7996 		applet.registerLite(idPrefix+id,glass_x+"",glass_y+"",glass_w+"",glass_h+"",redrawScript);
7997 		var elLite = drawing.getElementById(id);
7998 		if(elLite !== null)
7999 		{
8000 			elLite.setAttribute("onmousemove","dragArch(evt)");							 	
8001 			elLite.setAttribute("onmouseup","dropArch(evt)");
8002 		}							 	
8003 	}
8004 	
8005 	var archRadiusX,archRadiusY,arch,separationX,separationY,xStartArch,yStartArch,arch_id,arch_n;
8006 	
8007 	var arch1_radius = 0;
8008 	var arch1_center = new Point(cx,cy);
8009 	var arch1_width = 0;
8010 	var arch1_left = null;
8011 	var arch1_right = null;
8012 	var arch1_top = null;
8013 	
8014 	var spokeCounter = 0;
8015 	var archCircumference = 0;	
8016 	var d;
8017 	if(arches > 0)
8018 	{
8019 		
8020 		arch = 1;
8021 	
8022 		// adjust separation to account for the fact the arc
8023 		// orginates at the base of the frame, not the base of the glass.
8024 		separationX = 0;
8025 		separationY = 0;
8026 		yStartArch = yTopBar;
8027 		
8028 		if(iSpokes === 0 && spokes > 0 && arches > 0)
8029 		{ // center hub diameter == separation of outer arches
8030 			separationX = (radiusX)/((2*arches)+1);
8031 			separationY = (yTopBar-glass_y)/((2*arches)+1);
8032 		}
8033 		else
8034 		{
8035 			separationX = radiusX/(arches+1);
8036 			separationY = (yTopBar-glass_y)/(arches+1);
8037 		}
8038 		
8039 		
8040 			
8041 		for(;arch <= arches; arch++)
8042 		{
8043 			arch_id = (redraw?idPrefix+id:id)+"_arch_"+arch;
8044 			arch_n = drawing.getElementById(arch_id);
8045 			if(arch_n === null)
8046 			{
8047 				arch_n = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
8048 				arch_n.setAttribute("id",arch_id);
8049 				
8050 				arch_n.setAttribute("onmousemove","dragArch(evt)");							 	
8051 				arch_n.setAttribute("onmouseup","dropArch(evt)");
8052 				
8053 				grp.appendChild(arch_n);
8054 			}
8055 			arch_n.setAttribute("class","grid");
8056 		
8057 			archRadiusX = gN(id+"_aw"+arch);
8058 			if(archRadiusX == 0)
8059 			{
8060 				if(iSpokes === 0 && spokes > 0)
8061 				{ // center hub diameter == separation of outer arches
8062 					if(arch == 1)
8063 					{
8064 						archRadiusX = separationX;
8065 					}
8066 					else
8067 					{
8068 						archRadiusX = separationX + (separationX*(arch-1)*2);
8069 					}
8070 				}
8071 				else
8072 				{
8073 					archRadiusX = arch*separationX;
8074 				}
8075 				s(id+"_aw"+arch,archRadiusX*2);
8076 			}
8077 			else
8078 			{
8079 				archRadiusX = archRadiusX/2;
8080 			}
8081 			
8082 			archRadiusY = gN(id+"_ah"+arch);
8083 			if(archRadiusY === 0)
8084 			{
8085 				if(iSpokes === 0 && spokes > 0)
8086 				{ // center hub diameter == separation of outer arches
8087 					if(arch == 1)
8088 					{
8089 						archRadiusY = separationY;
8090 					}
8091 					else
8092 					{
8093 						archRadiusY = separationY + (separationY*(arch-1)*2);
8094 					}
8095 				}
8096 				else
8097 				{
8098 					archRadiusY = arch*separationY;
8099 				}
8100 				s(id+"_ah"+arch,archRadiusY);
8101 			}
8102 
8103 			
8104 			
8105 			xStartArch = cx - archRadiusX;  
8106 			cy = yTopBar;
8107 			computeCircleCenter(xStartArch,cy,cx,cy-archRadiusY,xStartArch+(2*archRadiusX),cy);
8108 
8109 			archCircumference = Math.atan2(Xo-xStartArch,Yo-cy)*R;		
8110 			switch(segType)
8111 			{
8112 				case 'F':	
8113 					archCircumference *= 2;	
8114 					d="M "+xStartArch+","+cy+" A "+R+","+R+" 0 0,1 "+(xStartArch+(2*archRadiusX))+","+cy;
8115 					if(leg_h > 0)
8116 					{
8117 					 	d+= " l 0,"+ leg_h + " M "+xStartArch+","+cy+" l 0,"+ leg_h; 
8118 					}
8119 					break;
8120 				case 'L':		
8121 					d="M "+xStartArch+","+cy+" A "+R+","+R+" 0 0,1 "+(xStartArch+archRadiusX)+","+(cy-archRadiusY);
8122 					if(leg_h > 0)
8123 					{
8124 					 	d+= " M "+xStartArch+","+cy+" l 0,"+ leg_h; 
8125 					}
8126 					
8127 					break;
8128 				case 'R':		
8129 					d="M "+glass_x+","+(cy-archRadiusY)+" A "+R+","+R+" 0 0,1 "+(glass_x+archRadiusX)+","+cy;
8130 					if(leg_h > 0)
8131 					{
8132 					 	d+= " l 0,"+ (leg_h) ; 
8133 					}
8134 					
8135 					break;
8136 				default:
8137 					break;	
8138 			}
8139 					
8140 			if(arch == 1 && spokes > 0)
8141 			{
8142 				arch1_radius = R;
8143 				arch1_center = new Point(Xo,Yo);
8144 				arch1_width = (archRadiusX*2);
8145 				arch1_left = new Point(xStartArch,cy);
8146 				arch1_right = new Point(xStartArch+(2*archRadiusX),cy);
8147 				arch1_top = new Point(xStartArch+archRadiusX,Yo-R);
8148 			}
8149 			if(applet)
8150 			{
8151 		
8152 				registerArchElement(id,arch,cx,cy-1,archRadiusX*2,archRadiusY,thk,segType,redraw);					
8153 				
8154 			}
8155 			arch_n.setAttribute("d",d);
8156 			arch_n.getStyle().setProperty("stroke",color,"");
8157 			arch_n.getStyle().setProperty("stroke-width",thk+"","");
8158 			createDescription(arch_id,"RADIUS: " + inchesToInchesDim(archRadiusX) + "   LENGTH: "+inchesToInchesDim(archCircumference)+"   STOCK WIDTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(thk) + ".");
8159 		} // for arch	
8160 	} // endif(arches > 0)
8161 	
8162 	var x1,y1,x2,y2,len,spoke_n,ispoke_n,path;
8163 	var spoke = 1;
8164 	var radialPointsInner = null;
8165 	if(spokes > 0)
8166 	{
8167 		switch(segType)
8168 		{
8169 			case "F":
8170 				radialPointsInner=getRadialPoints(	arch1_left,
8171 													arch1_right,
8172 													arch1_center,
8173 													arch1_radius,
8174 													spokes,
8175 													false,false);
8176 				break;
8177 
8178 			case "L":
8179 				radialPointsInner=getRadialPoints(	arch1_left,
8180 													arch1_top,
8181 													arch1_center,
8182 													arch1_radius,
8183 													spokes,
8184 													false, false);
8185 				break;
8186 			case "R":
8187 				radialPointsInner=getRadialPoints(	arch1_top,
8188 													arch1_right,
8189 													arch1_center,
8190 													arch1_radius,
8191 													spokes,
8192 													false,false);
8193 				break;
8194 			default:
8195 				break;
8196 		}
8197 		for(spoke=1;spoke<=radialPointsInner.length;spoke++)
8198 		{			
8199 			spoke_n = drawing.getElementById(idPrefix+id+"_spoke_"+spoke);
8200 			if(spoke_n === null)
8201 			{
8202 				spoke_n = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
8203 				spoke_n.setAttribute("id",idPrefix+id+"_spoke_"+spoke);
8204 				spoke_n.setAttribute("class","grid")
8205 				grp.appendChild(spoke_n);
8206 			}
8207 			x1=radialPointsOuter[spoke-1].x;
8208 			y1=radialPointsOuter[spoke-1].y;
8209 			x2=radialPointsInner[spoke-1].x;
8210 			if(spoke == splitHub)
8211 			{
8212 				y2=cy;
8213 			}
8214 			else
8215 			{
8216 				y2=radialPointsInner[spoke-1].y;
8217 			}
8218 			spokeCounter++;
8219 			s(id+"_S"+spoke+"I",radialPointsInner[spoke-1].c);
8220 			s(id+"_S"+spoke+"O",radialPointsOuter[spoke-1].c);
8221 			path="M " + (x1) + "," +(y1) + " L " + (x2) + "," + (y2);
8222 			len = Math.sqrt(Math.pow(x2-x1,2)+ Math.pow(y2-y1,2));
8223 			spoke_n.setAttribute("d",path);
8224 			spoke_n.getStyle().setProperty("stroke",color,"");
8225 			spoke_n.getStyle().setProperty("stroke-width",thk+"","");
8226 			createDescription(idPrefix+id+"_spoke_"+spoke,"LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(len) + "   STOCK WIDTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(thk) +"  RADIUS OFFSET (in/out): " +inchesToInchesDim(radialPointsInner[spoke-1].c) + ","+inchesToInchesDim(radialPointsOuter[spoke-1].c)+".");
8227 		}
8228 	}
8229 
8230 	var ispoke = 1;	
8231 
8232 	if(iSpokes > 0 && splitHub == 0)
8233 	{
8234 	
8235 		for(;ispoke <= iSpokes; ispoke++)
8236 		{
8237 			ispoke_n = drawing.getElementById(idPrefix+id+"_ispoke_"+ispoke);
8238 			if(ispoke_n === null)
8239 			{
8240 				ispoke_n = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
8241 				ispoke_n.setAttribute("id",idPrefix+id+"_ispoke_"+ispoke);
8242 				ispoke_n.setAttribute("class","grid");
8243 				grp.appendChild(ispoke_n);
8244 			}
8245 			
8246 			x=radialPointsOuter[ispoke-1].x;
8247 			y=radialPointsOuter[ispoke-1].y;
8248 
8249 			switch(segType)
8250 			{
8251 				case "F":
8252 					path="M " + (glass_x+glass_w/2) + "," +(cy) + " L " + (x) + "," + (y);
8253 					break;
8254 				case "L":
8255 					path="M " + (glass_x+glass_w) + "," +(cy) + " L " + (x) + "," + (y);
8256 					break;
8257 				case "R":
8258 					path="M " + (glass_x) + "," +(cy) + " L " + (x) + "," + (y);
8259 					break;
8260 				default:
8261 					break;
8262 			}
8263 			s(id+"_S"+spoke+"O",radialPointsOuter[ispoke-1].c);
8264 			
8265 			ispoke_n.setAttribute("d",path);
8266 			ispoke_n.getStyle().setProperty("stroke",color,"");
8267 			ispoke_n.getStyle().setProperty("stroke-width",thk+"","");
8268 			spokeCounter++;
8269 		
8270 			len = Math.sqrt(Math.pow(x-(cx-(thk/2)),2)+ Math.pow(y-(cy-(thk/2)),2));
8271 				
8272 			createDescription(idPrefix+id+"_ispoke_"+ispoke,"LENGTH: " +inchesToInchesDim(len)+ "   STOCK WIDTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(thk) +"   RADIAL OFFSET:"+ inchesToInchesDim(radialPointsOuter[ispoke-1].c)+".");
8273 		}
8274 	}
8275 
8276 	var centerVBar;
8277 	if((iSpokes > 0 || splitHub !== 0) && leg_h > 0 && segType == "F")
8278 	{
8279 	
8280 			centerVBar = drawing.getElementById(idPrefix+id+"_split");
8281 			if(centerVBar === null)
8282 			{
8283 				centerVBar = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
8284 				centerVBar.setAttribute("id",idPrefix+id+"_split");
8285 				centerVBar.setAttribute("class","grid");
8286 				grp.appendChild(centerVBar);
8287 			}
8288 			
8289 			x1=x2=glass_x+glass_w/2;
8290 			y1=yTopBar;
8291 			y2=yTopBar+leg_h;
8292 
8293 			path="M " + (x1) + "," +(y1) + " L " + (x2) + "," + (y2);
8294 			
8295 			centerVBar.setAttribute("d",path);
8296 			centerVBar.getStyle().setProperty("stroke",color,"");
8297 			centerVBar.getStyle().setProperty("stroke-width",thk+"","");
8298 				
8299 			createDescription(idPrefix+id+"_split","  LENGTH: " +inchesToInchesDim(leg_h)+ "   STOCK WIDTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(thk) +".");
8300 	
8301 	}
8302 
8303 	var nScallop = 0;
8304 	var xScallop = 0;
8305 	var radialPointsScallop = null;
8306 	var scallopInset = g("f_scallop_inset");
8307 	var scallopExtraEndPoints = 0;
8308 	if(scalloped && radialPointsOuter.length > 0)
8309 	{
8310 		
8311 		if(scallopInset == null)
8312 		{
8313 			scallopInset = 1.25;
8314 		}
8315 		
8316 				
8317 		switch(segType)
8318 		{
8319 		case 'F':
8320 			scallopExtraEndPoints = leg_h == 0 ? 2 : 0;
8321 			computeCircleCenter(glass_x+scallopInset,cy,cx,glass_y+scallopInset,glass_x+(radiusX*2)-scallopInset,cy);
8322 			radialPointsScallop=getRadialPoints(new Point(glass_x+scallopInset,cy),
8323 												new Point(glass_x+glass_w-scallopInset,cy),
8324 												new Point(Xo,Yo),R,
8325 												Math.max(spokes,iSpokes)+2, //scallopExtraEndPoints,
8326 												true, true);
8327 			break;
8328 		case 'L':
8329 			scallopExtraEndPoints = leg_h == 0 ? 2 : 1;
8330 		
8331 			computeCircleCenter(glass_x+scallopInset,cy,cx,glass_y+scallopInset,glass_x+(radiusX*2)-scallopInset,cy);
8332 			radialPointsScallop=getRadialPoints(new Point(glass_x+scallopInset,cy),
8333 												new Point(cx,glass_y+scallopInset),
8334 												new Point(Xo,Yo),R,Math.max(spokes,iSpokes)+2,// scallopExtraEndPoints,
8335 												true,true);
8336 			break;
8337 		case 'R':
8338 			scallopExtraEndPoints = leg_h == 0 ? 2 : 1;
8339 		
8340 			computeCircleCenter(glass_x-radiusX+scallopInset,cy,glass_x,glass_y+scallopInset,glass_x+radiusX-scallopInset,cy);
8341 			radialPointsScallop=getRadialPoints(new Point(glass_x,glass_y+scallopInset),
8342 												new Point(glass_x+glass_w-scallopInset,cy),
8343 												new Point(Xo,Yo),R,Math.max(spokes,iSpokes)+2,// scallopExtraEndPoints,
8344 												true,true);
8345 
8346 
8347 			break;
8348 		}
8349 		
8350 		for(;xScallop<(radialPointsScallop.length-1);xScallop++)
8351 		{
8352 			nScallop++;
8353 			createScallop(id, nScallop,grp,frameArch_radius,
8354 							new Point(radialPointsScallop[xScallop].x,radialPointsScallop[xScallop].y),
8355 							new Point(radialPointsScallop[xScallop+1].x,radialPointsScallop[xScallop+1].y),
8356 							color,thk,redraw);
8357 		}
8358 	}
8359 	if(hbars > 0)
8360 	{
8361 		drawHorizontalBars(id,grp,glass_x,glass_y+glass_h,glass_w,leg_h,hbars,color,thk,halfRound,redraw);
8362 	
8363 	}
8364 }catch(e)
8365 {
8366 	alertUser("Exception: 	drawArchGrille('"+id+"'"+glass_xP+","+glass_yP+","+glass_wP+","+glass_hP+","+leg_hP+","+inset+","+ arches+","+ spokes+","+ iSpokes+","+ scalloped +","+ thk +",'"+ color+"','"+segType+"')");
8367 	alertUser(e);
8368 	trace(e);
8369 }		
8370 }

8380 /**
8381  * Draw seg hub grille
8382  * 
8383  * @param id 			String id
8384  * @param glass_xP		decimal x coordinate of the glass rectangle
8385  * @param glass_yP		decimal y coordinate of the glass rectangle
8386  * @param glass_wP		decimal width of the glass rectangle
8387  * @param arch_hP		decimal height of the arch
8388  * @param leg_hP		decimal leg height of the glass
8389  * @param hbars			integer horizontal bars
8390  * @param inset			decimal inset from from the containing frame
8391  * @param vBars			integer arches
8392  * @param hBars			integer spokes radiating from inner arch
8393  * @param thk			decimal thickness of grille element
8394  * @param color			String web color of elements
8395  * @param redraw		boolean redrawing
8396  * @return	void
8397  */
8398 
8399 function drawSegHubGrille(id, glass_xP,glass_yP,glass_wP,arch_hP, leg_hP, inset, vBars, hBars, thk, color, redraw)
8400 {
8401 try{
8402 	trace("drawSegHubGrille('"+id+"'"+glass_xP+","+glass_yP+","+glass_wP+","+arch_hP+","+ leg_hP+","+ inset+","+ vBars+","+ hBars +","+ thk +",'"+ color+"')");
8403 	var horzAdj = computeHorzOffset(glass_wP,arch_hP+leg_hP,inset);
8404 	var glass_x = glass_xP + inset + horzAdj;
8405 	var glass_y = glass_yP + inset;
8406 	
8407 	var glass_w = glass_wP - (2*(inset+horzAdj));
8408 		
8409 	var leg_h = leg_hP - inset;
8410 	var arch_h = arch_hP - inset;
8411 	var glass_h = leg_h+arch_h;
8412 	
8413 	var idPrefix = g("f_idprefix");
8414 
8415 	var arches = 1; // Math.floor(vBars/2);
8416 	
8417 	var spokes = vBars;
8418 	
8419 
8420 	if(!redraw)
8421 	{
8422 		createClipPattern(id);
8423 	}
8424 	
8425 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id+"_grid");
8426 	if(grp === null)
8427 	{
8428 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
8429 		grp.setAttribute("id",id+"_grid");
8430 		grp.getStyle().setProperty("clip-path","url(#"+idPrefix+"clip_"+id+")","");
8431 		
8432 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
8433 	}
8434 
8435 
8436 	var cx = glass_x+ glass_w/2;
8437 	var cy = glass_y+ glass_h - leg_h;
8438 	
8439 	var x,y,lites,radius,radians,radianStart,radiansA1,radianStartA1,hSpacing,vSpacing;
8440 	
8441 	computeCircleCenter(glass_x,cy,cx,glass_y,glass_x+glass_w,cy);
8442 
8443 	var frameArch_center = new Point(Xo,Yo);
8444 	var frameArch_radius = R;
8445 	var radialPointsOuter=getRadialPoints(new Point(glass_x,cy),
8446 													new Point(glass_x+glass_w,cy),
8447 													new Point(Xo,Yo),R,spokes,
8448 													true, true);
8449 		
8450 
8451 
8452 	if(applet && !redraw)
8453 	{
8454 		var redrawScript = "drawSegHubGrille('"+id+"'"+glass_xP+","+glass_yP+","+glass_wP+","+arch_hP+","+ leg_hP+","+ inset+","+ vBars+","+ hBars +","+ thk +",'"+ color+"',true)";
8455 		
8456 		applet.registerLite(idPrefix+id,glass_x+"",glass_y+"",glass_w+"",glass_h+"",redrawScript);
8457 		var elLite = drawing.getElementById(id);
8458 		if(elLite !== null)
8459 		{
8460 			elLite.setAttribute("onmousemove","dragArch(evt)");							 	
8461 			elLite.setAttribute("onmouseup","dropArch(evt)");
8462 		}							 	
8463 	}
8464 	
8465 	var archRadiusX,archRadiusY,arch,separationX,separationY,xStartArch,yStartArch,arch_id,arch_n;
8466 	
8467 
8468 	var arch_radius;
8469 	var arch_height;
8470 	
8471 	var spoke = 1;
8472 
8473 	var spokeCounter = 0;
8474 	var radialPointsInner;	
8475 	arch = 1;
8476 	
8477 		separationY = (leg_h/(hBars+1))/(arches+1);
8478 		separationX = glass_w/(vBars+1);
8479 			
8480 			arch_id = (redraw?idPrefix+id:id)+"_arch_"+arch;
8481 			arch_n = drawing.getElementById(arch_id);
8482 			if(arch_n === null)
8483 			{
8484 				arch_n = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
8485 				arch_n.setAttribute("id",arch_id);
8486 				
8487 				arch_n.setAttribute("onmousemove","dragArch(evt)");							 	
8488 				arch_n.setAttribute("onmouseup","dropArch(evt)");
8489 				
8490 				grp.appendChild(arch_n);
8491 			}
8492 			arch_n.setAttribute("class","grid");
8493 		
8494 			archRadiusX = gN(id+"_aw"+arch)/2;
8495 			if(archRadiusX === 0)
8496 			{
8497 				archRadiusX = (separationX*(spokes-1))/2;
8498 				s(id+"_aw"+arch,archRadiusX*2);
8499 			}
8500 			
8501 			cy = glass_y + glass_h - (hBars*(leg_h/(hBars+1))) - (arch*separationY); 
8502 			xStartArch = glass_x+separationX;;
8503 			
8504 			if(g("f_material") == "WOOD")
8505 			{
8506 				arch_radius = frameArch_radius;
8507 				
8508 				Yo = Math.sqrt(Math.pow(arch_radius,2)-Math.pow(cx-xStartArch,2)) + cy;
8509 				computeCircleCenter(xStartArch,cy,cx,Yo-arch_radius,(xStartArch+(2*archRadiusX)),cy);
8510 				arch_radius = R;
8511 				trace("R="+R);
8512 				
8513 			}
8514 			else
8515 			{
8516 				arch_height = (archRadiusX*2)*(arch_h/glass_w);

8518 				arch_radius = R;
8519 			}
8520 			radialPointsInner=getRadialPointsByHorzSegments(new Point(xStartArch,cy),
8521 															new Point(	(xStartArch+(2*archRadiusX)),cy),
8522 															new Point(Xo,Yo),
8523 															arch_radius,
8524 															spokes,
8525 															true,true);
8526 				
8527 			
8528 			d="M "+xStartArch+","+(cy)+ 
8529 			  " A "+arch_radius+","+arch_radius+" 0 0,1 "+(xStartArch+(2*archRadiusX))+","+cy;
8530 				
8531 			if(applet)
8532 			{
8533 		
8534 			//	registerArchElement(id,arch,cx,cy-1,archRadiusX*2,archRadiusY,thk,segType,redraw);					
8535 				
8536 			}
8537 			trace("arch d="+d);
8538 			arch_n.setAttribute("d",d);
8539 			arch_n.getStyle().setProperty("stroke",color,"");
8540 			arch_n.getStyle().setProperty("stroke-width",thk+"","");
8541 			createDescription(arch_id,"RADIUS: " + inchesToInchesDim(archRadiusX) + "   STOCK WIDTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(thk) + ".");
8542 
8543 	
8544 	var x1,y1,x2,y2,len,spoke_n,path,vBar;
8545 	
8546 			
8547 		for(spoke=1;spoke <= spokes; spoke++)
8548 		{
8549 			
8550 			spoke_n = drawing.getElementById(idPrefix+id+"_spoke_"+spoke);
8551 			if(spoke_n === null)
8552 			{
8553 				spoke_n = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
8554 				spoke_n.setAttribute("id",idPrefix+id+"_spoke_"+spoke);
8555 				spoke_n.setAttribute("class","grid");
8556 				grp.appendChild(spoke_n);
8557 			}
8558 			
8559 			vBar = drawing.getElementById(idPrefix+id+"_v"+spoke);
8560 			if(vBar === null)
8561 			{
8562 				vBar = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
8563 				vBar.setAttribute("id",idPrefix+id+"_v"+spoke);
8564 				vBar.setAttribute("class","grid");
8565 				grp.appendChild(vBar);
8566 			}
8567 	
8568 			spokeCounter++;
8569 			
8570 			path="M " + (radialPointsInner[spoke-1].x) + "," +(radialPointsInner[spoke-1].y) + 
8571 					" L " + (radialPointsOuter[spoke-1].x) + "," + (radialPointsOuter[spoke-1].y);
8572 			len = Math.sqrt(Math.pow(radialPointsInner[spoke-1].x-radialPointsOuter[spoke-1].x,2)+
8573 							 Math.pow(radialPointsInner[spoke-1].y-radialPointsOuter[spoke-1].y,2));
8574 			
8575 			trace("spoke path="+path);
8576 			spoke_n.setAttribute("d",path);
8577 			spoke_n.getStyle().setProperty("stroke",color,"");
8578 			spoke_n.getStyle().setProperty("stroke-width",thk+"","");
8579 			createDescription(idPrefix+id+"_spoke_"+spoke,"LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(len) + "   STOCK WIDTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(thk) +".");
8580 
8581 			path="M " + (radialPointsInner[spoke-1].x) + "," +(radialPointsInner[spoke-1].y) + 
8582 					" L " + (radialPointsInner[spoke-1].x) + "," + (glass_y+glass_h);
8583 					
8584 			len = (glass_y+glass_h) - radialPointsInner[spoke-1].y;
8585 			vBar.setAttribute("d",path);
8586 			vBar.getStyle().setProperty("stroke",color,"");
8587 			vBar.getStyle().setProperty("stroke-width",thk+"","");
8588 			createDescription(idPrefix+id+"_v"+spoke,"LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(len) + "   STOCK WIDTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(thk) +".");
8589 
8590 		}
8591 
8592 
8593 
8594 		
8595 		var hBar = 1;
8596 		var hBarSep = leg_h/(hBars+1);
8597 		for(;hBar <= hBars; hBar++)
8598 		{
8599 			arch_id = (redraw?idPrefix+id:id)+"_h"+hBar;
8600 			arch_n = drawing.getElementById(arch_id);
8601 			if(arch_n === null)
8602 			{
8603 				arch_n = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
8604 				arch_n.setAttribute("id",arch_id);
8605 				
8606 				//arch_n.setAttribute("onmousemove","dragArch(evt)");							 	
8607 				//arch_n.setAttribute("onmouseup","dropArch(evt)");
8608 				
8609 				grp.appendChild(arch_n);
8610 			}
8611 			arch_n.setAttribute("class","grid");
8612 			arch_n.getStyle().setProperty("stroke",color,"");
8613 			
8614 			y = glass_y+arch_h+(hBar*hBarSep);
8615 			
8616 			path = "M " + glass_x +","+ y + " l " + (glass_w)+",0";
8617 			
8618 			arch_n.setAttribute("d",path);
8619 			arch_n.getStyle().setProperty("stroke",color,"");
8620 			arch_n.getStyle().setProperty("stroke-width",thk+"","");
8621 			createDescription(arch_id,"LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(glass_w) + "   STOCK WIDTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(thk) +".");
8622 		}
8623 			
8624 	if(hBars > 0)
8625 	{
8626 		drawHorizontalBars(id,grp,glass_x,glass_y+glass_h,glass_w,leg_h,hBars,color,thk,false,redraw);
8627 	
8628 	}
8629 
8630 	
8631 }catch(e)
8632 {
8633 	alertUser("Exception:  drawSegHubGrille('"+id+"'"+glass_xP+","+glass_yP+","+glass_wP+","+arch_hP+","+ leg_hP+","+ inset+","+ vBars+","+ hBars +","+ thk +",'"+ color+"')");
8634 	alertUser(e);
8635 	trace(e);
8636 }		
8637 }

8651 /**
8652  * Draw gothic grille
8653  * 
8654  * @param id 			String id
8655  * @param glass_xP		decimal x coordinate of the glass rectangle
8656  * @param glass_yP		decimal y coordinate of the glass rectangle
8657  * @param glass_wP		decimal width of the glass rectangle
8658  * @param glass_hP		decimal height of the glass rectangle
8659  * @param leg_hP		decimal leg height of the glass
8660  * @param hbars			integer horizontal bars
8661  * @param inset			decimal inset from from the containing frame
8662  * @param spokes		integer arc spokes 
8663  * @param thk			decimal thickness of grille element
8664  * @param color			String web color of elements
8665  * @param segType		char	F=full,L=left qtr-round, R=right qtr-round
8666  * @param redraw		boolean redrawing
8667  * @return	void
8668  */
8669 
8670 function drawGothicGrille(id, glass_xP,glass_yP,glass_wP,glass_hP, leg_hP, hBars, inset, spokes, thk, color, segType, redraw)
8671 {
8672 try{
8673 	trace("drawGothicGrille('"+id+"'"+glass_xP+","+glass_yP+","+glass_wP+","+glass_hP+","+ spokes+",'"+ thk +",'"+ color+"','"+ segType+"',"+redraw+")");
8674 	var horzAdj = computeHorzOffset(segType=='F'?glass_wP:glass_wP*2,glass_hP,inset);
8675 	var glass_x = segType == 'R' ? glass_xP + inset : glass_xP + inset + horzAdj;
8676 	var glass_y = glass_yP + inset;
8677 	
8678 	var glass_w = segType == 'F' ? glass_wP - (2*(inset+horzAdj)) : glass_wP - horzAdj - (2*inset);
8679 	
8680 	var glass_h = leg_hP === 0 ? glass_hP -(2*inset) : glass_hP - inset;
8681 	var leg_h = leg_hP === 0 ? 0 : leg_hP - inset;
8682 
8683 	var idPrefix = g("f_idprefix");
8684 
8685 	createClipPattern(id);
8686 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id+"grille");
8687 	if(grp === null)
8688 	{
8689 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
8690 		grp.setAttribute("id",id+"grille");
8691 		grp.getStyle().setProperty("clip-path","url(#"+idPrefix+"clip_"+id+")","");
8692 		
8693 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
8694 	}
8695 
8696 
8697 	if(applet && !redraw)
8698 	{
8699 		applet.registerLite(idPrefix+id,glass_x+"",glass_y+"",glass_w+"",glass_h+"","");
8700 		var elLite = drawing.getElementById(id);
8701 		if(elLite !== null)
8702 		{
8703 			elLite.setAttribute("onmousemove","dragArch(evt)");							 	
8704 			elLite.setAttribute("onmouseup","dropArch(evt)");
8705 		}	
8706 	}
8707 	
8708 
8709 	var radiusX = segType == 'F'?glass_w/2:glass_w;
8710 	var radiusY = glass_h;
8711 	var cx = segType == 'R'? glass_x : glass_x+ radiusX;
8712 	var cy = glass_y+glass_h;
8713 	
8714 	var lites,radius,radians,radianStart,radiansA1,radianStartA1;
8715 	var x,y;
8716 	
8717 	switch(segType)
8718 	{
8719 		case 'F':
8720 			computeCircleCenter(glass_x,cy,cx,glass_y,glass_x+(radiusX*2),cy);
8721 			break;
8722 		case 'L':
8723 			computeCircleCenter(glass_x,cy,cx,glass_y,glass_x+(radiusX*2),cy);
8724 			break;
8725 		case 'R':
8726 			computeCircleCenter(glass_x-radiusX,cy,glass_x,glass_y,glass_x+radiusX,cy);
8727 			break;
8728 		default:
8729 			break;
8730 	}
8731 
8732 	var frameArch_center = new Point(Xo,Yo);
8733 	var frameArch_radius = R;
8734 		
8735 	var sep = glass_w/(spokes+1);
8736 	var spoke_x = glass_x;
8737 	var dL,dR;
8738 	var spoke = 1;
8739 	for(;spoke <= spokes; spoke++)
8740 	{
8741 			var spoke_nL = drawing.getElementById(id+"_spoke_"+spoke+"L");
8742 			if(spoke_nL === null)
8743 			{
8744 				spoke_nL = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
8745 				spoke_nL.setAttribute("id",id+"_spoke_"+spoke+"L");
8746 				spoke_nL.setAttribute("class","grid");
8747 				spoke_nL.getStyle().setProperty("stroke",color,"");
8748 				spoke_nL.getStyle().setProperty("stroke-width",thk+"","");
8749 				
8750 				grp.appendChild(spoke_nL);
8751 			}
8752 	
8753 			var spoke_nR = drawing.getElementById(id+"_spoke_"+spoke+"R");
8754 			if(spoke_nR === null)
8755 			{
8756 				spoke_nR = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
8757 				spoke_nR.setAttribute("id",id+"_spoke_"+spoke+"R");
8758 				spoke_nR.setAttribute("class","grid");
8759 				spoke_nR.getStyle().setProperty("stroke",color,"");
8760 				spoke_nR.getStyle().setProperty("stroke-width",thk+"","");
8761 				grp.appendChild(spoke_nR);
8762 			}
8763 			spoke_x+=sep;
8764 			dL = "M "+(spoke_x)+","+(glass_y+glass_h)+" a "+R+","+R+" 180 0,0 -"+(glass_w/2)+",-"+glass_h;
8765 			dR = "M "+(spoke_x)+","+(glass_y+glass_h)+" a "+R+","+R+" 0 0,1 "+(glass_w/2)+",-"+glass_h;
8766 			
8767 			if(leg_h > 0)
8768 			{
8769 				dR+="M "+(spoke_x)+","+(glass_y+glass_h)+" l 0,"+ leg_h;
8770 			}
8771 			
8772 			spoke_nL.setAttribute("d",dL);
8773 			spoke_nR.setAttribute("d",dR);
8774 			
8775 			if(applet && !redraw)
8776 			{
8777 					applet.registerVertElement( idPrefix+id+"_spoke_"+spoke+"R",
8778 										idPrefix + id,
8779 										(spoke_x-(thk/2))+"",
8780 										thk+"",
8781 										"");
8782 			}
8783 	}
8784 	
8785 	if(hBars > 0)
8786 	{
8787 		drawHorizontalBars(id,grp,glass_x,glass_y+glass_h,glass_w,leg_h,hBars,color,thk,true,redraw);
8788 	
8789 	}
8790 
8791 }catch(e)
8792 {
8793 	alertUser("Exception:  drawGothicGrille('"+id+"'"+glass_xP+","+glass_yP+","+glass_wP+","+glass_hP+","+ spokes+",'"+ thk +",'"+ color+"','"+ segType+"',"+redraw+")");
8794 	alertUser(e);
8795 	trace(e);
8796 }
8797 }
8798 
8799 /**
8800  * Creates a arch scallop
8801  * 
8802  * @param idGlass		String id of glass
8803  * @param nScallop		integer ordinal number
8804  * @param grp			Node parent group
8805  * @param r				decimal radius
8806  * @param p1			Point start
8807  * @param p2			Point end
8808  * @param color			String web color code
8809  * @param thk			decimal thickness of grille element
8810  * @param redraw		boolean redrawing
8811  * @return
8812  */
8813 
8814 function createScallop(idGlass,nScallop,grp,r,p1,p2,color,thk,redraw)
8815 {
8816 	trace("createScallop('"+idGlass+"',"+nScallop+",grp,"+r+",p("+p1.x+","+p1.y+"),p("+p2.x+","+p2.y+","+color+"',"+thk+")");
8817 
8818 try{
8819 	var idPrefix = g("f_idprefix");
8820 			var scallop_id = (redraw?idPrefix+idGlass:idGlass)+"scallop_"+nScallop;
8821 			var scallop = drawing.getElementById(scallop_id);
8822 			if(scallop == null)
8823 			{
8824 			trace("creating scallop "+ nScallop);
8825 				scallop = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
8826 				scallop.setAttribute("id",scallop_id);
8827 				scallop.setAttribute("class","grid");
8828 				scallop.getStyle().setProperty("stroke",color,"");
8829 				scallop.getStyle().setProperty("stroke-width",thk,"");
8830 				grp.appendChild(scallop);
8831 			}
8832 			
8833 			var d="M " + p1.x + "," + p1.y + " A "+ r + "," + r + " 0 0,0 " + p2.x + "," + p2.y;
8834 			trace("scallop d="+d);
8835 			scallop.setAttribute("d",d);
8836 }
8837 catch(e)
8838 {
8839 	alertUser("Exception:  createScallop('"+idGlass+"',"+nScallop+",grp,"+r+",p("+p1.x+","+p1.y+"),p("+p2.x+","+p2.y+")");
8840 	alertUser(e);
8841 	trace(e);
8842 }				
8843 }
