8848 /**
8849  * Register an arch element for alignment
8850  * 
8851  * @param id		String id
8852  * @param n			integer ordinal number
8853  * @param xC		decimal x coordinate of the center
8854  * @param y			decimal y coordinate of top
8855  * @param w			decimal width of the arch
8856  * @param h			decimal height of the arch
8857  * @param thk		decimal thickness of the grille element
8858  * @param segType	char	F=full,L=left qtr-round, R=right qtr-round
8859  * @param redraw	boolean redrawing
8860  * @return
8861  */
8862 
8863 function registerArchElement(id,n,xC,y,w,h,thk,segType,redraw)
8864 {
8865 trace("registerArchElement('"+id+"',"+n+","+xC+","+y+","+w+","+h+","+thk+",'"+segType+"',"+redraw+")");
8866 
8867 	whRatio = w/h;
8868 	
8869 	var archId = id+"_arch_"+n;
8870 	var idPrefix = g("f_idprefix");
8871 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id+"_grid");
8872 
8873 
8874 	if(segType == 'F' || segType == 'L')
8875 	{
8876 		applet.registerVertElement( idPrefix+id+"_arch_"+n,
8877 										idPrefix + id,
8878 										(xC - (w/2)-(thk/2))+"",
8879 										thk+"",
8880 										"");
8881 	}
8882 	if(segType == 'F' || segType == 'R')
8883 	{
8884 		applet.registerVertElement( idPrefix+id+"_arch_"+n,
8885 										idPrefix + id,
8886 										(xC + (w/2)-(thk/2))+"",
8887 										thk+"",
8888 										"");
8889 	}
8890 				
8891 
8892 	var script = 
8893 		 "moveArch('"+id+"',"+n+",%X%,"+xC+","+y+","+whRatio+","+thk+",'"+segType+"');";
8894 	var m = null;
8895 	var append = false;
8896 	if(segType == 'F' || segType == 'L')
8897 	{
8898 		m = drawing.getElementById((redraw?idPrefix:"")+archId+"_left");
8899 		if(m===null)
8900 		{
8901 			m = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"rect");
8902 			m.setAttribute("id",(redraw?idPrefix:"")+archId+"_left");
8903 			append = true;
8904 		}
8905 	
8906 		m.setAttribute("class","draghide");
8907 		m.setAttribute("x",(xC - (w/2)-(thk/2)));
8908 		
8909 		m.setAttribute("y",y-thk);
8910 		m.setAttribute("width",thk);
8911 		m.setAttribute("height",thk);
8912 
8913 		m.setAttribute("onmousedown","startDragArch(evt)");							 	
8914 		m.setAttribute("onmousemove","dragArch(evt)");							 	
8915 		m.setAttribute("onmouseup","dropArch(evt)");	
8916 		m.setAttribute("onmouseover","showHandle('"+idPrefix+archId+"_left',true);");
8917 		m.setAttribute("onmouseout","showHandle('"+idPrefix+archId+"_left',false);");
8918 
8919 		if(append)
8920 		{
8921 			grp.appendChild(m);
8922 		}
8923 		
8924 		applet.registerVertElement(idPrefix+archId+"_left",
8925 								idPrefix+id,
8926 								(xC - (w/2)-(thk/2))+"", 	
8927 								thk+"",
8928 								script);
8929 	}
8930 	append = false;
8931 	if(segType == 'F' || segType == 'L')
8932 	{
8933 							
8934 		m = drawing.getElementById((redraw?idPrefix:"")+archId+"_right");
8935 		
8936 		if(m===null)
8937 		{
8938 			m = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"rect");
8939 			m.setAttribute("id",(redraw?idPrefix:"")+archId+"_right");
8940 			append = true;
8941 		}
8942 	
8943 		m.setAttribute("class","draghide");
8944 		m.setAttribute("x",(xC + (w/2)-(thk/2)));
8945 		
8946 		m.setAttribute("y",y-thk);
8947 		m.setAttribute("width",thk);
8948 		m.setAttribute("height",thk);
8949 		m.setAttribute("onmousedown","startDragArch(evt)");							 	
8950 		m.setAttribute("onmousemove","dragArch(evt)");							 	
8951 		m.setAttribute("onmouseup","dropArch(evt)");	
8952 		m.setAttribute("onmouseover","showHandle('"+idPrefix+archId+"_right',true);");
8953 		m.setAttribute("onmouseout","showHandle('"+idPrefix+archId+"_right',false);");
8954 	
8955 		if(append)
8956 		{
8957 			grp.appendChild(m);
8958 		}
8959 
8960 	
8961 		applet.registerVertElement(idPrefix+archId+"_right",
8962 								idPrefix+id,
8963 								(xC + (w/2)-(thk/2))+"", 	
8964 								thk+"",
8965 								script);							
8966 	}
8967 }

8969 
8970 function moveArch(id,n,x,xC,y,whRatio,thk,segType)
8971 {
8972 trace("moveArch("+id+","+n+","+x+","+xC+","+whRatio+")");
8973 	var r = (x+thk) - xC;
8974 	
8975 	var w = Math.abs(r*2);
8976 	var h = w/whRatio;
8977 
8978 
8979 	s(id+"_aw"+n, w);
8980 	s(id+"_ah"+n, h);
8981 	
8982 //	registerArchElement(id,n,xC,y,w,h,thk,segType,true);
8983 }
8984 
8985 function showHandle(id,show)
8986 {
8987 	if(applet===null)
8988 		return;
8989 	var el = drawing.getElementById(id);
8990 	if(el != null)
8991 	{	
8992 		el.setAttribute("class",show?"dragshow":"draghide");
8993 	}
8994 }
8995 
8996 function startDragArch(evt)
8997 {
8998 	if(applet===null)
8999 		return;
9000 	
9001 	var rightClick =  (evt.which && evt.which == 3)
9002 						||
9003 						(evt.button && evt.button == 2);
9004 
9005 	var el = evt.getTarget();
9006 	dragObj = el;
9007 	dragOffset = getX(evt) - el.getAttribute("x");  
9008 	dragType = "A";
9009 	
9010 	applet.startDragX(el.id,"");
9011 	dragObj.setAttribute("class","dragshow");
9012 
9013 }
9014 
9015 
9016 
9017 function dragArch(evt)
9018 {
9019 	if(dragObj === null)
9020 		return;
9021 		
9022 
9023 	dragObj.setAttribute("x",getX(evt)-dragOffset);
9024 	applet.dragX(dragObj.id);
9025 }
9026 
9027 
9028 
9029 function dropArch(evt)
9030 {
9031 	if(dragObj === null)
9032 		return;
9033 		
9034 
9035 
9036 	dragObj.setAttribute("x",getX(evt)-dragOffset);
9037 	applet.dropX(dragObj.id);
9038 	dragObj = null;
9039 	dragOffset = 0;
9040 	dragType = "";	
9041 }

9046 /**
9047  * Draw an image
9048  * 
9049  * @param id		String id
9050  * @param idParent	String id of parent group
9051  * @param resource	String file name (.jpg or .png)
9052  * @param x			decimal x coordinate
9053  * @param y			decimal y coordinate
9054  * @param w			decimal width
9055  * @param h			decimal height
9056  * @return	void
9057  */
9058 
9059 function initImage(id, idParent, resource, x, y, w, h)
9060 {
9061 try{
9062 	trace("initImage('"+id+"','"+idParent+"','"+resource+"',"+x+","+y+","+ w+","+ h+")");
9063 
9064 	var parent = idParent == null ? null : drawing.getElementById(idParent);
9065 	if(idParent != null && parent == null)
9066 	{
9067 		parent = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
9068 		parent.setAttribute("id",idPLarent);
9069 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(parent);
9070 	}
9071 	else
9072 	{
9073 		parent = drawing.getElementById("window");
9074 	}
9075 
9076 	var img = drawing.getElementById(id);
9077 	var create = false;
9078 	if(img == null)
9079 	{
9080 		img = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"image");
9081 		img.setAttribute("id",id);
9082 		create = true;
9083 	}
9084 	img.setAttribute("x",x);
9085 	img.setAttribute("y",y);
9086 	img.setAttribute("width",w);
9087 	img.setAttribute("height",h);
9088 	img.setAttribute("preserveAspectRatio","none");
9089 	
9090 		
9091 	var fromRasterize = g("f_rasterize") == "true";
9092 	var resourcePath = g("f_resourcePath");
9093 	
9094 	img.setAttributeNS(xlinkNS,"href",resourcePath + resource);
9095 
9096 	if(create)
9097 	{
9098 		parent.appendChild(img);
9099 	}
9100 }
9101 catch(e)
9102 {
9103 	alertUser("Exception:  initImage('"+id+"','"+idParent+"','"+resource+"',"+x+","+y+","+ w+","+ h+")");
9104 	alertUser(e);
9105 	trace(e);
9106 }		
9107 }

9110 /**
9111  * Draw glass triangle
9112  * 
9113  * @param id		String id
9114  * @param sashId	String id of containing sash
9115  * @param x			decimal x coordinate of containing rectangle
9116  * @param y			decimal y coordinate of containing rectangle
9117  * @param w			decimal width of containing rectangle
9118  * @param h			decimal height of containing rectangle
9119  * @param f			decimal frame thickness
9120  * @param v			decimal hidden glass inset
9121  * @param type		String LT=left/top,LB=left/bottom, RT=right/top, RB=right/bottom, 
9122  * 							IT=isosolese/top, IB=isosolese/bottom,
9123  * @return
9124  */
9125 function initGlassTriangle(id,sashId,x, y, w, h, f /*inset*/, v /*hidden glass inset*/, type)
9126 {
9127 try
9128 {
9129 trace("initGlassTriangle('"+id+"','"+sashId+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ h+","+ f+","+ v+",'"+type+"')");
9130 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id);
9131 	var idPrefix = g("f_idprefix");
9132 	if(grp === null)
9133 	{
9134 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
9135 		grp.setAttribute("id",id);
9136 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
9137 	}
9138 	
9139 	var gls = drawing.getElementById(id+"_pane");
9140 	if(gls === null)
9141 	{
9142 		
9143 		gls = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
9144 		gls.setAttribute("id",id+"_pane");
9145 		gls.setAttribute("class","glass");
9146 		gls.setAttribute("onmouseover","expose(evt,'"+idPrefix+sashId+"',true)");
9147 		gls.setAttribute("onmouseout","expose(evt,'"+idPrefix+sashId+"',false)");
9148 		gls.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
9149 	//These attributes don't apply to a <path>, but they feed the grid functions
9150 		gls.setAttribute("x",x);
9151 		gls.setAttribute("y",y);
9152 		gls.setAttribute("width",w);
9153 		gls.setAttribute("height",h);
9154 		
9155 		
9156 		grp.appendChild(gls);
9157 	}
9158 	var t,tText;
9159 	if(g("f_glass") == "TEMPERED")
9160 	{
9161 	trace("creating T");
9162 		t = drawing.getElementById(id+"_pane_t");
9163 		if(t == null)
9164 		{
9165 			t = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"text");
9166 			t.setAttribute("id",id+"_pane_t");
9167 			t.setAttribute("class","glass");
9168    			tText = drawing.createTextNode("T");
9169     		t.appendChild(tText);
9170 			grp.appendChild(t);			
9171 		}
9172 		switch(type)
9173 		{
9174 			case "RT":
9175 			case "LT":
9176 			case "IT":
9177 			case "LB":
9178 				t.setAttribute("x",x+w-2);
9179 				t.setAttribute("y",y+h-2);
9180 				break;
9181 				
9182 			case "RB":
9183 			case "IB":
9184 				t.setAttribute("x",x+2);
9185 				t.setAttribute("y",y+2);
9186 				break;	
9187 			default:
9188 				t.setAttribute("x",x+2);
9189 				t.setAttribute("y",y+2);
9190 				break;
9191 		}
9192 
9193 	}
9194 	var path,angleA,angleB,angleC,pointA, pointB, pointC, insetX, insetY,wV,hV,wNet,vNet;
9195 
9196 	switch(type)
9197 	{
9198 		case "RT":  // right triangle, facing right, pointy end up
9199 		{
9200 			angleA = Math.atan2(w,h);
9201 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
9202 			pointA = new Point(x+f,y+insetY);
9203 			
9204 			angleB = Math.atan2(h,w);
9205 			insetX = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9206 			pointB = new Point(x+w-insetX,y+h-f);
9207 			
9208 			pointC = new Point(x+f,y+h-f);
9209 			
9210 			wNet = w - (f+insetX);
9211 			hNet = h - (f+insetY);
9212 			
9213 			insetY = (f+v)/Math.tan(angleA/2);
9214 			insetX = (f+v)/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9215 
9216 			wV = w - ((f+v)+insetX);
9217 			hV = h - ((f+v)+insetY);
9218 		
9219 		
9220 		}
9221 		break;
9222 		case "RB": // right triangle, facing right, pointy end down
9223 		{
9224 			angleA = Math.atan2(w,h);
9225 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
9226 			pointA = new Point(x+f,y+h-insetY);
9227 			
9228 			angleB = Math.atan2(h,w);
9229 			insetX = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9230 			pointB = new Point(x+w-insetX,y+f);
9231 			
9232 			pointC = new Point(x+f,y+f);
9233 						
9234 			wNet = w - (f+insetX);
9235 			hNet = h - (f+insetY);
9236 			
9237 			insetY = (f+v)/Math.tan(angleA/2);
9238 			insetX = (f+v)/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9239 
9240 			wV = w - ((f+v)+insetX);
9241 			hV = h - ((f+v)+insetY);
9242 			
9243 		}
9244 			break;
9245 		case "LT":  // right triangle, facing left, pointy end up
9246 		{
9247 			angleA = Math.atan2(w,h);
9248 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
9249 			pointA = new Point(x+w-f,y+insetY);
9250 			
9251 			angleB = Math.atan2(h,w);
9252 			insetX = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9253 			pointB = new Point(x+insetX,y+h-f);
9254 			
9255 			pointC = new Point(x+w-f,y+h-f);
9256 						
9257 			wNet = w - (f+insetX);
9258 			hNet = h - (f+insetY);
9259 			
9260 			insetY = (f+v)/Math.tan(angleA/2);
9261 			insetX = (f+v)/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9262 
9263 			wV = w - ((f+v)+insetX);
9264 			hV = h - ((f+v)+insetY);
9265 			
9266 		}
9267 		break;
9268 		case "LB": // right triangle, facing left, pointy end down
9269 		{
9270 			angleA = Math.atan2(w,h);
9271 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
9272 			pointA = new Point(x+f,y+insetY);
9273 			
9274 			angleB = Math.atan2(h,w);
9275 			insetX = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9276 			pointB = new Point(x+w-insetX,y+h-f);
9277 			
9278 			pointC = new Point(x+w-f,y-f);
9279 						
9280 			wNet = w - (f+insetX);
9281 			hNet = h - (f+insetY);
9282 			
9283 			insetY = (f+v)/Math.tan(angleA/2);
9284 			insetX = (f+v)/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9285 
9286 			wV = w - ((f+v)+insetX);
9287 			hV = h - ((f+v)+insetY);
9288 			
9289 		
9290 		}
9291 			break;	
9292 		case "IT":  // isosoles, pointy end up
9293 		{
9294 			angleA = Math.atan2(w/2,h);
9295 			insetY = Math.sqrt(Math.pow(f/Math.tan(angleA),2)+Math.pow(f,2));
9296 			pointA = new Point(x+(w/2),y+insetY);
9297 		
9298 			angleB = Math.atan2(h,w/2);
9299 			insetX = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9300 			pointB = new Point(x+insetX,y+h-f);
9301 				
9302 			pointC = new Point(x+w-insetX,y+h-f);
9303 			
9304 						
9305 			
9306 			wNet = w - (2*insetX);
9307 			hNet = h - (f+insetY);
9308 			
9309 			insetY = (f+v)/Math.tan(angleA/2);
9310 			insetX = (f+v)/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9311 
9312 			wV = w - (2*insetX);
9313 			hV = h - ((f+v)+insetY);
9314 			
9315 			
9316 							
9317 		}
9318 		break;
9319 		case "IB":  // isosoles, pointy end down
9320 		{
9321 			angleA = Math.atan2(w/2,h);
9322 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleA);
9323 			pointA = new Point(x+(w/2),y+h-insetY);
9324 			
9325 			angleB = Math.atan2(h,w/2);
9326 			insetX = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9327 			pointB = new Point(x+w-insetX,y+f);
9328 			
9329 			pointC = new Point(x+insetX,y+f);
9330 		
9331 			wNet = w - (2*insetX);
9332 			hNet = h - (f+insetY);
9333 			
9334 			insetY = (f+v)/Math.tan(angleA/2);
9335 			insetX = (f+v)/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9336 
9337 			wV = w - (2*insetX);
9338 			hV = h - ((f+v)+insetY);
9339 			
9340 			
9341 		
9342 		}
9343 		break;
9344 		default:
9345 			break;
9346 	}
9347 	
9348 
9349 
9350 
9351 
9352 	path = "M " + pointA.x + "," + pointA.y + " L "+ pointB.x + "," + pointB.y + " L " + pointC.x + "," + pointC.y + " L " + pointA.x + "," + pointA.y;
9353 	gls.setAttribute("d",path);
9354 
9355 
9356 	if(g("f_tn")!="true")
9357 	{
9358 		var desc = "WIDTH: %W%  HEIGHT: %H%  VISIBLE: %WV%X%HV%.";
9359 		desc = desc.replace(/%W%/g,inchesToInchesDim(wNet));
9360 		desc = desc.replace(/%H%/g,inchesToInchesDim(hNet));
9361 		desc = desc.replace(/%WV%/g,inchesToInchesDim(wV));
9362 		desc = desc.replace(/%HV%/g,inchesToInchesDim(hV));
9363 		createDescription(id+"_pane",desc);
9364 	}
9365 }	
9366 catch(e)
9367 {
9368 	alertUser("Exception: initGlassTriangle('"+id+"','"+sashId+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ h+","+ f+","+ v+",'"+type+"')");
9369 
9370 	alertUser(e);
9371 	trace(e);
9372 }	
9373 }

9376 /**
9377  * Draw triangle frame, mitred
9378  * 
9379  * @param id		String id
9380  * @param x			decimal x coordinate of containing rectangle
9381  * @param y			decimal y coordinate of containing rectangle
9382  * @param w			decimal width of containing rectangle
9383  * @param h			decimal height of containing rectangle
9384  * @param f			decimal frame thickness
9385  * @param color		String web color code
9386  * @param type		String LT=left/top,LB=left/bottom, RT=right/top, RB=right/bottom, 
9387  * 							IT=isosolese/top, IB=isosolese/bottom,
9388  * @return
9389  */
9390 function initMitredTriangleFrame(id, x, y, w, h, f, color, type)
9391 {
9392 try
9393 {
9394 trace("initMitredTriangleFrame('"+id+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ h+","+ f+",'"+ color+"','"+ type+"')");
9395 
9396 	var desc = "";
9397 	var tn = g("f_tn") == "true";
9398 	// frame group
9399 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id);
9400 	if(grp == null)
9401 	{
9402 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
9403 		grp.setAttribute("id",id);
9404 		
9405 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
9406 	}
9407 
9408 	var sideA = drawing.getElementById(id+"_a");
9409 	if(sideA == null)
9410 	{
9411 		sideA = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
9412 		sideA.setAttribute("id",id+"_a");
9413 		sideA.setAttribute("class","frame");
9414 		sideA.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
9415 		
9416 		grp.appendChild(sideA);
9417 	}
9418 	
9419 	var sideB = drawing.getElementById(id+"_b");
9420 	if(sideB == null)
9421 	{
9422 		sideB = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
9423 		sideB.setAttribute("id",id+"_b");
9424 		sideB.setAttribute("class","frame");
9425 		sideB.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
9426 		
9427 		grp.appendChild(sideB);
9428 	}
9429 	
9430 	var sideC = drawing.getElementById(id+"_c");
9431 	if(sideC == null)
9432 	{
9433 		sideC = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
9434 		sideC.setAttribute("id",id+"_c");
9435 		sideC.setAttribute("class","frame");
9436 		sideC.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
9437 		
9438 		grp.appendChild(sideC);
9439 	}
9440 	
9441 	var angleA,angleB,angleC,degA,degB,degC,pointA, pointB, pointC, pathA, pathB, pathC, insetX, insetY;
9442 	
9443 
9444 	switch(type)
9445 	{
9446 		case "RT":  // right triangle, facing right, pointy end up
9447 		{
9448 			angleA = Math.atan2(w,h);
9449 			
9450 			degA = (angleA / Math.PI)*180;
9451 			
9452 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
9453 			pointA = new Point(x+f,y+insetY);
9454 			
9455 			angleB = Math.atan2(h,w);
9456 			degB = ((angleB) / Math.PI)*180;
9457 			
9458 			insetX = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9459 			pointB = new Point(x+w-insetX,y+h-f);
9460 			
9461 			pointC = new Point(x+f,y+h-f);
9462 			
9463 			pathA = "M " + x + "," + y + " l 0," + h + " L "+ pointC.x+","+pointC.y
9464 						+" L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y + " L " +x+","+y;
9465 			
9466 			pathB = "M " + x + "," + (y+h) + " l "+w+",0 L "+pointB.x+","+pointB.y
9467 						+" L "+ pointC.x+","+pointC.y + " L " +x+","+(y+h);
9468 				
9469 			pathC = "M " + x + "," + y + " l "+w+"," + h + " L "+ pointB.x+","+pointB.y
9470 						+" L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y + " L " +x+","+y;
9471 		
9472 			createDescription(id+"_b", "SILL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: 45," + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
9473 			createDescription(id+"_a", "SIDE-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(h) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degA) + ",45 degrees.");
9474 			createDescription(id+"_c", "CROSS-RAIL...base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(Math.sqrt(Math.pow(w,2)+Math.pow(h,2))) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: 45," + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
9475 		
9476 		}
9477 		break;
9478 		case "RB": // right triangle, facing right, pointy end down
9479 		{
9480 			angleA = Math.atan2(w,h);
9481 			degA = ((angleA/2) / Math.PI)*180;
9482 			
9483 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
9484 			pointA = new Point(x+f,y+h-insetY);
9485 			
9486 			angleB = Math.atan2(h,w);
9487 			degB = ((angleB/2) /Math.PI)*180;
9488 			
9489 			insetX = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9490 			pointB = new Point(x+w-insetX,y+f);
9491 			
9492 			pointC = new Point(x+f,y+f);
9493 			
9494 			pathA = "M " + x + "," + (y+h) + " l 0,-" + h + " L "+ pointC.x+","+pointC.y
9495 						+" L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y + " L " +x+","+(y+h);
9496 			
9497 			pathB = "M " + x + "," + y + " l "+w+",0 L "+pointB.x+","+pointB.y
9498 						+" L "+ pointC.x+","+pointC.y + " L " +x+","+y;
9499 				
9500 			pathC = "M " + (x+w) + "," + y + " l -"+w+"," + h + " L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y
9501 						+" L "+ pointB.x+","+pointB.y + " L " +(x+w)+","+y;
9502 
9503 			createDescription(id+"_b", "TOP-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w) + "  THICKNESS: " + (f) + "   MITRE: 45," + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
9504 			createDescription(id+"_a", "SIDE-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(h) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degA) + ",45 degrees.");
9505 			createDescription(id+"_c", "CROSS-RAIL...base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(Math.sqrt(Math.pow(w,2)+Math.pow(h,2))) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: 45," + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
9506 		
9507 		
9508 		}
9509 			break;
9510 		case "LT":  // right triangle, facing left, pointy end up
9511 		{
9512 			angleA = Math.atan2(w,h);
9513 			
9514 			degA = ((angleA/2) / Math.PI)*180;
9515 			
9516 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
9517 			pointA = new Point(x+w-f,y+insetY);
9518 			
9519 			angleB = Math.atan2(h,w);
9520 			degB = ((angleB/2) / Math.PI)*180;
9521 			
9522 			insetX = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9523 			
9524 			pointB = new Point(x+insetX,y+h-f);
9525 			
9526 			pointC = new Point(x+w-f,y+h-f);
9527 			
9528 			pathA = "M " + (x+w) + "," + y + " l 0," + h + " L "+ pointC.x+","+pointC.y
9529 						+" L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y + " L " +(x+w)+","+y;
9530 			
9531 			pathB = "M " + x + "," + (y+h) + " l "+w+",0 L "+pointC.x+","+pointC.y
9532 						+" L "+ pointB.x+","+pointB.y + " L " +x+","+(y+h);
9533 				
9534 			pathC = "M " + (x+w) + "," + y + " l -"+w+"," + h + " L "+ pointB.x+","+pointB.y
9535 						+" L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y + " L " +(x+w)+","+y;
9536 
9537 			createDescription(id+"_b", "SILL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: 45," + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
9538 			createDescription(id+"_a", "SIDE-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(h) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degA) + ",45 degrees.");
9539 			createDescription(id+"_c", "CROSS-RAIL...base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(Math.sqrt(Math.pow(w,2)+Math.pow(h,2))) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: 45," + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
9540 		
9541 		}
9542 		break;
9543 		case "LB": // right triangle, facing left, pointy end down
9544 		{
9545 			angleA = Math.atan2(w,h);

9560 						+" L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y + " L " +x+","+y;

9568 			createDescription(id+"_a", "TOP-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degA) + ",45 degrees.");
9569 			createDescription(id+"_b", "SIDE-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(h) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: 45," + Math.round(degA) + " degrees.");
9570 			createDescription(id+"_c", "CROSS-RAIL...base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(Math.sqrt(Math.pow(w,2)+Math.pow(h,2))) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: 45," + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
9571 		
9572 		}
9573 			break;	
9574 		case "IT":  // isosoles, pointy end up
9575 		{
9576 			angleA = Math.atan2(w/2,h);
9577 			degA = (angleA / Math.PI)*180;
9578 						
9579 			insetY = Math.sqrt(Math.pow(f/Math.tan(angleA),2)+Math.pow(f,2));
9580 			pointA = new Point(x+(w/2),y+insetY);
9581 		
9582 			angleB = Math.atan2(h,w/2);
9583 			degB = ((angleB/2) / Math.PI)*180;
9584 			
9585 			insetX = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9586 			pointB = new Point(x+insetX,y+h-f);
9587 				
9588 			pointC = new Point(x+w-insetX,y+h-f);
9589 			
9590 			pathA = "M " + (x+(w/2)) + "," + y + " l -"+(w/2)+","+ h + " L "+ pointB.x+","+pointB.y
9591 						+" L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y + " L " +(x+(w/2))+","+y;
9592 			pathB = "M " + (x+(w/2)) + "," + y + " l "+(w/2)+","+ h + " L "+ pointC.x+","+pointC.y
9593 						+" L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y + " L " +(x+(w/2))+","+y;
9594 			pathC = "M " + (x) + "," + (y+h) + " l "+w+",0 L "+ pointC.x+","+pointC.y
9595 						+" L "+ pointB.x+","+pointB.y + " L " +x+","+(y+h);
9596 						
9597 			createDescription(id+"_a", "SIDE-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(Math.sqrt(Math.pow(w/2,2)+Math.pow(h,2)))+ "  THICKNESS: " + (f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degA) + ","+Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
9598 			createDescription(id+"_b", "SIDE-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(Math.sqrt(Math.pow(w/2,2)+Math.pow(h,2))) + "  THICKNESS: " + (f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degA) + ","+Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
9599 			createDescription(id+"_c", "SILL...base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: "+ Math.round(degB)+"," + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
9600 						
9601 		}
9602 		break;
9603 		case "IB":  // isosoles, pointy end down
9604 		{
9605 			angleA = Math.atan2(w/2,h);
9606 			degA = (angleA / Math.PI)*180;
9607 			
9608 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleA);
9609 			pointA = new Point(x+(w/2),y+h-insetY);
9610 			
9611 			angleB = Math.atan2(h,w/2);
9612 			degB = ((angleB/2) / Math.PI)*180;
9613 			
9614 			insetX = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9615 			pointB = new Point(x+w-insetX,y+f);
9616 			
9617 			pointC = new Point(x+insetX,y+f);
9618 			
9619 			pathA = "M " + x + "," + y + " l "+(w/2)+","+ h + " L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y
9620 						+" L "+ pointC.x+","+pointC.y + " L " +x+","+y;
9621 			pathB = "M " + (x+w) + "," + y + " l -"+(w/2)+","+ h + " L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y
9622 						+" L "+ pointB.x+","+pointB.y + " L " +(x+w)+","+y;
9623 			pathC = "M " + x + "," + y + " l "+w+",0 L "+ pointB.x+","+pointB.y
9624 						+" L "+ pointC.x+","+pointC.y + " L " +x+","+y;
9625 						
9626 			createDescription(id+"_a", "SIDE-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(Math.sqrt(Math.pow(w/2,2)+Math.pow(h,2)))+ "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degA) + ","+Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
9627 			createDescription(id+"_b", "SIDE-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(Math.sqrt(Math.pow(w/2,2)+Math.pow(h,2))) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degA) + ","+Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
9628 			createDescription(id+"_c", "TOP-RAIL...base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: 45," + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
9629 						
9630 		
9631 		}
9632 		break;
9633 		default:
9634 			break;
9635 	}
9636 	
9637 	sideA.setAttribute("d",pathA);
9638 	sideB.setAttribute("d",pathB);
9639 	sideC.setAttribute("d",pathC);
9640 	
9641 	sideA.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
9642 	sideB.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
9643 	sideC.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
9644 	
9645 	
9646 		
9647 
9648 	
9649 
9650 }	
9651 catch(e)
9652 {
9653 	alertUser("Exception:  initMitredTriangleFrame('"+id+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ h+","+ f+",'"+ color+"','"+ type+"')");
9654 	alertUser(e);
9655 	trace(e);
9656 }	
9657 }

9661 /**
9662  * Draw trapezoid glass
9663  * 
9664  * @param id		String id
9665  * @param sashId 	String id of containing sash/frame
9666  * @param x			decimal x coordinate of containing rectangle
9667  * @param y			decimal y coordinate of containing rectangle
9668  * @param w			decimal width 
9669  * @param h			decimal height of long side
9670  * @param hs		decimal height of short side
9671  * @param f			decimal frame thickness
9672  * @param v			decimal visible inset
9673  * @param type		String LT=left/top,LB=left/bottom, RT=right/top, RB=right/bottom, 
9674  * 							IT=isosolese/top, IB=isosolese/bottom,
9675  * @return
9676  */
9677 function initGlassTrapezoid(id,sashId,x, y, w, h, hs, f /*inset*/, v /*hidden glass inset*/, type)
9678 {
9679 try
9680 {
9681 trace("initGlassTrapezoid('"+id+"','"+sashId+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ h+","+ hs+","+ f+","+ v+",'"+type+"')");
9682 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id);
9683 	var idPrefix = g("f_idprefix");
9684 	if(grp === null)
9685 	{
9686 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
9687 		grp.setAttribute("id",id);
9688 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
9689 	}
9690 	
9691 	var gls = drawing.getElementById(id+"_pane");
9692 	if(gls === null)
9693 	{
9694 		
9695 		gls = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
9696 		gls.setAttribute("id",id+"_pane");
9697 		gls.setAttribute("class","glass");
9698 		gls.setAttribute("onmouseover","expose(evt,'"+idPrefix+sashId+"',true)");
9699 		gls.setAttribute("onmouseout","expose(evt,'"+idPrefix+sashId+"',false)");
9700 		gls.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
9701 		
9702 		//These attributes don't apply to a <path>, but they feed the grid functions
9703 		gls.setAttribute("x",x);
9704 		gls.setAttribute("y",y);
9705 		gls.setAttribute("width",w);
9706 		gls.setAttribute("height",h);
9707 		
9708 		grp.appendChild(gls);
9709 	}
9710 	
9711 	var t,tText;
9712 	if(g("f_glass") == "TEMPERED")
9713 	{
9714 	trace("creating T");
9715 		t = drawing.getElementById(id+"_pane_t");
9716 		if(t == null)
9717 		{
9718 			t = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"text");
9719 			t.setAttribute("id",id+"_pane_t");
9720 			t.setAttribute("class","glass");
9721    			tText = drawing.createTextNode("T");
9722     		t.appendChild(tText);
9723 			grp.appendChild(t);			
9724 		}
9725 		switch(type)
9726 		{
9727 			case "RT":
9728 			case "LT":
9729 			case "IT":
9730 			case "LB":
9731 				t.setAttribute("x",x+w-2);
9732 				t.setAttribute("y",y+h-2);
9733 				break;
9734 				
9735 			case "RB":
9736 			case "IB":
9737 				t.setAttribute("x",x+2);
9738 				t.setAttribute("y",y+2);
9739 				break;
9740 			default:
9741 				t.setAttribute("x",x+2);
9742 				t.setAttribute("y",y+2);
9743 				break;
9744 		}
9745 	}
9746 	
9747 	var path,angleA,angleB,angleC,pointA, pointB, pointC, pointD, insetX, insetY,wV,hV, hsV,wNet,hNet, hsNet, lDiag;
9748 
9749 	switch(type)
9750 	{
9751 		case "RT":  // facing right, pointy end up
9752 		{
9753 			angleA = Math.atan2(w,(h-hs));
9754 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
9755 			pointA = new Point(x+f,y+insetY);
9756 									
9757 			angleB = Math.PI - angleA;
9758 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9759 			
9760 			pointB = new Point(x+w-f,y+(h-hs)+insetY);
9761 			
9762 			pointC = new Point(x+w-f,y+h-f);
9763 			
9764 			pointD = new Point(x+f,y+h-f);
9765 			
9766 		
9767 		}
9768 		break;
9769 		case "RB": // facing right, pointy end down
9770 		{
9771 			angleA = Math.atan2(w,(h-hs));
9772 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
9773 			pointA = new Point(x+f,y+h-insetY);
9774 			
9775 			angleB = Math.PI - angleA;
9776 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9777 			
9778 			pointB = new Point(x+w-f,y+hs-insetY);
9779 			
9780 			pointC = new Point(x+w-f,y-f);
9781 			pointD = new Point(x+f,y+f);
9782 			
9783 		}
9784 			break;
9785 		case "LT":  // facing left, pointy end up
9786 		{
9787 			angleA = Math.atan2(w,(h-hs));
9788 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
9789 			pointA = new Point(x+w-f,y+insetY);
9790 			
9791 			angleB = Math.PI - angleA;
9792 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9793 			
9794 			pointB = new Point(x+f,y+(h-hs)+insetY);
9795 			pointC = new Point(x+f,y+h-f);
9796 			pointD = new Point(x+w-f,y+h-f);
9797 		}
9798 		break;
9799 		case "LB": // facing left, pointy end down
9800 		{
9801 			angleA = Math.atan2(w,(h-hs));
9802 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
9803 			pointA = new Point(x+w-f,y+h+insetY);
9804 				
9805 			angleB = Math.PI - angleA;
9806 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9807 			
9808 			pointB = new Point(x+f,y+hs-insetY);
9809 			
9810 			
9811 			pointC = new Point(x+f,y+f);
9812 			pointD = new Point(x+w-f,y+f);
9813 		}
9814 			break;	
9815 
9816 		case "IT": // narrow end Up
9817 		{
9818 			pointA = new Point(x+((w-hs)/2),y+f);
9819 			pointB = new Point(x+f,y+h-f);
9820 			pointC = new Point(x+w-f,y+h-f);
9821 			pointD = new Point(x+w-((w-hs)/2),y+f);
9822 		}
9823 			break;	
9824 
9825 		case "IB": // narrow end Down
9826 		{
9827 			pointA = new Point(x+w-((w-hs)/2),y+h-f);
9828 			pointB = new Point(x+w-f,y+f);
9829 			pointC = new Point(x+f,y+f);
9830 			pointD = new Point(x+((w-hs)/2),y+h-f);
9831 		}
9832 			break;	
9833 		default:
9834 			break;
9835 	}
9836 	
9837 
9838 
9839 
9840 
9841 	path = "M " + pointA.x + "," + pointA.y + " L "+ pointB.x + "," + pointB.y + " L " + pointC.x + "," + pointC.y + " L " + pointD.x + "," + pointD.y + " L " + pointA.x + "," + pointA.y;
9842 	gls.setAttribute("d",path);
9843 
9844 
9845 	if(g("f_tn")!="true")
9846 	{
9847 		var desc = "WIDTH: %W%  HEIGHT: %H%  VISIBLE: %WV%X%HV%.";
9848 		desc = desc.replace(/%W%/g,inchesToInchesDim(wNet));
9849 		desc = desc.replace(/%H%/g,inchesToInchesDim(hNet));
9850 		desc = desc.replace(/%WV%/g,inchesToInchesDim(wV));
9851 		desc = desc.replace(/%HV%/g,inchesToInchesDim(hV));
9852 		createDescription(id+"_pane",desc);
9853 	}
9854 }	
9855 catch(e)
9856 {
9857 	alertUser("Exception: initGlassTrapezoid('"+id+"','"+sashId+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ h+","+ hs+","+ f+","+ v+",'"+type+"')");
9858 
9859 	alertUser(e);
9860 	trace(e);
9861 }	
9862 }

9865 
9866 /**
9867  * Draw trapezoid frame (non-mitred)
9868  * 
9869  * @param id		String id
9870  * @param x			decimal x coordinate of containing rectangle
9871  * @param y			decimal y coordinate of containing rectangle
9872  * @param w			decimal width 
9873  * @param h			decimal height of long side
9874  * @param hs		decimal height of short side
9875  * @param f			decimal frame thickness
9876  * @param sillThk	decimal sill thickness
9877  * @param color 	String web color code
9878  * @param type		String LT=left/top,LB=left/bottom, RT=right/top, RB=right/bottom, 
9879  * 							IT=isosolese/top, IB=isosolese/bottom,
9880  * @return
9881  */
9882 function initTrapezoidFrame(id, x, y, w, h, hs, f,sillThk, color, type)
9883 {
9884 try
9885 {
9886 trace("initTrapezoidFrame('"+id+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ h+","+hs+","+ f+",'"+sillThk+",'"+ color+"','"+ type+"')");
9887 
9888 	var desc = "";
9889 	var tn = g("f_tn") == "true";
9890 	// frame group
9891 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id);
9892 	if(grp === null)
9893 	{
9894 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
9895 		grp.setAttribute("id",id);
9896 		
9897 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
9898 	}
9899 
9900 	var sideA = drawing.getElementById(id+"_a");
9901 	if(sideA === null)
9902 	{
9903 		sideA = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
9904 		sideA.setAttribute("id",id+"_a");
9905 		sideA.setAttribute("class","frame");
9906 		sideA.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
9907 		
9908 		grp.appendChild(sideA);
9909 	}
9910 	
9911 	var sideB = drawing.getElementById(id+"_b");
9912 	if(sideB === null)
9913 	{
9914 		sideB = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
9915 		sideB.setAttribute("id",id+"_b");
9916 		sideB.setAttribute("class","frame");
9917 		sideB.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
9918 		
9919 		grp.appendChild(sideB);
9920 	}
9921 	
9922 	var sideC = drawing.getElementById(id+"_c");
9923 	if(sideC === null)
9924 	{
9925 		sideC = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
9926 		sideC.setAttribute("id",id+"_c");
9927 		sideC.setAttribute("class","frame");
9928 		sideC.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
9929 		
9930 		grp.appendChild(sideC);
9931 	}
9932 
9933 	var sideD = drawing.getElementById(id+"_d");
9934 	if(sideD === null)
9935 	{
9936 		sideD = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
9937 		sideD.setAttribute("id",id+"_d");
9938 		sideD.setAttribute("class","frame");
9939 		sideD.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
9940 		
9941 		grp.appendChild(sideD);
9942 	}
9943 		
9944 	var angleA,angleB,angleC,degA,degB,degC,pointA, pointB, pointC, pointD, pathA, pathB, pathC, insetX, insetY;
9945 	
9946 
9947 	switch(type)
9948 	{
9949 		case "RT":  // facing right, pointy end up
9950 		{
9951 			angleA = Math.atan2(w,(h-hs));
9952 			
9953 			degA = (angleA / Math.PI)*90;
9954 			
9955 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
9956 			
9957 			pointA = new Point(x+f,y+insetY);
9958 			
9959 							
9960 			angleB = Math.PI - angleA;
9961 			degB = (angleB / Math.PI)*90;
9962 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
9963 			
9964 			pointB = new Point(x+w-f,y+(h-hs)+insetY);
9965 			
9966 			
9967 			
9968 			
9969 			
9970 			pointC = new Point(x+w-f,y+h-sillThk);
9971 			
9972 			pointD = new Point(x+f,y+h-sillThk);
9973 			
9974 			
9975 			pathA = "M " + x + "," + y + " l "+ w+","+ (h-hs) + " L "+ pointB.x+","+pointB.y+
9976 						" L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y + " L " +x+","+y;
9977 			
9978 			pathB = "M " + (x+w) + "," + (y+h-hs) + " l 0,"+(y+hs-sillThk)+" L "+pointC.x+","+pointC.y+
9979 						" L "+ pointB.x+","+pointB.y + " L " +(x+w)+","+(y+h-hs);
9980 				
9981 			pathC = "M " + (x+w) + "," + (y+h) + " l -"+w+",0 l 0,-"+ sillThk+
9982 						" l "+ w+",0 l 0,"+sillThk;
9983 		
9984 			pathD = "M " + (x) + "," + (y) + " l 0,"+(h-sillThk)+" L "+ pointD.x+","+pointD.y+
9985 						" L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y + " L "+ (x) + "," + (y);
9986 		
9987 			createDescription(id+"_a", "HEAD-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(Math.sqrt(Math.pow(w,2)+Math.pow((h-hs),2)))  + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degA)+"," + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
9988 			createDescription(id+"_b", "SIDE-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(hs-sillThk) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
9989 			createDescription(id+"_c", "SILL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(sillThk) + ".");
9990 			createDescription(id+"_d", "SIDE-RAIL...base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(h-sillThk) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degA)+" degrees.");
9991 		
9992 		}
9993 		break;
9994 
9995 		case "LT":  // facing left, pointy end up
9996 		{
9997 			angleA = Math.atan2(w,(h-hs));
9998 			
9999 			degA = (angleA / Math.PI)*90;
10000 			
10001 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
10002 			
10003 			pointA = new Point(x+w-f,y+insetY);
10004 			
10005 			angleB = Math.PI - angleA;
10006 			degB = (angleB / Math.PI)*90;
10007 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
10008 			
10009 			pointB = new Point(x+f,y+(h-hs)+insetY);
10010 			
10011 			pointC = new Point(x+f,y+h-sillThk);
10012 			
10013 			pointD = new Point(x+w-f,y+h-sillThk);
10014 			
10015 			
10016 			pathA = "M " + (x+w) + "," + (y) + " l -"+ w+","+ (h-hs) + " L "+ pointB.x+","+pointB.y+
10017 						" L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y + " L " +(x+w)+","+(y);
10018 			
10019 			pathB = "M " + (x) + "," + (y+(h-hs)) + " l 0,"+(hs-sillThk)+" L "+pointC.x+","+pointC.y+
10020 						" L "+ pointB.x+","+pointB.y + " L " +(x)+","+(y+(h-hs));
10021 				
10022 			pathC = "M " + (x+w) + "," + (y+h) + " l -"+w+",0 l 0,-"+ sillThk+
10023 						" l "+ w+",0 l 0,"+sillThk;
10024 		
10025 			pathD = "M " + (x+w) + "," + (y+h-sillThk) + " l 0,-"+(h-sillThk)+" L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y+
10026 						" L "+ pointD.x+","+pointD.y + " L "+ (x+w) + "," + (y+h-sillThk);
10027 		
10028 			createDescription(id+"_a", "CROSS-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(Math.sqrt(Math.pow(w,2)+Math.pow((h-hs),2)))  + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degA)+"," + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
10029 			createDescription(id+"_b", "SIDE-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(hs-sillThk) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: "+Math.round(degB)+" degrees.");
10030 			createDescription(id+"_c", "SILL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(sillThk) + ".");
10031 			createDescription(id+"_d", "SIDE-RAIL...base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(h-sillThk) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: "+ Math.round(degA)+" degrees.");
10032 			
10033 		}
10034 		break;
10035 
10036 
10037 		default:
10038 			break;
10039 	}
10040 	
10041 	sideA.setAttribute("d",pathA);
10042 	sideB.setAttribute("d",pathB);
10043 	sideC.setAttribute("d",pathC);
10044 	sideD.setAttribute("d",pathD);
10045 	
10046 	sideA.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
10047 	sideB.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
10048 	sideC.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
10049 	sideD.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
10050 	
10051 	
10052 		
10053 
10054 	
10055 
10056 }	
10057 catch(e)
10058 {
10059 	alertUser("Exception:  initTrapezoidFrame('"+id+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ h+","+hs+","+ f+",'"+sillThk+",'"+ color+"','"+ type+"')");
10060 	alertUser(e);
10061 	trace(e);
10062 }	
10063 }

10066 /**
10067  * Draw trapezoid frame (mitred)
10068  * 
10069  * @param id		String id
10070  * @param x			decimal x coordinate of containing rectangle
10071  * @param y			decimal y coordinate of containing rectangle
10072  * @param w			decimal width 
10073  * @param h			decimal height of long side
10074  * @param hs		decimal height of short side
10075  * @param f			decimal frame thickness
10076  * @param color 	String web color code
10077  * @param type		String LT=left/top,LB=left/bottom, RT=right/top, RB=right/bottom, 
10078  * 							IT=isosolese/top, IB=isosolese/bottom,
10079  * @return

10405 	sideA.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
10406 	sideB.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
10407 	sideC.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
10408 	sideD.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
10409 	
10410 	
10411 		
10412 
10413 	
10414 
10415 }	
10416 catch(e)
10417 {
10418 	alertUser("Exception:  initMitredTrapezoidFrame('"+id+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ h+","+hs+","+ f+",'"+ color+"','"+ type+"')");
10419 	alertUser(e);
10420 	trace(e);
10421 }

10428 /**
10429  * Draw clip trapezoid glass
10430  * 
10431  * @param id		String id
10432  * @param sashId	String id of containing sash/frame
10433  * @param x			decimal x coordinate of containing rectangle
10434  * @param y			decimal y coordinate of containing rectangle
10435  * @param w			decimal width 
10436  * @param ws		decimal width of short side
10437  * @param h			decimal height of long side
10438  * @param hs		decimal height of short side
10439  * @param f			decimal frame thickness
10440  * @param v			decimal visible inset
10441  * @param type		String LT=left/top, RT=right/top 
10442  * @return
10443  */
10444 function initGlassClipTrap(id,sashId,x, y, w, ws, h, hs, f /*inset*/, v /*hidden glass inset*/, type)
10445 {
10446 try
10447 {
10448 trace("initGlassClipTrap('"+id+"','"+sashId+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ws+","+ h+","+ hs+","+ f+","+ v+",'"+type+"')");
10449 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id);
10450 	var idPrefix = g("f_idprefix");
10451 	if(grp === null)
10452 	{
10453 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
10454 		grp.setAttribute("id",id);
10455 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
10456 	}
10457 	
10458 	var gls = drawing.getElementById(id+"_pane");
10459 	if(gls === null)
10460 	{
10461 		
10462 		gls = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
10463 		gls.setAttribute("id",id+"_pane");
10464 		gls.setAttribute("class","glass");
10465 		gls.setAttribute("onmouseover","expose(evt,'"+idPrefix+sashId+"',true)");
10466 		gls.setAttribute("onmouseout","expose(evt,'"+idPrefix+sashId+"',false)");
10467 		gls.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
10468 		
10469 		//These attributes don't apply to a <path>, but they feed the grid functions
10470 		gls.setAttribute("x",x);
10471 		gls.setAttribute("y",y);
10472 		gls.setAttribute("width",w);
10473 		gls.setAttribute("height",h);
10474 		
10475 		grp.appendChild(gls);
10476 	}
10477 	
10478 	var t,tText;
10479 	if(g("f_glass") == "TEMPERED")
10480 	{
10481 	trace("creating T");
10482 		t = drawing.getElementById(id+"_pane_t");
10483 		if(t == null)
10484 		{
10485 			t = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"text");
10486 			t.setAttribute("id",id+"_pane_t");
10487 			t.setAttribute("class","glass");
10488    			tText = drawing.createTextNode("T");
10489     		t.appendChild(tText);
10490 			grp.appendChild(t);			
10491 		}
10492 		switch(type)
10493 		{
10494 			case "RT":
10495 			case "LT":
10496 			case "LB":
10497 				t.setAttribute("x",x+w-2);
10498 				t.setAttribute("y",y+h-2);
10499 				break;
10500 				
10501 			case "RB":
10502 				t.setAttribute("x",x+2);
10503 				t.setAttribute("y",y+2);
10504 				break;
10505 			default:
10506 				t.setAttribute("x",x+2);
10507 				t.setAttribute("y",y+2);
10508 				break;
10509 		}
10510 	}
10511 	
10512 	
10513 	var path,angleA,angleB,angleC,pointA, pointB, pointC, pointD, pointE, insetX, insetY,wV,hV, hsV,wNet,hNet, hsNet, lDiag;
10514 
10515 	switch(type)
10516 	{
10517 		case "RT":  // facing right, narrow end up
10518 		{
10519 			angleA = Math.atan2((w-ws),(h-hs))+(Math.PI/2);
10520 			insetX = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
10521 			pointA = new Point(x+ws-insetX,y+f);
10522 
10523 			angleB = Math.atan2((h-hs),(w-ws))+(Math.PI/2);
10524 			insetY = f/Math.tan((angleB/2));
10525 
10526 			pointB = new Point(x+w-f,y+(h-hs)+insetY);
10527 									
10528 			pointC = new Point(x+w-f,y+h-f);
10529 			pointD = new Point(x+f,y+h-f);
10530 			pointE = new Point(x+f,y+f);
10531 			
10532 		
10533 		}
10534 		break;
10535 		case "RB": // facing right, pointy end down
10536 		{
10537 			angleA = Math.atan2((w-ws),(h-hs))+(Math.PI/2);
10538 			insetX = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
10539 			pointA = new Point(x+ws-insetX,y+h-f);
10540 
10541 			angleB = Math.atan2((h-hs),(w-ws))+(Math.PI/2);
10542 			insetY = f/Math.tan((angleB/2));
10543 			pointB = new Point(x+w,y+hs-insetY);
10544 									
10545 			pointC = new Point(x+w-f,y+f);
10546 			pointD = new Point(x+f,y+f);
10547 			pointE = new Point(x+f,y+h-f);
10548 
10549 			
10550 		}
10551 			break;
10552 		case "LT":  // facing left, pointy end up
10553 		{
10554 			angleA = Math.atan2((w-ws),(h-hs))+(Math.PI/2);
10555 			insetX = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
10556 			pointA = new Point(x+(w-ws)+insetX,y+f);
10557 
10558 			angleB = Math.atan2((h-hs),(w-ws))+(Math.PI/2);
10559 			insetY = f/Math.tan((angleB/2));
10560 			pointB = new Point(x+f,y+(h-hs)+insetY);
10561 									
10562 			pointC = new Point(x+f,y+h-f);
10563 			pointD = new Point(x+w-f,y+h-f);
10564 			pointE = new Point(x+w-f,y+f);
10565 
10566 		}
10567 		break;
10568 		case "LB": // facing left, pointy end down
10569 		{
10570 			angleA = Math.atan2((w-ws),(h-hs))+(Math.PI/2);
10571 			insetX = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
10572 			pointA = new Point(x+(w-ws)+insetX,y+h-f);
10573 
10574 			angleB = Math.atan2((h-hs),(w-ws))+(Math.PI/2);
10575 			insetY = f/Math.tan((angleB/2));
10576 			pointB = new Point(x+f,y+hs-insetY);
10577 									
10578 			pointC = new Point(x+f,y+f);
10579 			pointD = new Point(x+w+f,y+f);
10580 			pointE = new Point(x+w+f,y+h-f);
10581 
10582 		}
10583 			break;	
10584 
10585 		default:
10586 			break;
10587 	}
10588 	
10589 
10590 
10591 
10592 
10593 	path = "M " + pointA.x + "," + pointA.y + 
10594 					" L " + pointB.x + "," + pointB.y + 
10595 					" L " + pointC.x + "," + pointC.y + 
10596 					" L " + pointD.x + "," + pointD.y + 
10597 					" L " + pointE.x + "," + pointE.y + 
10598 					" L " + pointA.x + "," + pointA.y;
10599 	gls.setAttribute("d",path);
10600 
10601 
10602 	if(g("f_tn")!="true")
10603 	{
10604 		var desc = "WIDTH: %W%  HEIGHT: %H%  VISIBLE: %WV%X%HV%.";
10605 		desc = desc.replace(/%W%/g,inchesToInchesDim(wNet));
10606 		desc = desc.replace(/%H%/g,inchesToInchesDim(hNet));
10607 		desc = desc.replace(/%WV%/g,inchesToInchesDim(wV));
10608 		desc = desc.replace(/%HV%/g,inchesToInchesDim(hV));
10609 		createDescription(id+"_pane",desc);
10610 	}
10611 }	
10612 catch(e)
10613 {
10614 	alertUser("Exception: initGlassClipTrap('"+id+"','"+sashId+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ h+","+ hs+","+ f+","+ v+",'"+type+"')");
10615 
10616 	alertUser(e);
10617 	trace(e);
10618 }	
10619 }

10623 /**
10624  * Draw clip trapezoid frame (non-mitred)
10625  * 
10626  * @param id		String id
10627  * @param x			decimal x coordinate of containing rectangle
10628  * @param y			decimal y coordinate of containing rectangle
10629  * @param w			decimal width 
10630  * @param ws		decimal width of short side
10631  * @param h			decimal height of long side
10632  * @param hs		decimal height of short side
10633  * @param f			decimal frame thickness
10634  * @param sillThk	decimal sill thickness
10635  * @param color 	String web color code
10636  * @param type		String LT=left/top, RT=right/top
10637  * @return
10638  */
10639 
10640 function initClipTrapFrame(id, x, y, w, ws, h, hs, f,sillThk, color, type)
10641 {
10642 try
10643 {
10644 trace("initClipTrapFrame('"+id+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ws+",",h+","+hs+","+ f+","+sillThk+",'"+ color+"','"+ type+"')");
10645 
10646 	var desc = "";
10647 	var tn = g("f_tn") == "true";
10648 	// frame group
10649 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id);
10650 	if(grp === null)
10651 	{
10652 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
10653 		grp.setAttribute("id",id);
10654 		
10655 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
10656 	}
10657 
10658 	var sideA = drawing.getElementById(id+"_a");
10659 	if(sideA === null)
10660 	{
10661 		sideA = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
10662 		sideA.setAttribute("id",id+"_a");
10663 		sideA.setAttribute("class","frame");
10664 		sideA.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
10665 		
10666 		grp.appendChild(sideA);
10667 	}
10668 	
10669 	var sideB = drawing.getElementById(id+"_b");
10670 	if(sideB === null)
10671 	{
10672 		sideB = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
10673 		sideB.setAttribute("id",id+"_b");
10674 		sideB.setAttribute("class","frame");
10675 		sideB.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
10676 		
10677 		grp.appendChild(sideB);
10678 	}
10679 	
10680 	var sideC = drawing.getElementById(id+"_c");
10681 	if(sideC === null)
10682 	{
10683 		sideC = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
10684 		sideC.setAttribute("id",id+"_c");
10685 		sideC.setAttribute("class","frame");
10686 		sideC.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
10687 		
10688 		grp.appendChild(sideC);
10689 	}
10690 
10691 	var sideD = drawing.getElementById(id+"_d");
10692 	if(sideD === null)
10693 	{
10694 		sideD = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
10695 		sideD.setAttribute("id",id+"_d");
10696 		sideD.setAttribute("class","frame");
10697 		sideD.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
10698 		
10699 		grp.appendChild(sideD);
10700 	}
10701 	
10702 	var sideE = drawing.getElementById(id+"_e");
10703 	if(sideE === null)
10704 	{
10705 		sideE = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
10706 		sideE.setAttribute("id",id+"_e");
10707 		sideE.setAttribute("class","frame");
10708 		sideE.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
10709 		
10710 		grp.appendChild(sideE);
10711 	}		
10712 	var angleA,angleB,angleC,degA,degB,degC,pointA, pointB, pointC, pointD, pointE, pathA, pathB, pathC, pathD, pathE, insetX, insetY;
10713 	
10714 
10715 	switch(type)
10716 	{
10717 		case "RT":  // facing right, narrow end up
10718 		{
10719 		
10720 			angleA = Math.atan2((w-ws),(h-hs))+(Math.PI/2);
10721 			insetX = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
10722 			pointA = new Point(x+ws-insetX,y+f);
10723 			degA = (angleA / Math.PI)*90;
10724 
10725 			angleB = Math.atan2((h-hs),(w-ws))+(Math.PI/2);
10726 			insetY = f/Math.tan((angleB/2));
10727 			pointB = new Point(x+w-f,y+(h-hs)+insetY);
10728 			degB = (angleB / Math.PI)*90;
10729 			
10730 			pointC = new Point(x+w-f,y+h-sillThk);
10731 			
10732 			pointD = new Point(x+f,y+h-sillThk);
10733 
10734 			pointE = new Point(x+f,y+f);
10735 			
10736 			pathA = "M " + (x+ws) + "," + y + " L "+ (x+w)+","+ (y+(h-hs)) + 
10737 						" L "+ pointB.x+","+pointB.y+
10738 						" L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y + " L " +(x+ws)+","+y;
10739 			
10740 			pathB = "M " + (x+w) + "," + (y+h-hs) + " l 0,"+(hs-sillThk)+
10741 						" L "+pointC.x+","+pointC.y+
10742 						" L "+ pointB.x+","+pointB.y + 
10743 						" L " +(x+w)+","+(y+h-hs);
10744 				
10745 			pathC = "M " + (x+w) + "," + (y+h) + " l -"+w+",0 l 0,-"+ sillThk+
10746 						" l "+ w+",0 l 0,"+sillThk;
10747 		
10748 			pathD = "M " + (x) + "," + (y+h-sillThk) + " l 0,-"+(h-sillThk)+" L "+ pointE.x+","+pointE.y+
10749 						" L "+ pointD.x+","+pointD.y + " L "+ (x) + "," + (y+h-sillThk);
10750 
10751 			pathE = "M " + (x) + "," + (y) + " l "+(ws)+",0 L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y+
10752 						" L "+ pointE.x+","+pointE.y + " L "+ (x) + "," + (y);
10753 		
10754 			createDescription(id+"_a", "CROSS-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(Math.sqrt(Math.pow((w-ws),2)+Math.pow((h-hs),2)))  + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degA)+"," + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
10755 			createDescription(id+"_e", "HEAD-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(ws) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: 45," + Math.round(degA) + " degrees.");
10756 			createDescription(id+"_b", "SIDE-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(hs-sillThk) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
10757 			createDescription(id+"_c", "SILL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(sillThk) + ".");
10758 			createDescription(id+"_d", "SIDE-RAIL...base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(h-sillThk) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: 45 degrees.");
10759 		
10760 		}
10761 		break;
10762 
10763 		case "LT":  // facing left, pointy end up
10764 		{
10765 			angleA = Math.atan2((w-ws),(h-hs))+(Math.PI/2);
10766 			insetX = f/Math.tan(angleA/2);
10767 			pointA = new Point(x+(w-ws)+insetX,y+f);
10768 			degA = (angleA / Math.PI)*90;
10769 
10770 			angleB = Math.atan2((h-hs),(w-ws))+(Math.PI/2);
10771 			insetY = f/Math.tan((angleB/2));
10772 			pointB = new Point(x+f,y+(h-hs)+insetY);
10773 			degB = (angleB / Math.PI)*90;
10774 			
10775 			pointC = new Point(x+f,y+h-sillThk);
10776 			
10777 			pointD = new Point(x+w-f,y+h-sillThk);
10778 
10779 			pointE = new Point(x+w-f,y+f);
10780 			
10781 			pathA = "M " + (x+(w-ws)) + "," + y + " L "+ (x)+","+ (y+(h-hs)) + 
10782 						" L "+ pointB.x+","+pointB.y+
10783 						" L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y + " L " +(x+(w-ws))+","+y;
10784 			
10785 			pathB = "M " + (x) + "," + (y+(h-hs)) + " l 0,"+(hs-sillThk)+
10786 						" L "+pointC.x+","+pointC.y+
10787 						" L "+ pointB.x+","+pointB.y + 
10788 						" L " +(x)+","+(y+h-hs);
10789 				
10790 			pathC = "M " + (x+w) + "," + (y+h) + " l -"+w+",0 l 0,-"+ sillThk+
10791 						" l "+ w+",0 l 0,"+sillThk;
10792 		
10793 			pathD = "M " + (x+w) + "," + (y+h-sillThk) + " l 0,-"+(h-sillThk)+" L "+ pointE.x+","+pointE.y+
10794 						" L "+ pointD.x+","+pointD.y + " L "+ (x+w) + "," + (y+h-sillThk);
10795 
10796 			pathE = "M " + (x+w) + "," + (y) + " l -"+ws+",0  L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y+
10797 						" L "+ pointE.x+","+pointE.y + " L "+ (x+w) + "," + (y);
10798 		
10799 			createDescription(id+"_a", "CROSS-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(Math.sqrt(Math.pow((w-ws),2)+Math.pow((h-hs),2)))  + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degA)+"," + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
10800 			createDescription(id+"_e", "HEAD-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(ws) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: 45," + Math.round(degA) + " degrees.");
10801 			createDescription(id+"_b", "SIDE-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(hs) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
10802 			createDescription(id+"_c", "SILL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + ".");
10803 			createDescription(id+"_d", "SIDE-RAIL...base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(h) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: 45 degrees.");
10804 		}
10805 		break;
10806 
10807 
10808 		default:
10809 			break;
10810 	}
10811 	
10812 	sideA.setAttribute("d",pathA);
10813 	sideB.setAttribute("d",pathB);
10814 	sideC.setAttribute("d",pathC);
10815 	sideD.setAttribute("d",pathD);
10816 	sideE.setAttribute("d",pathE);
10817 	
10818 	sideA.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
10819 	sideB.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
10820 	sideC.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
10821 	sideD.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
10822 	sideE.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
10823 
10824 }	
10825 catch(e)
10826 {
10827 	alertUser("Exception:  initClipTrapFrame('"+id+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ h+","+hs+","+ f+","+sillThk+",'"+ color+"','"+ type+"')");
10828 	alertUser(e);
10829 	trace(e);
10830 }	
10831 }

10843  * @param h			decimal height of long side

11144 /**
11145  * Draw pentagon glass
11146  * 
11147  * @param id		String id
11148  * @param sashId	String id of containing sash/frame
11149  * @param x			decimal x coordinate of containing rectangle
11150  * @param y			decimal y coordinate of containing rectangle
11151  * @param w			decimal width 
11152  * @param h			decimal height of long side
11153  * @param hs		decimal height of short side
11154  * @param f			decimal frame thickness
11155  * @param v			decimal visible glass inset
11156  * @param type		String T=top, B=bottom
11157  * @return
11158  */
11159 
11160 
11161 function initGlassHomePlate(id,sashId,x, y, w, h, hs, f /*inset*/, v /*hidden glass inset*/, type)
11162 {
11163 try
11164 {
11165 trace("initGlassHomePlate('"+id+"','"+sashId+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ h+","+ hs+","+ f+","+ v+",'"+type+"')");
11166 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id);
11167 	var idPrefix = g("f_idprefix");
11168 	if(grp === null)
11169 	{
11170 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
11171 		grp.setAttribute("id",id);
11172 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
11173 	}
11174 	
11175 	var gls = drawing.getElementById(id+"_pane");
11176 	if(gls === null)
11177 	{
11178 		
11179 		gls = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
11180 		gls.setAttribute("id",id+"_pane");
11181 		gls.setAttribute("class","glass");
11182 		gls.setAttribute("onmouseover","expose(evt,'"+idPrefix+sashId+"',true)");
11183 		gls.setAttribute("onmouseout","expose(evt,'"+idPrefix+sashId+"',false)");
11184 		gls.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
11185 		
11186 		//These attributes don't apply to a <path>, but they feed the grid functions
11187 		gls.setAttribute("x",x);
11188 		gls.setAttribute("y",y);
11189 		gls.setAttribute("width",w);
11190 		gls.setAttribute("height",h);
11191 		
11192 		grp.appendChild(gls);
11193 	}
11194 	
11195 	var t,tText;
11196 	if(g("f_glass") == "TEMPERED")
11197 	{
11198 	trace("creating T");
11199 		t = drawing.getElementById(id+"_pane_t");
11200 		if(t == null)
11201 		{
11202 			t = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"text");
11203 			t.setAttribute("id",id+"_pane_t");
11204 			t.setAttribute("class","glass");
11205    			tText = drawing.createTextNode("T");
11206     		t.appendChild(tText);
11207 			grp.appendChild(t);			
11208 		}
11209 		switch(type)
11210 		{
11211 			case "T":
11212 				t.setAttribute("x",x+w-2);
11213 				t.setAttribute("y",y+h-2);
11214 				break;
11215 				
11216 			case "B":
11217 				t.setAttribute("x",x+2);
11218 				t.setAttribute("y",y+2);
11219 				break;
11220 			default:
11221 				t.setAttribute("x",x+2);
11222 				t.setAttribute("y",y+2);
11223 				break;
11224 		}
11225 	}
11226 	
11227 	
11228 	
11229 	var path,angleA,angleB,angleC,angleD,angleE,pointA, pointB, pointC, pointD, pointE, insetX, insetY,wV,hV, hsV,wNet,hNet, hsNet;
11230 
11231 	switch(type)
11232 	{
11233 		case "T":  // pointy end up
11234 		{
11235 			angleA = Math.atan2(w/2,h-hs);
11236 			insetY = Math.sqrt(Math.pow(f/Math.tan(angleA),2)+Math.pow(f,2));
11237 			pointA = new Point(x+(w/2),y+insetY);
11238 									
11239 			angleE = angleB = Math.PI - angleA;
11240 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
11241 			
11242 			pointB = new Point(x+w-f,y+(h-hs)+insetY);
11243 			pointE = new Point(x+f,y+(h-hs)+insetY);
11244 			
11245 			pointC = new Point(x+w-f,y+h-f);
11246 			
11247 			pointD = new Point(x+f,y+h-f);
11248 			
11249 		
11250 		}
11251 		break;
11252 		case "B": // pointy end down
11253 		{
11254 			angleA = Math.atan2(w/2,h-hs);
11255 			insetY = Math.sqrt(Math.pow(f/Math.tan(angleA),2)+Math.pow(f,2));
11256 			pointA = new Point(x+(w/2),y+h-insetY);
11257 			
11258 			angleE = angleB = Math.PI - angleA;
11259 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
11260 			
11261 			pointB = new Point(x+f,y+(hs)-insetY);
11262 			pointE = new Point(x+w-f,y+(hs)-insetY);
11263 			
11264 			pointC = new Point(x+f,y+f);
11265 			
11266 			pointD = new Point(x+w-f,y+f);
11267 			
11268 		}
11269 			break;
11270 
11271 		default:
11272 			break;
11273 	}
11274 	
11275 
11276 
11277 
11278 
11279 	path = "M " + pointA.x + "," + pointA.y + " L "+ pointB.x + "," + pointB.y + " L " + 
11280 				pointC.x + "," + pointC.y + " L " + pointD.x + "," + pointD.y + " L " + pointE.x + "," + pointE.y +
11281 				 " L " + pointA.x + "," + pointA.y;
11282 	trace("glass path="+path);
11283 	gls.setAttribute("d",path);
11284 
11285 
11286 	if(g("f_tn")!="true")
11287 	{
11288 		var desc = "WIDTH: %W%  HEIGHT: %H%  VISIBLE: %WV%X%HV%.";
11289 		desc = desc.replace(/%W%/g,inchesToInchesDim(wNet));
11290 		desc = desc.replace(/%H%/g,inchesToInchesDim(hNet));
11291 		desc = desc.replace(/%WV%/g,inchesToInchesDim(wV));
11292 		desc = desc.replace(/%HV%/g,inchesToInchesDim(hV));
11293 		createDescription(id+"_pane",desc);
11294 	}
11295 }	
11296 catch(e)
11297 {
11298 	alertUser("Exception: initGlassHomePlate('"+id+"','"+sashId+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ h+","+ hs+","+ f+","+ v+",'"+type+"')");
11299 
11300 	alertUser(e);
11301 	trace(e);
11302 }	
11303 } 
11304 
11305 
11306 
11307 /**
11308  * Draw pentagon frame (non-mitred)
11309  * 
11310  * @param id		String id
11311  * @param x			decimal x coordinate of containing rectangle
11312  * @param y			decimal y coordinate of containing rectangle
11313  * @param w			decimal width 
11314  * @param h			decimal height of long side
11315  * @param hs		decimal height of short side
11316  * @param f			decimal frame thickness
11317  * @param sillThk	decimal sill thickness
11318  * @param color		String web color code
11319  * @param type		String T=top, B=bottom
11320  * @return
11321  */
11322 function initHomePlateFrame(id, x, y, w, h, hs, f,sillThk, color, type)
11323 {
11324 try
11325 {
11326 trace("initHomePlateFrame('"+id+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w+","+ h+","+hs+","+ f+","+sillThk+",'"+ color+"','"+ type+"')");
11327 
11328 	var desc = "";
11329 	var tn = g("f_tn") == "true";
11330 	// frame group
11331 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id);
11332 	if(grp === null)
11333 	{
11334 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
11335 		grp.setAttribute("id",id);
11336 		
11337 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
11338 	}
11339 
11340 	var sideA = drawing.getElementById(id+"_a");
11341 	if(sideA === null)
11342 	{
11343 		sideA = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
11344 		sideA.setAttribute("id",id+"_a");
11345 		sideA.setAttribute("class","frame");
11346 		sideA.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
11347 		
11348 		grp.appendChild(sideA);
11349 	}
11350 	
11351 	var sideB = drawing.getElementById(id+"_b");
11352 	if(sideB === null)
11353 	{
11354 		sideB = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
11355 		sideB.setAttribute("id",id+"_b");
11356 		sideB.setAttribute("class","frame");
11357 		sideB.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
11358 		
11359 		grp.appendChild(sideB);
11360 	}
11361

11363 	if(sideC === null)
11364 	{
11365 		sideC = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
11366 		sideC.setAttribute("id",id+"_c");
11367 		sideC.setAttribute("class","frame");
11368 		sideC.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
11369 		
11370 		grp.appendChild(sideC);
11371 	}
11372 
11373 	var sideD = drawing.getElementById(id+"_d");
11374 	if(sideD === null)
11375 	{
11376 		sideD = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
11377 		sideD.setAttribute("id",id+"_d");
11378 		sideD.setAttribute("class","frame");
11379 		sideD.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
11380 		
11381 		grp.appendChild(sideD);
11382 	}
11383 
11384 	var sideE = drawing.getElementById(id+"_e");
11385 	if(sideE === null)
11386 	{
11387 		sideE = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
11388 		sideE.setAttribute("id",id+"_e");
11389 		sideE.setAttribute("class","frame");
11390 		sideE.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
11391 		
11392 		grp.appendChild(sideE);
11393 	}
11394 		
11395 	var angleA,angleB,angleC,angleEdegA,degB,degC,degE, pointA, pointB, pointC, pointD, pointE, pathA, pathB, pathC, pathD, pathE, insetX, insetY;
11396 	
11397 
11398 	switch(type)
11399 	{
11400 		case "T":  // pointy end up
11401 		{
11402 		
11403 			angleA = Math.atan2(w/2,(h-hs));
11404 						
11405 			insetY = Math.sqrt(Math.pow(f/Math.tan(angleA),2)+Math.pow(f,2));
11406 			pointA = new Point(x+(w/2),y+insetY);
11407 				
11408 			degA = (angleA / Math.PI)*90;
11409 			
11410 										
11411 			angleB = angleE = Math.PI - angleA;
11412 			degB = degE = (angleB / Math.PI)*90;
11413 			insetY = f/Math.tan(angleB/2);
11414 			
11415 			pointB = new Point(x+w-f,y+(h-hs)+insetY);
11416 			pointE = new Point(x+f,y+(h-hs)+insetY);
11417 				
11418 			
11419 			pointC = new Point(x+w-f,y+h-sillThk);
11420 			
11421 			pointD = new Point(x+f,y+h-sillThk);
11422 			
11423 			
11424 			pathA = "M " + (x+(w/2)) + "," + y + " l "+ (w/2)+","+ (h-hs) + " L "+ pointB.x+","+pointB.y+
11425 						" L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y + " L " +(x+(w/2))+","+y;
11426 			trace("pathA="+pathA);	
11427 			
11428 			pathB = "M " + (x+w) + "," + (y+h-hs) + " l 0,"+(hs-sillThk)+" L "+pointC.x+","+pointC.y+
11429 						" L "+ pointB.x+","+pointB.y + " L " +(x+w)+","+(y+h-hs);
11430 			trace("pathB="+pathB);	
11431 			
11432 			pathC = "M " + (x+w) + "," + (y+h) + " l -"+w+",0 l 0,-"+ sillThk+
11433 						" l "+ w+",0 l 0,"+sillThk;
11434 			trace("pathC="+pathC);	
11435 		
11436 			pathD = "M " + (x) + "," + (y+h-hs) + " l 0,"+(hs-sillThk)+" L "+ pointD.x+","+pointD.y+
11437 						" L "+ pointE.x+","+pointE.y + " L "+ (x) + "," + (y+h-hs);
11438 			trace("pathD="+pathD);	
11439 
11440 			pathE = "M " + (x) + "," + (y+h-hs) + " l "+(w/2)+",-"+(h-hs)+" L "+ pointA.x+","+pointA.y+
11441 						" L "+ pointE.x+","+pointE.y + " L "+ (x) + "," + (y+h-hs);
11442 			trace("pathE="+pathE);	
11443 		
11444 			createDescription(id+"_a", "HEAD-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(Math.sqrt(Math.pow(w,2)+Math.pow((h-hs),2)))  + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degA)+"," + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
11445 			createDescription(id+"_e", "HEAD-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(Math.sqrt(Math.pow(w,2)+Math.pow((h-hs),2)))  + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degA)+"," + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
11446 			createDescription(id+"_b", "SIDE-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(hs-sillThk) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
11447 			createDescription(id+"_d", "SIDE-RAIL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(hs-sillThk) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: " + Math.round(degB) + " degrees.");
11448 			createDescription(id+"_c", "SILL... base LENGTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w) + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(sillThk) + ".");
11449 		
11450 		}
11451 		break;
11452 
11453 
11454 		default:
11455 			break;
11456 	}
11457 	
11458 	sideA.setAttribute("d",pathA);
11459 	sideB.setAttribute("d",pathB);
11460 	sideC.setAttribute("d",pathC);
11461 	sideD.setAttribute("d",pathD);
11462 	sideE.setAttribute("d",pathE);
11463 	
11464 	sideA.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
11465 	sideB.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
11466 	sideC.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
11467 	sideD.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
11468 	sideE.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");

11470 	
11471 		
11472 
11473 	
11474

11641 			pointE = new Point(x+f,y-hs+insetY);

11722 /**
11723  * Draw octagon glass
11724  * 
11725  * @param id		String id
11726  * @param sashId	String id of containing sash/frame
11727  * @param x			decimal x coordinate of containing rectangle
11728  * @param y			decimal y coordinate of containing rectangle
11729  * @param d			decimal diameter/width 
11730  * @param f			decimal frame thickness
11731  * @param v			decimal visible glass inset
11732  * @return
11733  */
11734 function initGlassOctagon(id,sashId,x, y, d, f /*inset*/, v /*hidden glass inset*/)
11735 {
11736 try
11737 {
11738 trace("initGlassOctagon('"+id+"','"+sashId+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ d+","+ f+","+ v+")");
11739 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id);
11740 	var idPrefix = g("f_idprefix");
11741 	if(grp === null)
11742 	{
11743 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
11744 		grp.setAttribute("id",id);
11745 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
11746 	}
11747 	
11748 	var gls = drawing.getElementById(id+"_pane");
11749 	if(gls === null)
11750 	{
11751 		
11752 		gls = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
11753 		gls.setAttribute("id",id+"_pane");
11754 		gls.setAttribute("class","glass");
11755 		gls.setAttribute("onmouseover","expose(evt,'"+idPrefix+sashId+"',true)");
11756 		gls.setAttribute("onmouseout","expose(evt,'"+idPrefix+sashId+"',false)");
11757 		gls.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
11758 	//These attributes don't apply to a <path>, but they feed the grid functions
11759 		gls.setAttribute("x",x);
11760 		gls.setAttribute("y",y);
11761 		gls.setAttribute("width",d);
11762 		gls.setAttribute("height",d);
11763 		
11764 		
11765 		grp.appendChild(gls);
11766 	}
11767 	
11768 	var s = (d-(2*f))*.414211;
11769 	var sd = Math.sqrt(Math.pow(s,2)/2);
11770 	
11771 	
11772 	insetXY = Math.tan(Math.PI/8)*f;
11773 	
11774 	var point1 = new Point(x+f+sd+insetXY, y+f);
11775 	var point2 = new Point(x+f+sd+s-insetXY, y+f);
11776 	var point3 = new Point(x+f+sd+s+sd, y+f+sd+insetXY);
11777 	var point4 = new Point(x+f+sd+s+sd, y+f+sd+s-insetXY);
11778 	var point5 = new Point(x+f+sd+s-insetXY, y+f+sd+s+sd);
11779 	var point6 = new Point(x+f+sd+insetXY, y+f+sd+s+sd);
11780 	var point7 = new Point(x+f, y+f+sd+s-insetXY);
11781 	var point8 = new Point(x+f, y+f+sd+insetXY);
11782 	
11783 
11784 
11785 	path = 
11786 		"M " +	point1.x + "," + point1.y + 
11787 		" L "+  point2.x + "," + point2.y + 
11788 		" L "+  point3.x + "," + point3.y +

12059 /**
12060  * Embed a submodel drawing
12061  * 
12062  * @param pos		integer ordinal 
12063  * @param x			decimal x coordinate
12064  * @param y			decimal y coordinate
12065  * @param w			decimal width
12066  * @param h			decimal height
12067  * @return
12068  */
12069 function embedSubmodel(pos,x,y,w,h)
12070 {
12071 	var url = g("f_POS"+pos+"_IMGURL")
12072 	var pn = g("f_POS"+pos+"_PN");
12073 	
12074 	if(g("f_applet") == "true")
12075 	{
12076 		embedSubmodelSvg(url,pos,x,y,w,h,pn);
12077 	}
12078 	else
12079 	{
12080 		embedSubmodelImage(url,pos,x,y,w,h);
12081 	}
12082 }

12084 /**
12085  * Embed a submodel drawing SVG
12086  * 
12087  * @param url 		String url to generate SVG
12088  * @param pos		integer ordinal 
12089  * @param x			decimal x coordinate
12090  * @param y			decimal y coordinate
12091  * @param w			decimal width
12092  * @param h			decimal height
12093  * @param pn		String product ID
12094  * @return
12095  */
12096 function embedSubmodelSvg(url,pos,x,y,w,h,pn)
12097 {
12098 try{
12099 
12100 	var mulledSet = null;
12101 	if(g("f_mulling") == "true")
12102 	{
12103 		mulledSet = MulledSet.getInstance(g("f_order"));
12104 		mulledSet.setPosition(pos,x,y);
12105 		return;
12106 	}
12107 	
12108 	trace("embedSubmodelSvg('"+url+"',"+pos+","+x+","+y+","+w+","+h+")");
12109 	var grpWindow = drawing.getElementById("window");
12110 	if(grpWindow === null)
12111 	{
12112 		alert("<g id=window ... is required in all drawings.");
12113 		return;
12114 	}
12115 // Generate Download Progress
12116 	var	grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
12117 	grp.setAttribute("id","p" + pos);
12118 	grp.setAttribute("transform","translate("+x+","+y+")");
12119 	
12120 	var	progress = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
12121 	
12122 	progress.setAttribute("id","p" + pos + "_PROGRESS");
12123 	progress.setAttribute("transform","translate("+(w/2)+","+(h/2)+")");
12124 
12125 	var use = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"use");
12126 	use.setAttribute("id","p" + pos + "_PROGRESS_WHEEL");
12127 	use.setAttributeNS(xlinkNS,"href","#progress");
12128 	use.setAttribute("transform","translate(12,2)");
12129 	use.setAttribute("visibility","hidden");
12130 	var text = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"text");
12131 	text.setAttribute("x","12");
12132 	text.setAttribute("y","3");
12133 	text.setAttribute("class","prod");
12134 	var textContent = drawing.createTextNode(pn);
12135 	text.appendChild(textContent);
12136 	
12137 	progress.appendChild(use);
12138 	progress.appendChild(text);
12139 	
12140 	grp.appendChild(progress);
12141 
12142 	applet.registerVertElement("p0_V_SEAM_"+pos,
12143 								"p0",
12144 								x,
12145 								gN("v_mull_thk"),							 	
12146 								null);
12147 
12148 	
12149 	grpWindow.appendChild(grp);
12150 	
12151 	applet.addEmbed("p" + pos, url);
12152 	
12153 
12154 }catch(e)
12155 {
12156 	alertUser("Exception:  embedSubmodelSvg('"+url+"',"+pos+","+x+","+y+","+w+","+h+")");
12157 	alertUser(e);
12158 	trace(e);
12159 }			
12160 }

12222 /**
12223  * Draw ellipse glass
12224  * 
12225  * @param id		String id
12226  * @param sashId	String id of containing sash/frame
12227  * @param x			decimal x coordinate of containing rectangle
12228  * @param y			decimal y coordinate of containing rectangle
12229  * @param d			decimal diameter/width 
12230  * @param f			decimal frame thickness
12231  * @param v			decimal visible glass inset
12232  * @return
12233  */
12234 function initGlassEllipse(id,sashId,x, y, w, h, f /*inset*/, v /*hidden glass inset*/)
12235 {
12236 try
12237 {
12238 trace("initGlassEllipse('"+id+"','"+sashId+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w +"," +h +","+ f+","+ v+")");
12239 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id);
12240 	var idPrefix = g("f_idprefix");
12241 	if(grp === null)
12242 	{
12243 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
12244 		grp.setAttribute("id",id);
12245 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
12246 	}
12247 sss	
12248 	
12249 	var ellipse = drawing.getElementById(id+"_pane");
12250 	if(ellipse === null)
12251 	{
12252 		trace("creating glass");
12253 	
12254 		ellipse = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
12255 		ellipse.setAttribute("id",id+"_pane");
12256 		ellipse.setAttribute("class","glass");
12257 		ellipse.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
12258 		ellipse.setAttribute("onmouseover","expose(evt,'"+idPrefix+sashId+"',true)");
12259 		ellipse.setAttribute("onmouseout","expose(evt,'"+idPrefix+sashId+"',false)");
12260 			//These attributes don't apply to a <path>, but they feed the grid functions
12261 		ellipse.setAttribute("x",x);
12262 		ellipse.setAttribute("y",y);
12263 		ellipse.setAttribute("width",w);
12264 		ellipse.setAttribute("height",h);
12265 		
12266 		grp.appendChild(ellipse);
12267 	}
12268 	var t,tText;
12269 	if(g("f_glass") == "TEMPERED")
12270 	{
12271 		t = drawing.getElementById(id+"_pane_t");
12272 		if(t == null)
12273 		{
12274 			t = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"text");
12275 			t.setAttribute("id",id+"_pane_t");
12276 			t.setAttribute("class","glass");
12277    			tText = drawing.createTextNode("T");
12278     		t.appendChild(tText);
12279 			grp.appendChild(t);			
12280 		}
12281 		t.setAttribute("x",x+w/2);
12282 		t.setAttribute("y",y+h-2);
12283 	}
12284 
12285 
12286 	var path = 
12287 		" M " + (x+f) + "," + (y+(h/2)) +
12288 		" A " + ((w-(2*f))/2) +","+((h-(2*f))/2)+" 0 1,0 "+ (x+f) + "," + (y+(h/2)-.001)+
12289 		" l 0,.001";
12290 	
12291 	trace("ellipse path="+path);	  
12292 	ellipse.setAttribute("d",path);
12293 	if(g("f_tn")!="true")
12294 	{
12295 		createDescription(id+"_pane", "GLASS ... base WIDTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w-f)  +"  HEIGHT: " + inchesToInchesDim(h-f)  + "  VISSIBLE: " + inchesToInchesDim(w-f-v) + "," + inchesToInchesDim(h-f-v) + ".");
12296 	}
12297 
12298 }	
12299 catch(e)
12300 {
12301 	alertUser("Exception: initGlassEllipse('"+id+"','"+sashId+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w +","+ h +","+ f+","+ v+")");
12302 
12303 	alertUser(e);
12304 	trace(e);
12305 }	
12306 }

12310 /**

12352 	trace("creating frame bottom");
12353 		ellipseB = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
12354 		ellipseB.setAttribute("id",id+"_frame_bottom");
12355 		ellipseB.setAttribute("class","frame");
12356 		ellipseB.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
12357 		grp.appendChild(ellipseB);
12358 	}
12359 
12360 	var pathT = 
12361 		"M " +	(x) + "," + (y+(h/2)) +
12362 		" A " + (w/2) +","+(h/2)+" 0 0,1 "+ (x+w) + "," + (y+(h/2)) +
12363 		" l -"+f+ ",0 " +
12364 		" A " + ((w-(2*f))/2) +","+((h-(2*f))/2)+" 0 0,0 "+ (x+f) + "," + (y+(h/2))+
12365 		" l -" + (f) + ",0";
12366 
12367 	var pathB = 
12368 		"M " +	(x) + "," + (y+(h/2)) +
12369 		" A " + (w/2) +","+(h/2)+" 0 0,0 "+ (x+w) + "," + (y+(h/2)) +
12370 		" l -"+f+ ",0 " +
12371 		" A " + ((w-(2*f))/2) +","+((h-(2*f))/2)+" 0 0,1 "+ (x+f) + "," + (y+(h/2))+
12372 		" l -" + (f) + ",0";
12373 	
12374 			  
12375 	trace("ellipse frame top path="+pathT);	  
12376 	ellipseT.setAttribute("d",pathT);
12377 	ellipseT.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
12378 	
12379 	trace("ellipse frame bot path="+pathB);	  
12380 	ellipseB.setAttribute("d",pathB);
12381 	ellipseB.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
12382 
12383 	if(g("f_tn")!="true")
12384 	{
12385 		createDescription(id,"FRAME ... base WIDTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w)  +"  HEIGHT: " + inchesToInchesDim(h)  + "  THICKNESS: " + inchesToInchesDim(f) + "   MITRE: 67.5 degrees.");
12386 	}
12387 
12388 }	
12389 catch(e)
12390 {
12391 	alertUser("Exception:  initEllipseFrame('"+id+"',"+x+","+ y+","+ w +","+ h +","+ f+",'"+ color+"')");
12392 	alertUser(e);
12393 	trace(e);
12394 }	
12395 }
