12401 /**
12402  * Draw 3-centered arch glass
12403  * 
12404  * @param id		String id
12405  * @param sashId	String id of containing sash/frame
12406  * @param x			decimal x coordinate of containing rectangle
12407  * @param y			decimal y coordinate of containing rectangle
12408  * @param w			decimal width  
12409  * @param h			decimal height 
12410  * @param hleg		decimal height legs 
12411  * @param inset		decimal visible glass inset
12412  * @param segType	F=full, L=left qtr-round, R=right qtr-round
12413  * @return
12414  */
12415 function initGlass3CentredArch(id, idFrame, xParm, yParm, wParm, hParm, hlegParm, inset, segType)
12416 {
12417 // segType: F=full, L=left half, R=right half
12418 
12419 	trace("initGlass3CentredArch('"+id+"','"+idFrame+"',"+xParm+","+ yParm+","+ wParm+","+ hParm+","+ hlegParm+","+ inset+",'"+segType+"'");
12420 
12421 try{	
12422 
12423 	var x = xParm+inset;
12424 	var y = yParm + inset;
12425 	var w = segType == 'F' ? wParm - (2*inset) : wParm*2 - (4*inset);
12426 	var h = hlegParm === 0 ? hParm-(2*inset) : hParm - inset;
12427 	var h2 = hlegParm === 0 ? 0 : hlegParm - inset;
12428 	
12429 
12430 
12431 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id);
12432 	var idPrefix = g("f_idprefix");
12433 	if(grp === null)
12434 	{
12435 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
12436 		grp.setAttribute("id",id);
12437 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
12438 	}
12439 	
12440 	
12441 	var gls = drawing.getElementById(id+"_pane");
12442 	if(gls === null)
12443 	{
12444 		trace("creating glass");
12445 	
12446 		gls = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
12447 		gls.setAttribute("id",id+"_pane");
12448 		gls.setAttribute("class","glass");
12449 		gls.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
12450 		gls.setAttribute("onmouseover","expose(evt,'"+idPrefix+idFrame+"',true)");
12451 		gls.setAttribute("onmouseout","expose(evt,'"+idPrefix+idFrame+"',false)");
12452 			//These attributes don't apply to a <path>, but they feed the grid functions
12453 		gls.setAttribute("x",x);
12454 		gls.setAttribute("y",y);
12455 		gls.setAttribute("width",segType=="F"?w:w/2);
12456 		gls.setAttribute("height",h+h2);
12457 		gls.setAttribute("shape","3CTRARC");
12458 		
12459 		grp.appendChild(gls);
12460 	}
12461 
12462 	var r1,r2,r3,af,afBisectR,afAngle,afBisectX,afBisectY,gAngle,hAngle,hHyp,hX,fPoint,gPoint,hPoint,aAngle,jAngle,jPoint,kPoint,path;
12463 	
12464 		
12465 with(Math)
12466 {
12467 
12468 	aAngle = Math.atan2(h,w/2);
12469 	
12470 	r2 = (w/2) - h;
12471 	fPoint = new Point(x+(w/2) - (Math.cos(aAngle)*r2), (y+Math.sin(aAngle)*r2));
12472 	 
12473 	afBisectR = (sqrt(pow(fPoint.x-x,2)+pow(y+h-fPoint.y,2)))/2; 
12474 	trace("afBisectR="+afBisectR);
12475 	afBisectX = cos(aAngle)*afBisectR + x;	
12476 	afBisectY = y+h-sin(aAngle)*afBisectR;
12477 	
12478 	gPoint=new Point(x+w/2, afBisectY + tan((PI/2)-aAngle)*(x+(w/2)-afBisectX));
12479 	trace("gPoint=" + gPoint.x+","+gPoint.y);
12480 	r1 = y-gPoint.y;
12481 	trace("r1="+r1);
12482 	
12483 	
12484 	gAngle = atan2(gPoint.x-afBisectX,gPoint.y-afBisectY);
12485 	hPoint = new Point(x+w/2-tan(gAngle)*(gPoint.y-h-y),y+h);
12486 	trace("hPoint="+hPoint.x+","+hPoint.y);
12487 	r3 = hPoint.x - x;
12488 	hAngle = (PI/2) - gAngle;
12489 
12490 	jPoint = new Point(hPoint.x - sin(gAngle)*r3,hPoint.y-cos(gAngle)*r3);
12491 	kPoint = new Point(x+w-(jPoint.x-x), jPoint.y);
12492 }
12493 
12494 if(h2===0)
12495 {
12496 	switch(segType)
12497 	{
12498 		case 'F':
12499 		 	path = 
12500 			" M " + (x) + "," + (y+h) +
12501 			" A " + (r3) +","+(r3)+" 0 0,1 "+ (jPoint.x) + "," + (jPoint.y)+
12502 			" A " + (r1) +","+(r1)+" 0 0,1 "+ (kPoint.x) + "," + (kPoint.y)+
12503 			" A " + (r3) +","+(r3)+" 0 0,1 "+ (x+w) + "," + (y+h)+
12504 			" l -"+w+",0";
12505 			break;
12506 		case 'R':
12507 		 	path = 
12508 			" M " + (x) + "," + (y) +
12509 			" A " + (r1) +","+(r1)+" 0 0,1 "+ (kPoint.x-(w/2)) + "," + (kPoint.y)+
12510 			" A " + (r3) +","+(r3)+" 0 0,1 "+ (x+(w/2)) + "," + (y+h)+
12511 			" l -"+(w/2)+",0"+
12512 			" l 0,-"+h;
12513 			break;
12514 		
12515 		case 'L':
12516 		trace("w="+w);
12517 		 	path = 
12518 			" M " + (x) + "," + (y+h) +
12519 			" A " + (r3) +","+(r3)+" 0 0,1 "+ (jPoint.x) + "," + (jPoint.y)+
12520 			" A " + (r1) +","+(r1)+" 0 0,1 "+ (x+w/2) + "," + (y)+
12521 			" l 0,"+h+
12522 			" l -"+(w/2)+",0";
12523 			break;
12524 		default:
12525 			break;
12526 		}	
12527 	
12528 }
12529 else
12530 {
12531 	switch(segType)
12532 	{
12533 		case 'F':
12534 		 	path = 
12535 			" M " + (x) + "," + (y+h) +
12536 			" A " + (r3) +","+(r3)+" 0 0,1 "+ (jPoint.x) + "," + (jPoint.y)+
12537 			" A " + (r1) +","+(r1)+" 0 0,1 "+ (kPoint.x) + "," + (kPoint.y)+
12538 			" A " + (r3) +","+(r3)+" 0 0,1 "+ (x+w) + "," + (y+h)+
12539 			" l 0,"+h2+
12540 			" l -"+w+",0"+
12541 			" l 0,-"+h2;
12542 			break;
12543 		case 'R':
12544 		 	path = 
12545 			" M " + (x) + "," + (y) +
12546 			" A " + (r1) +","+(r1)+" 0 0,1 "+ (kPoint.x-(w/2)) + "," + (kPoint.y)+
12547 			" A " + (r3) +","+(r3)+" 0 0,1 "+ (x+(w/2)) + "," + (y+h)+
12548 			" l 0,"+h2+
12549 			" l -"+(w/2)+",0"+
12550 			" l 0,-"+(h+h2);
12551 			break;
12552 		
12553 		case 'L':
12554 		 	path = 
12555 			" M " + (x) + "," + (y+h) +
12556 			" A " + (r3) +","+(r3)+" 0 0,1 "+ (jPoint.x) + "," + (jPoint.y)+
12557 			" A " + (r1) +","+(r1)+" 0 0,1 "+ (x+w/2) + "," + (y)+
12558 			" l 0,"+(h+h2)+
12559 			" l -"+w/2+",0"+
12560 			" l 0,-"+(h2);
12561 			break;
12562 		default:
12563 			break;
12564 		}	
12565 }
12566 trace("glass path="+path);
12567 	gls.setAttribute("d",path);
12568 	
12569 	if(g("f_tn")!="true")
12570 	{
12571 		createDescription(id+"_pane", "GLASS ... base WIDTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w-inset)  +"  HEIGHT: " + inchesToInchesDim(h-inset) + ".");
12572 	}
12573 	
12574 
12575 }	
12576 catch(e)
12577 {
12578 	alertUser("Exception: initGlass3CentredArch('"+id+"','"+idFrame+"',"+xParm+","+ yParm+","+ wParm+","+ hParm+","+ hlegParm+","+ inset+",'"+segType+"'");
12579 
12580 	alertUser(e);
12581 	trace(e);
12582 }	
12583 } 
12584 
12585 
12586 /**
12587  * Draw 3-centered arch frame (mitered)
12588  * 
12589  * @param id		String id
12590  * @param x			decimal x coordinate of containing rectangle
12591  * @param y			decimal y coordinate of containing rectangle
12592  * @param w			decimal width  
12593  * @param h			decimal height 
12594  * @param hleg		decimal height legs 
12595  * @param inset		decimal frame inset
12596  * @param color		String web color code
12597  * @param segType	F=full, L=left qtr-round, R=right qtr-round
12598  * @return
12599  */
12600 function initFrame3CentredArch(id, xParm, yParm, wParm, hParm, hlegParm, inset, color, segType)
12601 {
12602 // segType: F=full, L=left half, R=right half
12603 
12604 	trace("initFrame3CentredArch('"+id+"',"+xParm+","+ yParm+","+ wParm+","+ hParm+","+ hlegParm+","+ inset+",'"+color+"','"+segType+"')");
12605 
12606 try{	
12607 
12608 	var x = xParm;
12609 	var xi = xParm+inset;
12610 	var y = yParm;
12611 	var yi = yParm + inset;
12612 	var w = segType == 'F' ? wParm : wParm*2;
12613 	var wi = segType == 'F' ? wParm - (2*inset) : wParm*2 - (2*inset);
12614 	var h = hParm;
12615 	var hi = hParm - inset;
12616 	var h2 = hlegParm;
12617 	var h2i = hlegParm;
12618 	
12619 
12620 
12621 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id);
12622 	var idPrefix = g("f_idprefix");
12623 	if(grp === null)
12624 	{
12625 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
12626 		grp.setAttribute("id",id);
12627 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
12628 	}
12629 	
12630 	
12631 	var frame = drawing.getElementById(id+"_frame");
12632 	if(frame === null)
12633 	{
12634 		frame = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
12635 		frame.setAttribute("id",id+"_frame");
12636 		frame.setAttribute("class","frame");
12637 		frame.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
12638 		
12639 		grp.appendChild(frame);
12640 	}
12641 	
12642 	var sill = drawing.getElementById(id+"_sill");
12643 	if(sill === null)
12644 	{
12645 		sill = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
12646 		sill.setAttribute("id",id+"_sill");
12647 		sill.setAttribute("class","frame");
12648 		sill.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
12649 		
12650 		grp.appendChild(sill);
12651 	}
12652 
12653 	var siderail,siderail2;
12654 	if(!(segType == "F" && h2 == 0))
12655 	{
12656 		siderail = drawing.getElementById(id+"_siderail1");
12657 		if(siderail === null)
12658 		{
12659 			siderail = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
12660 			siderail.setAttribute("id",id+"_siderail1");
12661 			siderail.setAttribute("class","frame");
12662 			siderail.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
12663 		
12664 			grp.appendChild(siderail);
12665 		}
12666 		if(h2 > 0)
12667 		{
12668 			siderail2 = drawing.getElementById(id+"_siderail2");
12669 			if(siderail2 === null)
12670 			{
12671 				siderail2 = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"path");
12672 				siderail2.setAttribute("id",id+"_siderail2");
12673 				siderail2.setAttribute("class","frame");
12674 				siderail2.setAttribute("d","M 0,0");
12675 		
12676 				grp.appendChild(siderail2);
12677 			}
12678 		}
12679 	}
12680 	
12681 	var r1,r1i,r2,r2i,r3,r3i,afBisectR,afBisectX,afBisectY,aAngle,aAngle,gAngle,hAngle,hHyp,hX,fPoint,gPoint,hPoint,jAngle,jPoint,kPoint,jiPoint,kiPoint,aPoint,bPoint,path;
12682 	var pathSill = null;
12683 	var pathRail = null;
12684 	var pathRail2 = null;
12685 	
12686 	var center1;
12687 
12688 with(Math)
12689 {
12690 	// outer
12691 	aAngle = Math.atan2(h,w/2);
12692 	
12693 	r2 = (w/2) - h;
12694 	fPoint = new Point(x+(w/2) - (Math.cos(aAngle)*r2), (y+Math.sin(aAngle)*r2));
12695 	
12696 	afBisectR = (sqrt(pow(fPoint.x-x,2)+pow(y+h-fPoint.y,2)))/2;
12697 	afBisectX = cos(aAngle)*afBisectR + x;	
12698 	afBisectY = y+h-sin(aAngle)*afBisectR;
12699 
12700 	gPoint=new Point(w/2, afBisectY + tan((PI/2)-aAngle)*(x+(w/2)-afBisectX));
12701 	r1 = y-gPoint.y;
12702 	trace("r1="+r1);
12703 	gAngle = atan2(gPoint.x-afBisectX,gPoint.y-afBisectY);
12704 	hPoint = new Point(x+w/2-tan(gAngle)*(gPoint.y-h-y),y+h);
12705 
12706 	r3 = hPoint.x - x;
12707 	trace("r3="+r3);
12708 	
12709 	jPoint = new Point(hPoint.x - sin(gAngle)*r3,hPoint.y-cos(gAngle)*r3);
12710 	kPoint = new Point(segType=="R"?x+w/2-(jPoint.x-x):x+w-(jPoint.x-x), jPoint.y);
12711 		
12712 	// inner
12713 	aAngle = Math.atan2(hi,wi/2);
12714 	
12715 	r2i = (wi/2) - hi;
12716 	fPoint = new Point(x+(w/2) - (Math.cos(aAngle)*r2i), (yi+Math.sin(aAngle)*r2i));
12717 	
12718 	afBisectR = (sqrt(pow(fPoint.x-xi,2)+pow(yi+hi-fPoint.y,2)))/2;
12719 	afBisectX = cos(aAngle)*afBisectR + xi;	
12720 	afBisectY = y+h-sin(aAngle)*afBisectR;
12721 
12722 	gPoint=new Point(w/2, afBisectY + tan((PI/2)-aAngle)*(x+(w/2)-afBisectX));
12723 	r1i = yi-gPoint.y;
12724 	trace("r1i="+r1i);
12725 	gAngle = atan2(gPoint.x-afBisectX,gPoint.y-afBisectY);
12726 	hPoint = new Point(x+w/2-tan(gAngle)*(gPoint.y-h-y),y+h);
12727 	r3i = hPoint.x - xi;
12728 
12729 	jiPoint = new Point(hPoint.x - sin(gAngle)*r3i,hPoint.y-cos(gAngle)*r3i);
12730 	kiPoint = new Point(segType=="R"?x+w/2-(jiPoint.x-x):x+w-(jiPoint.x-x), jiPoint.y);
12731 
12732 	llPoint = new Point(hPoint.x-(cos(atan2(inset,hPoint.x-xi))*r3i),hPoint.y-inset); // lower left
12733 	lrPoint = segType == "R" ?new Point(x+(w/2)-(llPoint.x-x),hPoint.y-inset):new Point(x+w-(llPoint.x-x),hPoint.y-inset); 
12734 			
12735 	ulPoint = new Point(x+inset,gPoint.y-sqrt(pow(r1i,2)-pow(inset,2))); // upper left, used only if segType=R
12736 	urPoint = new Point(x+(w/2)-inset, gPoint.y-sqrt(pow(r1i,2)-pow(inset,2)));  // upper right, used only if segType=L
12737 			
12738 }
12739  
12740 if(h2===0)
12741 {
12742 	switch(segType)
12743 	{
12744 		case 'F':
12745 		 	path = 
12746 			" M " + (x) + "," + (y+h) +
12747 			" A " + (r3) +","+(r3)+" 0 0,1 "+ (jPoint.x) + "," + (jPoint.y)+
12748 			" A " + (r1) +","+(r1)+" 0 0,1 "+ (kPoint.x) + "," + (kPoint.y)+
12749 			" A " + (r3) +","+(r3)+" 0 0,1 "+ (x+w) + "," + (y+h)+
12750 			" L "+lrPoint.x+","+lrPoint.y +
12751 			" A " + (r3i) +","+(r3i)+" 0 0,0 "+ (kiPoint.x) + "," + (kiPoint.y)+
12752 			" A " + (r1) +","+(r1)+" 0 0,0 "+ (jiPoint.x) + "," + (jiPoint.y)+
12753 			" A " + (r3i) +","+(r3i)+" 0 0,0 "+ (llPoint.x) + "," + (llPoint.y)+
12754 			" L " + (x) + "," + (y+h);
12755 			
12756 			pathSill = "M "+ (x) +","+(y+h)+
12757 					" l "+w+",0" +
12758 					" L "+lrPoint.x+","+lrPoint.y+
12759 					" L "+llPoint.x+","+llPoint.y+
12760 					" L "+ (x) +","+(y+h);
12761 			break;
12762 		case 'R':
12763 		 	path = 
12764 			" M " + (x) + "," + (y) +
12765 			" A " + (r1) +","+(r1)+" 0 0,1 "+ (kPoint.x) + "," + (kPoint.y)+
12766 			" A " + (r3) +","+(r3)+" 0 0,1 "+ (x+(w/2)) + "," + (y+h)+
12767 			" L "+lrPoint.x+","+lrPoint.y +
12768 			" A " + (r3i) +","+(r3i)+" 0 0,0 "+ (kiPoint.x) + "," + (kiPoint.y)+
12769 			" A " + (r1i) +","+(r1i)+" 0 0,0 "+ (ulPoint.x) + "," + (ulPoint.y)+
12770 			" L " + (x) + "," + (y);
12771 			
12772 			pathSill = "M "+ (x) +","+(y+h)+
12773 					" l "+(w/2)+",0" +
12774 					" L "+lrPoint.x+","+lrPoint.y+
12775 					" L "+(x+inset)+","+(y+h-inset)+
12776 					" L "+ (x) +","+(y+h);
12777 
12778 			
12779 			pathRail = "M "+(x)+","+(y)+
12780 					   	" l 0,"+(h)+
12781 						" l "+inset+",-"+inset+
12782 						" L "+(ulPoint.x)+","+ulPoint.y+
12783 						" L "+(x)+","+(y);
12784 			
12785 			break;
12786 		
12787 		case 'L':
12788 		 	path = 
12789 			" M " + (x) + "," + (y+h) +
12790 			" A " + (r3) +","+(r3)+" 0 0,1 "+ (jPoint.x) + "," + (jPoint.y)+
12791 			" A " + (r1) +","+(r1)+" 0 0,1 "+ (x+w/2) + "," + (y)+
12792 			" L "+urPoint.x+","+urPoint.y+
12793 			" A " + (r1i) +","+(r1i)+" 0 0,0 "+ (jiPoint.x) + "," + (jiPoint.y)+
12794 			" A " + (r3i) +","+(r3i)+" 0 0,0 "+ (llPoint.x) + "," + (llPoint.y)+
12795 			" L " + (x) + "," + (y+h);
12796 			
12797 			pathSill = "M "+ (x) +","+(y+h)+
12798 					" l "+(w/2)+",0" +
12799 					" L "+(x+(w/2)-inset)+","+(y+h-inset)+
12800 					" L "+llPoint.x+","+llPoint.y+
12801 					" L "+ (x) +","+(y+h);
12802 			
12803 			pathRail = "M "+(x+(w/2))+","+(y)+
12804 					   	" l 0,"+(h)+
12805 						" l -"+inset+",-"+inset+
12806 						" L "+(urPoint.x)+","+urPoint.y+
12807 						"M "+(x+(w/2))+","+(y);
12808 			
12809 			break;
12810 		default:
12811 			break;
12812 		}	
12813 }
12814 else
12815 {
12816 	switch(segType)

12826 			" A " + (r3i) +","+(r3i)+" 0 0,0 "+ (kiPoint.x) + "," + (kiPoint.y)+
12827 			" A " + (r1) +","+(r1)+" 0 0,0 "+ (jiPoint.x) + "," + (jiPoint.y)+
12828 			" A " + (r3i) +","+(r3i)+" 0 0,0 "+ (x+inset) + "," + (y+h)+
12829 			" L " + (x) + "," + (y+h);
12830 			
12831 			pathRail = "M "+(x)+","+(y+h)+
12832 					   	" l 0,"+h2+
12833 						" l "+inset+",-"+ inset +
12834 						" L " + (x+inset) + "," + (y+h);
12835 						" L "+(x)+","+(y+h);
12836

12838 					   	" l 0,"+h2+

12841 						" L "+(x+w)+","+(y+h);

12844 					" l "+ w +",0"+
12845 					" l -"+inset+",-"+inset +

12847 					 " L "+ (x) +","+(y+h+h2);

12861 					   	" l 0,"+(h+h2)+

12871

12873 					" l "+ (w/2) +",0"+
12874 					" l -"+inset+",-"+inset +
12875 					" l -"+ ((w/2)-(2*inset)) +",0"+
12876 					 " L "+ (x) +","+(y+h+h2);
12877 
12878 				
12879 			break;
12880 		
12881 		case 'L':
12882 		 	path = 
12883 			" M " + (x) + "," + (y+h) +
12884 			" A " + (r3) +","+(r3)+" 0 0,1 "+ (jPoint.x) + "," + (jPoint.y)+

12886 			" L  "+urPoint.x+","+urPoint.y+

12889 			" L " + (x) + "," + (y+h);
12890 			
12891 			pathRail = "M "+(x)+","+(y+h)+
12892 					   	" l 0,"+h2+

12904 					" l "+ (w/2) +",0"+
12905 					" l -"+inset+",-"+inset +

12907 					 " L "+ (x) +","+(y+h+h2);
12908 
12909 			
12910 			break;
12911 		default:
12912 			break;
12913 		}	
12914 }
12915 	trace("frame path="+path);

12917 	frame.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
12918

12921 	sill.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");

12927 		siderail.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
12928 	}

12931 	{

12933 		siderail2.setAttribute("d",pathRail2);
12934 		siderail2.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");

12938 	{
12939 		createDescription(id+"_frame", "FRAME ... base WIDTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w)  +"  HEIGHT: " + inchesToInchesDim(h) + ".");
12940 	}
12941 	
12942 
12943 }	
12944 catch(e)
12945 {
12946 	alertUser("Exception: initFrame3CentredArch('"+id+","+xParm+","+ yParm+","+ wParm+","+ hParm+","+ hlegParm+","+ inset+",'"+color+"','"+segType+"')");
12947

12951 }

12955 /**
12956  * Draw 3-centered arch frame (non-mitered)
12957  * 
12958  * @param id		String id
12959  * @param x			decimal x coordinate of containing rectangle
12960  * @param y			decimal y coordinate of containing rectangle
12961  * @param w			decimal width  
12962  * @param h			decimal height 
12963  * @param hleg		decimal height legs 
12964  * @param inset		decimal frame inset
12965  * @param sillThk	decimal sill thickness
12966  * @param color		String web color code
12967  * @param segType	F=full, L=left qtr-round, R=right qtr-round
12968  * @return
12969  */
12970 function initFrame3CentredArchWithSill(id, xParm, yParm, wParm, hParm, hlegParm, inset, sillThk, color, segType)
12971 {
12972 // segType: F=full, L=left half, R=right half
12973 
12974 	trace("initFrame3CentredArchWithSill('"+id+"',"+xParm+","+ yParm+","+ wParm+","+ hParm+","+ hlegParm+","+ inset+","+ sillThk+",'"+color+"','"+segType+"')");
12975 
12976 try{	
12977 
12978 	var x = xParm;
12979 	var xi = xParm+inset;
12980 	var y = yParm;
12981 	var yi = yParm + inset;
12982 	var w = segType == 'F' ? wParm : wParm*2;
12983 	var wi = segType == 'F' ? wParm - (2*inset) : wParm*2 - (2*inset);
12984 	var h = hlegParm === 0 ? hParm-sillThk: (sillThk > hlegParm ? hParm+hlegParm-sillThk : hParm);
12985 	var hi = h - inset;
12986 	var h2 = hlegParm === 0 || hlegParm < sillThk ? 0 : hlegParm-sillThk;
12987 	var h2i = h2;
12988 	
12989 
12990 
12991 	var grp = drawing.getElementById(id);
12992 	var idPrefix = g("f_idprefix");
12993 	if(grp === null)
12994 	{
12995 		grp = drawing.createElementNS(svgNS,"g");
12996 		grp.setAttribute("id",id);
12997 		drawing.getElementById("window").appendChild(grp);
12998 	}
12999 	
13000 	
13001 	var frame = drawing.getElementById(id+"_frame");

13005 		frame.setAttribute("id",id+"_frame");

13021 	}

13053

13056 	var pathRail2=null;

13059 {
13060 	// outer
13061 	aAngle = Math.atan2(h,w/2);
13062 	
13063 	r2 = (w/2) - h;
13064 	fPoint = new Point(x+(w/2) - (Math.cos(aAngle)*r2), (y+Math.sin(aAngle)*r2));
13065 	
13066 	afBisectR = (sqrt(pow(fPoint.x-x,2)+pow(y+h-fPoint.y,2)))/2;
13067 	afBisectX = cos(aAngle)*afBisectR + x;	
13068 	afBisectY = y+h-sin(aAngle)*afBisectR;
13069 
13070 	gPoint=new Point(w/2, afBisectY + tan((PI/2)-aAngle)*(x+(w/2)-afBisectX));
13071 	r1 = y-gPoint.y;
13072 	trace("r1="+r1);
13073 	gAngle = atan2(gPoint.x-afBisectX,gPoint.y-afBisectY);
13074 	hPoint = new Point(x+w/2-tan(gAngle)*(gPoint.y-h-y),y+h);
13075

13077 	trace("r3="+r3);
13078

13080 	kPoint = new Point(segType=="R"?x+w/2-(jPoint.x-x):x+w-(jPoint.x-x), jPoint.y);
13081 		
13082 	// inner
13083 	aAngle = Math.atan2(hi,wi/2);
13084

13087

13089 	afBisectX = cos(aAngle)*afBisectR + xi;	
13090 	afBisectY = y+h-sin(aAngle)*afBisectR;
13091 
13092 	gPoint=new Point(w/2, afBisectY + tan((PI/2)-aAngle)*(x+(w/2)-afBisectX));
13093 	r1i = yi-gPoint.y;

13095 	gAngle = atan2(gPoint.x-afBisectX,gPoint.y-afBisectY);
13096 	hPoint = new Point(x+w/2-tan(gAngle)*(gPoint.y-h-y),y+h);

13103 	lrPoint = segType == "R" ?new Point(x+(w/2)-(llPoint.x-x),hPoint.y-inset):new Point(x+w-(llPoint.x-x),hPoint.y-inset); 
13104 			
13105 	ulPoint = new Point(x+inset,gPoint.y-sqrt(pow(r1i,2)-pow(inset,2))); // upper left, used only if segType=R
13106 	urPoint = new Point(x+(w/2)-inset, gPoint.y-sqrt(pow(r1i,2)-pow(inset,2)));  // upper right, used only if segType=L
13107 			
13108 }
13109  
13110 if(h2===0)

13113 	{
13114 		case 'F':
13115 		 	path =

13118 			" A " + (r1) +","+(r1)+" 0 0,1 "+ (kPoint.x) + "," + (kPoint.y)+
13119 			" A " + (r3) +","+(r3)+" 0 0,1 "+ (x+w) + "," + (y+h)+
13120 			" l -"+inset+",0"+
13121 			" A " + (r3i) +","+(r3i)+" 0 0,0 "+ (kiPoint.x) + "," + (kiPoint.y)+
13122 			" A " + (r1) +","+(r1)+" 0 0,0 "+ (jiPoint.x) + "," + (jiPoint.y)+
13123 			" A " + (r3i) +","+(r3i)+" 0 0,0 "+ (xi) + "," + (y+h)+
13124 			" l -"+inset+",0";
13125 			pathSill = "M "+ (x) +","+(y+h)+
13126 					" l "+ (w) +",0"+
13127 					" l 0,"+ sillThk +
13128 					" l -"+ (w) + ",0"+
13129 					" l 0,-"+ sillThk;
13130 			break;
13131 		case 'R':
13132 		 	path = 
13133 			" M " + (x) + "," + (y) +
13134 			" A " + (r1) +","+(r1)+" 0 0,1 "+ (kPoint.x) + "," + (kPoint.y)+
13135 			" A " + (r3) +","+(r3)+" 0 0,1 "+ (x+(w/2)) + "," + (y+h)+
13136 			" l -"+inset+",0"+
13137 			" A " + (r3i) +","+(r3i)+" 0 0,0 "+ (kiPoint.x) + "," + (kiPoint.y)+
13138 			" A " + (r1i) +","+(r1i)+" 0 0,0 "+ (ulPoint.x) + "," + (ulPoint.y)+
13139 			" L " + (x) + "," + (y);
13140 			
13141 			pathRail = "M "+(x)+","+(y)+
13142 					   	" l 0,"+(h)+
13143 						" l "+inset+",0"+

13172 					" l "+ (w/2) +",0"+

13258 			
13259 			pathRail = "M "+(x)+","+(y+h)+
13260 					   	" l 0,"+h2+
13261 						" l "+inset+",0"+
13262 						" L  "+(x+inset) + "," + (y+h)+
13263 						" L "+(x)+","+(y+h);
13264 		
13265 			pathRail2 = "M "+(x+(w/2))+","+(y)+
13266 					   	" l 0,"+(h+h2)+
13267 						" l -"+inset+",0"+
13268 						" L  "+urPoint.x+","+urPoint.y+
13269 						" L "+(x+(w/2))+","+(y);
13270 	
13271 			pathSill = "M "+ (x) +","+(y+h+h2)+
13272 					" l "+ (w/2) +",0"+
13273 					" l 0,"+ sillThk +
13274 					" l -"+ (w/2) + ",0"+
13275 					" l 0,-"+ sillThk;
13276 	
13277 			
13278 			break;
13279 		default:
13280 			break;
13281 		}	
13282 }
13283 	trace("frame path="+path);
13284 	frame.setAttribute("d",path);
13285 	frame.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
13286 
13287 	trace("sill path="+pathSill);
13288 	sill.setAttribute("d",pathSill);
13289 	sill.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
13290 
13291 	if(pathRail !== null)
13292 	{
13293 		trace("rail path="+pathRail);
13294 		siderail.setAttribute("d",pathRail);
13295 		siderail.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
13296 	}
13297 	
13298 	if(pathRail2!== null)
13299 	{
13300 		trace("rail2 path="+pathRail2);
13301 		siderail2.setAttribute("d",pathRail2);
13302 		siderail2.getStyle().setProperty("fill",color,"");
13303 	}
13304 	
13305 	if(g("f_tn")!="true")
13306 	{
13307 		createDescription(id+"_frame", "FRAME ... base WIDTH: " + inchesToInchesDim(w)  +"  HEIGHT: " + inchesToInchesDim(h) + ".");
13308 	}
13309 	
13310 
13311 }	
13312 catch(e)
13313 {
13314 	alertUser("Exception: 	initFrame3CentredArchWithSill('"+id+"',"+xParm+","+ yParm+","+ wParm+","+ hParm+","+ hlegParm+","+ inset+","+ sillThk+",'"+color+"','"+segType+"')");
13315 
13316 	alertUser(e);
13317 	trace(e);
13318 }

13322 /**
13323  * Get an array of end points for a radial grille.
13324  * 
13325  * @param p1Radians			decimal angle(radians) of arc beginning
13326  * @param p2Radians			decimal	angle(radians) of arc end
13327  * @param center			Point	center point
13328  * @param radius			decimal radius
13329  * @param spokes			integer number of spokes
13330  * @param includeStartPoint	boolean spoke at beginning
13331  * @param includeEndPoint	boolean spoke at end
13332  * @return	Array of Points
13333  */
13334 
13335 function getAnglePoints(p1Radians,p2Radians,center,radius,spokes,includeStartPoint, includeEndPoint)
13336 {
13337 trace("getAnglePoints("+p1Radians+","+p2Radians+",("+center.x+","+center.y+"),"+radius+","+spokes+","+includeStartPoint+","+includeEndPoint+")");
13338 	var spokeEndPoints = new Array(spokes);
13339 	
13340 	var radians = p2Radians - p1Radians;
13341 	var segs = spokes+1;
13342 	if(includeStartPoint)
13343 	{
13344 		segs--;
13345 	}
13346 	if(includeEndPoint)
13347 	{
13348 		segs--;
13349 	}
13350 	var radianSeg = radians/segs;
13351 	var circumSeg = Math.abs(radianSeg*radius);
13352 	trace("radianSeg="+radianSeg);
13353 	trace("circumSeg="+circumSeg);
13354 	
13355 	var x,y,c,a,aTotal;
13356 	
13357 	var spoke=1;
13358 	if(includeStartPoint)
13359 	{
13360 		a = p1Radians;
13361 		c = 0;
13362 		
13363 		x = center.x - Math.sin(a)*radius;
13364 		y = center.y - Math.abs(Math.cos(a)*radius);
13365 		spokeEndPoints[0] =	new RadialPoint(x,y,c,a);
13366 		trace(" x="+x+" y="+y +" c="+c+" a="+a);
13367 		spoke++;
13368 	}
13369 	for(;spoke<=spokes;spoke++)
13370 	{
13371 		a = p1Radians+radianSeg*(includeStartPoint?spoke-1:spoke);
13372 		c = circumSeg*(includeStartPoint?spoke-1:spoke);
13373 		
13374 		x = center.x - Math.sin(a)*radius;
13375 		y = center.y - Math.abs(Math.cos(a)*radius);
13376 		spokeEndPoints[spoke-1] = 
13377 				new RadialPoint(x,y,c,a);
13378 		trace(" x="+x+" y="+y +" c="+c+" a="+a);
13379 		
13380 	}
13381 	return spokeEndPoints;
13382 }

13389  *

13391  * @param p2				Point	point at arc end
13392  * @param center			Point	center point
13393  * @param radius			decimal radius
13394  * @param spokes			integer number of spokes
13395  * @param includeStartPoint	boolean spoke at beginning
13396  * @param includeEndPoint	boolean spoke at end

13399 
13400 function getRadialPoints(p1,p2,center,radius,spokes,includeStartPoint, includeEndPoint)
13401 {
13402 trace("getRadialPoints(("+p1.x+","+p1.y+"),("+p2.x+","+p2.y+"),("+center.x+","+center.y+"),"+radius+","+spokes+","+includeStartPoint+","+includeEndPoint+")");

13405 	var p1Radians = Math.atan2(center.x-p1.x,center.y-p1.y);
13406 	var p2Radians = Math.atan2(center.x-p2.x,center.y-p2.y);
13407 	trace("p1Radians="+p1Radians);
13408 	trace("p2Radians="+p2Radians);
13409 	var radians = p2Radians - p1Radians;
13410 	var segs = spokes+1;
13411 	if(includeStartPoint)
13412 	{
13413 		segs--;
13414 	}
13415 	if(includeEndPoint)
13416 	{
13417 		segs--;
13418 	}
13419 	var radianSeg = radians/segs;
13420 	var circumSeg = Math.abs(radianSeg*radius);
13421 	trace("radianSeg="+radianSeg);
13422 	trace("circumSeg="+circumSeg);
13423 	
13424 	var spoke=1;
13425 	if(includeStartPoint)
13426 	{
13427 		spokeEndPoints[0] = new RadialPoint(p1.x,p1.y,0,0);
13428 		spoke++;
13429 	}
13430 	var x,y,c,a,aTotal;
13431 	for(;spoke<=spokes;spoke++)

13434 		c = circumSeg*(includeStartPoint?spoke-1:spoke);
13435 		
13436 		x = center.x - Math.sin(a)*radius;
13437 		y = center.y - Math.abs(Math.cos(a)*radius);
13438 		spokeEndPoints[spoke-1] = 
13439 				new RadialPoint(x,y,c,a);
13440 		trace(" x="+x+" y="+y +" c="+c+" a="+a);
13441 		
13442 	}
13443 	return spokeEndPoints;

13448 /**
13449  * Get an array of end points for a radial grille.
13450  * Same as getRadialPoints() except it supports an arch segment
13451  * within a wall-of-windows modelset.
13452  * 
13453  * @param p1				Point	point at arc beginning
13454  * @param p2				Point	point at arc end
13455  * @param center			Point	center point
13456  * @param radius			decimal radius
13457  * @param spokes			integer number of spokes
13458  * @param includeStartPoint	boolean spoke at beginning
13459  * @param includeEndPoint	boolean spoke at end
13460  * @return	Array of Points
13461  */
13462 
13463 function getRadialPointsByHorzSegments(p1,p2,center,radius,spokes,includeStartPoint, includeEndPoint)
13464 {
13465 trace("getRadialPointsByHorzSegments(("+p1.x+","+p1.y+"),("+p2.x+","+p2.y+"),("+center.x+","+center.y+"),"+radius+","+spokes+","+includeStartPoint+","+includeEndPoint+")");
13466 	var spokeEndPoints = new Array(spokes);
13467 	
13468 	var p1Radians = Math.atan2(center.x-p1.x,center.y-p1.y);
13469 	var p2Radians = Math.atan2(center.x-p2.x,center.y-p2.y);
13470 	trace("p1Radians="+p1Radians);
13471 	trace("p2Radians="+p2Radians);
13472 	var radians = p2Radians - p1Radians;
13473 	var segs = spokes+1;
13474 	if(includeStartPoint)
13475 	{
13476 		segs--;
13477 	}
13478 	if(includeEndPoint)
13479 	{
13480 		segs--;
13481 	}
13482 
13483 	var horzSeg = (p2.x - p1.x)/segs;
13484 	trace("horzSeg="+horzSeg);
13485 	
13486 	var spoke=1;
13487 	if(includeStartPoint)
13488 	{
13489 		spokeEndPoints[0] = new RadialPoint(p1.x,p1.y,0,0);
13490 		spoke++;
13491 	}
13492 	var x,y,c,a,h,aTotal;
13493 	for(;spoke<=spokes;spoke++)
13494 	{
13495 		h = (includeStartPoint?spoke-1:spoke)*horzSeg;
13496 		a = Math.atan2((p1.x+h)-center.x,Math.sqrt(Math.pow(radius,2)-Math.pow(center.x-(p1.x+h),2)));
13497 		c = a*radius;
13498 		
13499 		x = p1.x+ h;
13500 		y = center.y - Math.abs(Math.cos(a)*radius);
13501 		spokeEndPoints[spoke-1] = 
13502 				new RadialPoint(x,y,c,a);
13503 		trace(" x="+x+" y="+y +" c="+c+" a="+a);
13504 		
13505 	}
13506 	return spokeEndPoints;
13507 }

13514 /**
13515  * Get an array of spoke end points for a radial grille pattern applied
13516  * to a 3-centered arch.
13517  * UNDER DEVELOPMENT ... USE WITH CAUTION!
13518  * 
13519  * @param xP		decimal x coordinate of containing rectangle
13520  * @param y			decimal y coordinate of containing rectangle
13521  * @param wP		decimal width coordinate of containing rectangle
13522  * @param h			decimal height coordinate of containing rectangle
13523  * @param spokes	integer number of spokes
13524  * @param segType	character F=full, L=left qtr-round, R=right qtr-round
13525  * @return
13526  */
13527 
13528 function getRadialPointsFor3CenterArc(xP,y,wP,h,spokes,segType)
13529 {
13530 trace("getRadialPointsFor3CenterArc("+xP+","+y+","+wP+","+h+","+spokes+",'"+segType+"')");
13531 	var spokeEndPoints = new Array(spokes);
13532 	
13533 	var x = segType=="L" ? xP-wP : xP;
13534 	var w = segType=="F" ? wP : wP*2;
13535 	
13536 	var r1,r2,r3,af,afBisectR,afAngle,afBisectX,afBisectY,gAngle,hAngle,hHyp,hX,fPoint,gPoint,hPoint,iPoint,aAngle,jAngle,jPoint,kPoint,path;
13537 	
13538 	var c1,c2,c3;
13539 		
13540 	with(Math)
13541 	{
13542 
13543 	aAngle = Math.atan2(h,w/2);
13544 	trace("aAngle="+aAngle);
13545 	r2 = (w/2) - h;
13546 	trace("r2="+r2);
13547 	trace("w="+w);
13548 	trace("x="+x);
13549 	trace("cos(aAngle)*r2="+(cos(aAngle)*r2));
13550 	fPoint = new Point(x+(w/2) - (cos(aAngle)*r2), (y+sin(aAngle)*r2));
13551 	trace("fPoint="+fPoint.x+","+fPoint.y);
13552 	 
13553 	afBisectR = (sqrt(pow(fPoint.x-x,2)+pow(y+h-fPoint.y,2)))/2; 
13554 	trace("afBisectR="+afBisectR);
13555 	afBisectX = cos(aAngle)*afBisectR + x;	
13556 	afBisectY = y+h-sin(aAngle)*afBisectR;
13557 	
13558 	gPoint=new Point(x+w/2, afBisectY + tan((PI/2)-aAngle)*(x+(w/2)-afBisectX));
13559 	trace("gPoint=" + gPoint.x+","+gPoint.y);
13560 	r1 = gPoint.y-y;
13561 	trace("r1="+r1);
13562 	
13563 	
13564 	gAngle = atan2(gPoint.x-afBisectX,gPoint.y-afBisectY);
13565 	hPoint = new Point(x+w/2-tan(gAngle)*(gPoint.y-h-y),y+h);
13566 	trace("hPoint="+hPoint.x+","+hPoint.y);
13567 	r3 = hPoint.x - x;
13568 	trace("r3="+r3);
13569 	trace("gAngle="+gAngle);
13570 	hAngle = (PI/2) - abs(gAngle);
13571 	trace("hAngle="+hAngle);
13572 
13573 	iPoint = new Point(x+w/2+tan(gAngle)*(gPoint.y-h-y),y+h);
13574 	trace("iPoint="+iPoint.x+","+iPoint.y);
13575 	
13576 	jPoint = new Point(hPoint.x - sin(gAngle)*r3,hPoint.y-cos(gAngle)*r3);
13577 	trace("jPoint="+jPoint.x+","+jPoint.y);
13578 	
13579 	kPoint = new Point(x+w-(jPoint.x-x), jPoint.y);
13580 	trace("kPoint="+kPoint.x+","+kPoint.y);
13581 	
13582 	c1=c3=abs(r3*hAngle);
13583 	c2=abs(r1*gAngle*2);
13584 	
13585 	}
13586 trace("c1="+c1);
13587 trace("c2="+c2);
13588 trace("c3="+c3);
13589 
13590 	var cSeg = (c1+c2+c3)/(spokes+1);
13591 	trace("cSeg="+cSeg);
13592 
13593 	
13594 	var spoke=1;
13595 	var xx,yy,aa,aTotal;
13596 	var cc = 0;
13597 	var ccRem = 0;
13598 	for(;spoke<=spokes;spoke++)
13599 	{
13600 		cc = cSeg*spoke;
13601 		trace("cc="+cc);
13602 		if(cc <= c1)
13603 		{
13604 		trace("11111");
13605 			aa = cc/r3;
13606 				trace("aa="+aa);
13607 					trace("Math.cos(aa)="+Math.cos(aa));
13608 					trace("Math.sin(aa)="+Math.sin(aa));
13609 			xx = hPoint.x - Math.abs(Math.cos(aa)*r3);
13610 			yy = hPoint.y - Math.abs(Math.sin(aa)*r3);			
13611 		}
13612 		else
13613 		if(cc > c1 && cc <= (c1+c2))
13614 		{
13615 			trace("222222");
13616 		
13617 			
13618 			ccRem = cc - c1;
13619 			trace("ccRem="+ccRem);
13620 			if(ccRem < c2/2)
13621 			{
13622 				aa = Math.abs(((c2/2)-ccRem)/r1);
13623 				trace("aa="+aa);
13624 				trace("Math.cos(aa)="+Math.cos(aa));
13625 				trace("Math.sin(aa)="+Math.sin(aa));
13626 				xx = gPoint.x - Math.sin(aa)*r1;
13627 				yy = gPoint.y - Math.cos(aa)*r1;
13628 			}
13629 			else
13630 			{
13631 				aa = Math.abs((ccRem - (c2/2))/r1);
13632 				trace("aa="+aa);
13633 				trace("Math.cos(aa)="+Math.cos(aa));
13634 				trace("Math.sin(aa)="+Math.sin(aa));
13635 				xx = gPoint.x + Math.sin(aa)*r1;
13636 				yy = gPoint.y - Math.cos(aa)*r1;
13637 				
13638 			}
13639 			
13640 		}
13641 		else
13642 		{
13643 			trace("3333333");
13644 		
13645 			ccRem = (c1+c2+c3) - cc;
13646 			aa = ccRem/r3;
13647 					trace("aa="+aa);
13648 					trace("Math.cos(aa)="+Math.cos(aa));
13649 					trace("Math.sin(aa)="+Math.sin(aa));
13650 			
13651 			xx = iPoint.x + Math.abs(Math.cos(aa)*r3);
13652 			yy = iPoint.y - Math.abs(Math.sin(aa)*r3);
13653 		}
13654 		
13655 		spokeEndPoints[spoke-1] = 
13656 				new RadialPoint(xx,yy,cc,0);
13657 		trace(" x="+xx+" y="+yy +" c="+cc+" a=0");
13658 		
13659 	}
13660 	return spokeEndPoints;
13661 }
13662 
13663 
13664 
13665 /////////// Functions to calculate circle center 
13666 /////////// and radius given 3 points (e.g. left,top,right).
13667 
13668 var zero = parseFloat("0");
13669 var Xo, Yo;
13670 var R;
13671 var P = [[zero,zero],[zero,zero],[zero,zero]];
13672 
13673 /**
13674  * Determine the center point of a circle given 3 points on an arc.
13675  * Will be indeterminant if points do not fall on a circular arc.
13676  * 
13677  * @param x1
13678  * @param y1
13679  * @param x2
13680  * @param y2
13681  * @param x3
13682  * @param y3
13683  * @return
13684  */
13685 function computeCircleCenter(x1,y1,x2,y2,x3,y3)
13686 {
13687     P[0][0] = x1;
13688     P[0][1] = y1;
13689     P[1][0] = x2;
13690     P[1][1] = y2;
13691     P[2][0] = x3;
13692     P[2][1] = y3;
13693 
13694     // check input
13695     if (isNaN(P[0][0])||isNaN(P[0][1])||
13696         isNaN(P[1][0])||isNaN(P[1][1])||
13697         isNaN(P[2][0])||isNaN(P[2][1]))
13698     {
13699         window.alert("Invalid input!");
13700         return;
13701     }
13702   
13703     var r = circle();
13704     if (r > 0)
13705     {
13706        // calc.x0.value = Xo;
13707        // calc.y0.value = Yo;
13708        // calc.r0.value = r;
13709        R = r;
13710     }
13711     else
13712        alert("Internal logic error.. computeCircleCenter()"); // calc.r0.value = "Not a circle";
13713 }
13714 
13715 //  Calculate center and radius of circle given three points
13716 function circle()
13717 {
13718     var i;
13719     var r, m11, m12, m13, m14;
13720     var a = [[zero,zero,zero],[zero,zero,zero],[zero,zero,zero]];
13721 
13722     for (i = 0; i < 3; i++)                    // find minor 11
13723     {
13724         a[i][0] = P[i][0];
13725         a[i][1] = P[i][1];
13726         a[i][2] = 1;
13727     }
13728     m11 = determinant( a, 3 );
13729 
13730     for (i = 0; i < 3; i++)                    // find minor 12 
13731     {
13732         a[i][0] = P[i][0]*P[i][0] + P[i][1]*P[i][1];
13733         a[i][1] = P[i][1];
13734         a[i][2] = 1;
13735     }
13736     m12 = determinant( a, 3 );
13737 
13738     for (i = 0; i < 3; i++)                    // find minor 13
13739     {
13740         a[i][0] = P[i][0]*P[i][0] + P[i][1]*P[i][1];
13741         a[i][1] = P[i][0]
13742         a[i][2] = 1;
13743     }
13744     m13 = determinant( a, 3 );
13745 
13746     for (i = 0; i < 3; i++)                    // find minor 14
13747     {
13748         a[i][0] = P[i][0]*P[i][0] + P[i][1]*P[i][1];
13749         a[i][1] = P[i][0];
13750         a[i][2] = P[i][1];
13751     }
13752     m14 = determinant( a, 3 );
13753 
13754     if (m11 == 0)
13755     {
13756         r = 0;                                 // not a circle
13757     }
13758     else
13759     {
13760         Xo =  0.5 * m12 / m11;                 // center of circle
13761         Yo = -0.5 * m13 / m11;
13762         r  = Math.sqrt( Xo*Xo + Yo*Yo + m14/m11 );
13763     }
13764 
13765     return r;                                  // the radius
13766 }
13767 
13768 // Recursive definition of determinate using expansion by minors.
13769 function determinant( a, n )
13770 {
13771     var i, j, j1, j2;
13772     var d = parseFloat("0");
13773     var m = [[zero,zero,zero],[zero,zero,zero],[zero,zero,zero]];
13774 
13775     if (n == 2)                                // terminate recursion
13776     {
13777         d = a[0][0]*a[1][1] - a[1][0]*a[0][1];
13778     }
13779     else 
13780     {
13781         d = 0;
13782         for (j1 = 0; j1 < n; j1++ )            // do each column
13783         {
13784             for (i = 1; i < n; i++)            // create minor
13785             {
13786                 j2 = 0;
13787                 for (j = 0; j < n; j++)
13788                 {
13789                     if (j == j1) continue;
13790                     m[i-1][j2] = a[i][j];
13791                     j2++;
13792                 }
13793             }
13794             
13795             // sum (+/-)cofactor * minor  
13796             d = d + Math.pow(-1.0, j1)*a[0][j1]*determinant( m, n-1 );
13797         }
13798     }
13799 
13800     return d;
13801 }
13802 
13803 
13804  
13805
